Kwiyongera cyane kw'ubwandu bw'indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19) mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'ubukungu k'Uburayi n'ubw'ubwami bw'Ubwongereza, kuva ku wa 1 Mutarama kugeza ku wa 15 Werurwe 2020
Umubare w'abandura coronavirus (COVID-19) ugaragaza ibintu nk'ibi mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, byemeza ko nubwo mu byiciro bitandukanye bitewe n'igihugu, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kigenda gihinduka vuba mu bihugu byose.
Hashingiwe ku byaranze Ubutaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibyumba byita ku barwayi bakomeye bigomba kongera imyiteguro yabo yo guhangana n'ubwiyongere bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazagomba kwitabwaho mu by'ubuzima, cyane cyane mu by'ubuvuzi bukomeye.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, hamaze kugaragara icyiciro cy'abantu banduye icyorezo cya Pneumonia kitaramenyekana mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kugenzura no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari coronavirus nshya ubu yitwa severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 yiswe indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko abagera kuri 80% bafite COVID-19 bafite indwara yoroheje, ni ukuvuga ubwandu bw'inzira zo guhumeka hamwe na pneumonia cyangwa ntayo, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
Mu bantu bagera kuri 14%, COVID-19 iba indwara ikomeye cyane igasaba kuvurirwa mu bitaro, mu gihe abasigaye 6% baba barwaye indwara ikomeye igasaba kwitabwaho cyane.
Urupfu rw'abarwayi bari mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 ni hafi 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye imiterere y'ubwiyongere bwa COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cy'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu k'u Burayi (EU/EEA) n'u Bwongereza (Ubwongereza) maze tugereranya n'ibyabaye mu Ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Turagereranya kandi umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza n'uw'u Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 yakomeje gukwirakwira mu bice bitandukanye by'isi kandi icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bindi bice by'isi ubu gikurikirana icy'iki gihugu.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu nomero yo ku ya 5 Werurwe ya Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. batangaje ku byerekeye abarwayi ba mbere bemejwe ba COVID-19 mu Burayi hakurikijwe ibisobanuro by'abarwayi ba OMS.
Mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi, abarwayi batatu ba mbere bemejwe batangajwe n'u Bufaransa ku wa 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bagarutse baturutse i Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, abanduye COVID-19 bari bamaze kugaragara mu bihugu byose 30 bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza (Ubwongereza), aho kuva ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza kuri iyo tariki harimo, abanduye 39,768 n'abapfuye 1,727 bari bamaze kumenyekana, mu Butaliyani honyine hakaba hari abanduye 17,750 n'abapfuye 1,441.
Kubona umubare w'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 n'ubw'ubwandu bwabwo
Mu Kigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara no Kuzirinda (ECDC), imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 bamenyeshejwe mu bihugu byose ku isi, iboneka gusa ku nkomoko z'ubutegetsi nka Minisiteri y'Ubuzima, inzego z'ubuzima z'igihugu n'iz'akarere na OMS, iherutse gusubirwamo buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gupima imiterere ya COVID-19 muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, no kuyigereranya n'iyo mu Butaliyani.
Nk'igaragaza ry'ubwiyongere bw'abanduye COVID-19, twabaze imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14, bityo dufata mu mutwe icyiciro cy'indwara ya COVID-19, muri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, mu gihe cy'itariki ya 1 Mutarama-15 Werurwe 2020.
Twagaragaje kandi umubare w'ubwandu bwemejwe muri buri gihugu ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani za mu gitondo ugereranyije n'uw'u Butaliyani ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama 15 Werurwe 2020.
Uko COVID-19 imeze mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza
Imiterere y'ibimenyetso by'iminsi 14 by'ubwandu bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza byakurikiyeho mu Ntara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Ku bihugu byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA n'u Bwongereza muri rusange, umubare w'abandura COVID-19 watangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, nyuma y'aho wiyongera cyane ahagana ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Ibitabo by'inyongera).
Ibi ahanini byatewe n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'umubare w'abandura baturuka mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byagaragaje ingendo zimeze nk'izo mu kwiyongera kw'ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 (Ibitabo by'inyongera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza umubare w'ubwandu bwa COVID-19, mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza ugereranyije n'uw'u Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama- 15 Werurwe 2020.
Igaragaza ko ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani za mu gitondo, ibindi bihugu 15 bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byari bimaze gutanga raporo y'umubare w'abanduye ugereranywa n'uw'u Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu gusa cyangwa munsi y'aho.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu bigaragaza ko umubare w'abamenyeshejwe ko banduye COVID-19 uri kwiyongera cyane mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Imiterere yafashwe mu mubare w'abandura COVID-19 igaragaza ko icyorezo kigenda kigenda ku muvuduko ugereranywa mu bihugu byose.
Ibi ni nubwo ibihugu biri mu byiciro bitandukanye, gutandukana mu bisubizo by'ubuzima rusange bw'igihugu, kandi bishoboka ko ibisobanuro by'abanduye bitandukanye mu bihugu ndetse n'amabwiriza atandukanye yo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo COVID-19 yemezwe, harimo no gupima.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere twugarijwe n'iki cyorezo mu Butaliyani basobanuye uko byari byifashe aho abagera kuri 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, kandi amakuru y'ibinyamakuru yatangaje ko ibitaro n'ibyumba byitabwaho cyane muri utwo turere byari byamaze kugera ku bushobozi busesuye.
Amakuru ku byerekeranye no kwakira abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bitaro no/cyangwa mu byumba byita ku barwayi bakomeye ubu araboneka ku rwego rwa EU/EEA ku byerekeranye na 6% na 1% by'abarwayi gusa (amakuru ntabwo agaragajwe).
Icyakora, bigomba gukusanywa mu buryo bufite gahunda kugira ngo byuzuze amakuru y'ubugenzuzi ariho ubu, yibanda ku mubare w'abamaze kwandura n'umubare w'abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 201011 bwagaragaje itandukaniro rinini mu bubiko bw'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bwitondewe n'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi hagati mu Burayi, kuva kuri 29,2 mu Budage kugeza kuri 4,2 ku baturage 100,000 muri Portugal.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bishobora kugira umutungo munini cyangwa muke ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (12,5 ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bwimbitse n'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bwa hagati ku baturage 100,000 mu 201011).
Imiterere y'ibitegurwa ijyanye no guhaza ubushobozi bwo kwita ku buzima, hamwe n'ibaruramari kuri buri gihugu cya EU / EEA na UK by'ubwiyongere bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari mu bitaro bifitanye isano na &gt; 90% y'ibyago byo kurenga ubushobozi bw'ibitanda byitabwaho cyane, byatanzwe mu ihererekanywa rya gatandatu ry'icyerekezo cyihuse cy'ibyago cya ECDC kuri COVID-19.
Kubera ko kugeza ubu abantu banduye bakunze kwibasirwa n'uburwayi mu turere tumwe na tumwe two mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe bikunze gukorera abaturage bo mu karere runaka, amakuru ajyanye n'abantu banduye n'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe, byaba byiza byatanzwe ku rwego rwa Nomenclature of territorial units for statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Ibyaranze Ubutaliyani n'imiterere iriho mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kirimo kugenda gihinduka vuba mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibyumba byita ku barwayi bakomeye rero bigomba kwitegura uko bizagenda mu gihe SARS-CoV-2 izakwirakwira mu baturage kandi umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho, cyane cyane ku barwayi bakomeye, nk'uko bigenda mu turere twugarijwe n'iki cyorezo mu Butaliyani.
Nkuko byagaragajwe mu bushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa na ECDC, uburyo bwihuse, bwigenga kandi burambuye ni ngombwa kugira ngo umuntu atinda gukwirakwira kwa SARS-COV-2, aho guhera ku buryo bwo kwirinda ngo agere ku buryo bwo kugabanya ubwandu, kuko kwiyongera byihuse kw'umubare w'abandura bishobora kudahesha abafata ibyemezo n'ibitaro igihe gihagije cyo gusobanukirwa, kwemera no guhindura uko babyifatamo mu gihe bidashyizweho mu bikorwa hakiri kare.
Igenzura ry'ibyago byihuse ririmo kandi urutonde rw'ingamba zo kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo ku buzima bw'abaturage.
Hari umwanya muto w'amahirwe mu gihe ibihugu bifite amahirwe yo kongera imbaraga mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya igitutu ku buzima.
Iyo bitabaye ibyo, birashoboka ko sisitemu z'ubuvuzi z'ibindi bihugu bya EU / EEA zizagerwaho n'ubwiyongere bw'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe na severe acute respiratory syndrome (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kugeza ubu kimaze kwica abantu barenga 3,000 no kwandura abarenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, bigatuma abantu bagerwaho n'amakuba.
Kimwe na virusi ihwanye nayo, SARS-CoV, yateje SARS mu bihumbi by'abantu mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 nayo ishobora kwandura mu nyamaswa kandi igatera ibimenyetso nk'ibyo binyuze mu buryo nk'ubwo.
Icyakora, COVID-19 ifite ubukana buciriritse kandi buciriritse ugereranyije na SARS ariko irandura cyane kandi igera ku bantu bakuru benshi kurusha urubyiruko no ku bagabo benshi kurusha abagore.
