Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bikeneye ibisubizo, twizeye ko iyi ngingo izadufasha gusobanukirwa no kurandura iyo ndwara iteye ubwoba.
Umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi wo ku wa 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye urwibutso rutazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose basabwe kuguma mu ngo zabo muri iyi minsi mikuru yose ndetse no mu byumweru byinshi nyuma yaho kubera icyorezo cy'indwara nshya y'ubwandu.
Iyi virusi imeze kimwe cyane na coronavirus (CoV) yateje icyorezo cy'indwara ikomeye yo guhumeka (SARS) mu 2003; bityo, yiswe SARS-CoV-2 n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, kandi indwara ifitanye isano n'iyo yitwa CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, maze gikwira mu gihugu cyose mu buryo bwihuse, kigera no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi hose.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi imaze gutuma haboneka abantu barenga 80,000 banduye COVID-19, abasaga 40,000 barirukanywe ndetse abasaga 3,000 barapfuye.
OMS iraburira ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi wa rubanda wa 1" kandi ko ishobora kuba ikomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) ibivuga, mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, hamaze gutangwa inyandiko zirenga 200 ku bijyanye na COVID-19 harimo n'ubushakashatsi ku mikorobe, indwara z'ibyorezo, impamvu z'indwara, gupima no kuvura kuva raporo ya mbere yo ku wa 7 Mutarama 2020 yagaragazaga urutonde rwa virusi yavanywe mu barwayi benshi.
Iyi raporo igerageza gusobanura mu magambo make uko ubushakashatsi buhagaze muri iki kibazo gishya kandi kigenda gihinduka vuba.
Aho bishoboka, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara yatewe na CoV, Middle East respiratory syndrome (MERS, icyorezo cyabaye mu mwaka wa 2012).
Nanone kandi, turi busuzume ibyo tumaze kumenya ku birebana no kwirinda iyo ndwara no kumenya uko izaba imeze, ndetse turi busuzume n'ibibazo bimwe na bimwe bikomeje kuba ngombwa.
CoVs zagiye zibonwa nk'indwara zitera abantu uburwayi, ahanini zitera 15% by'indwara zisanzwe ziterwa n'ubukonje 4.
Ariko muri iki kinyejana, twahuye na CoV z'abantu ziterwa n'indwara nyinshi inshuro ebyiri, ni ukuvuga SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, byateje icyorezo mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, nyuma yaho bidatinze bikwira mu bindi bihugu byinshi bifite uburwayi n'urupfu biteye ubwoba.
Ku bw'ibyo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya CoV mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragara ku ishusho ya 1,1, amatsinda y'indwara y'ibicurane yari ifite inkomoko itazwi, yavuzwe bwa mbere i Wuhan ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kuri Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima y'Ubushinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, urutonde rwa CoV rwarasohotse.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020 nibwo habonetse umuntu wa mbere wahitanywe n'iyi ndwara i Wuhan.
Hagati aho, icyo cyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu migi, mu ntara no mu bihugu by'ibituranyi.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama, havuzwe ko abashinzwe ubuzima banduye, ibyo bikaba byumvikanisha ko umuntu ashobora kwandura undi muntu.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan wafunzwe, imodoka zose za Leta zihagarara.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere ku ndwara bwagaragaje ko, ku barwayi 41 bafite ubwandu bwahamijwe, 21 gusa ari bo bagiranye isano ya bugufi n'isoko ry'ibyokurya byo mu nyanja rya Wuhan byafatwaga nk'ahantu hatangiriye ubwandu buturutse ku nyamaswa zitazwi.
Ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko icyo cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubukungu cyugarije isi yose.
