Ku bw'ibyo, kugira ngo umuntu ashobore gusuzuma neza indwara, ni ngombwa ko asuzuma uko yari yarayirwaye, uko yagaragaye, ibyo yakoze mu mavuriro n'ibyavumbuwe mu byuma by'imikorere y'ubushakashatsi bw'ibinyabuzima.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda rya Feng Zhang ryasobanuye porotokaramu yo gukoresha uburyo bwa SHERLOCK bushingiye kuri CRISPR mu kumenya SARS-CoV-2, igaragaza ibice bya SARS-CoV-2 bya RNA by'imiterere kuri 20 × 10-18 mol/L kugeza kuri 200 × 10-18 mol/L (10-100 copies kuri microliter y'ibyinjira) hakoreshejwe inkoni mu gihe kitarenze isaha nta bikoresho byimbitse bikenewe.
Twizeye ko ubwo buryo bushya bushobora kongera cyane ubushobozi bwo kumenya ibintu n'uburyo bwo kubikora, mu gihe byaba byemejwe mu bipimo byo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi.
Kubera kubura ubunararibonye mu bijyanye na CoV nshya, abaganga bashobora ahanini gufasha abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu gihe bagerageza uburyo butandukanye bwo kuvura bwakoreshejwe cyangwa bwatanzwe mbere yo kuvura izindi CoV nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV n'izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi (Igishushanyo (Igishushanyo cya 2).2).
Ubu buryo bwo kuvura burimo gukorwa ubu n'ubu bushobora gukorwa, harimo imiti igabanya ubukana bwa virusi, imiti ituma umuntu adakomeza kugira ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri, imiti yitwa steroïde, plasma y'abarwayi bakize, imiti y'Abashinwa no kubafasha mu by'imitekerereze.
Ndetse na plasma y'abarwayi bakize yasabwe gukoreshwa mu kuvura.
Ibigo bikora imiti birimo birwanira gukora uduhimba tw'umubiri n'inkingo zo kurwanya virusi.
SARS-CoV-2 yibasira cyane cyane ibihaha mu ntangiriro kandi birashoboka ko yibasira, mu rugero ruto, izindi ngingo zigaragaza ACE2, nk'uruhu n'impyiko.
Nyamara, ikibazo gikomeye ku barwayi n'impamvu y'ibanze y'urupfu, ni ikibazo cyo guhumeka nabi no kunanirwa guhumeka.
Bityo rero, ubufasha bwo guhumeka ni ingenzi mu kugabanya ibimenyetso no kurokora ubuzima kandi burimo imiti yo guhumeka, umwuka wo guhumeka wihuta, guhumeka udakoresha umwuka usanzwe, no guhumeka ukoresheje imashini bivanze n'uburemere bw'indwara.
Abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso bikomeye byo guhumeka bagomba gushyigikirwa na oxygenation ya membrane extracorporeal (ECMO), uburyo bwo guhindura umutima ukongera umwuka ukoreshwa mu kuvura umutima cyangwa guhumeka bishobora gushyira ubuzima mu kaga.
Byongeye kandi, kubungabunga uburinganire bw'amashanyarazi, gukumira no kuvura indwara z'ibanze n'imihangayiko y'ubwandu, no kurinda imikorere y'ingingo z'ingenzi na byo ni ngombwa ku barwayi ba SARS-CoV-2.
Byari bizwi ko cytocin storm iterwa no guhugira cyane kw'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri mu barwayi ba SARS na MERS.
Cytokine storm ni uburyo bwo gusubiza kw'ubuhumekero bwa sisitemu buvugwaho kurekura urukurikirane rw'ibikomoka kuri cytokine harimo TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ na MCP-1.
Izi cytokine zituma ingirabuzimafatizo z'ubwirinzi zifungura umubare munini w'ibinyabuzima by'ubwigenge ari byo ahanini bitera ARDS n'ibindi byatuma ingingo z'umubiri zidakora neza.
Immunosuppression ni ingenzi mu kuvura cytocin storms, cyane cyane mu barwayi bafite ibibazo bikomeye.
Corticosteroids na tocilizumab, umuti urwanya IL6 wa monoclonal, byakoreshejwe mu kuvura cytocin storm.
Ubundi buvuzi bwo kurwanya immunosuppression ku cyorezo cy'imiti yitwa cytokine harimo uburyo bwo guhindura imyitwarire y'umubiri igengwa n'ingirabuzimafatizo ya T; kubuza IFN-γ, IL-1, na TNF; kubuza JAK; blinatumomab; kubuza cytocin gutanga ibimenyetso 4; na HDAC inhibitors.
Steroids, nk'imiti yo kurwanya indwara, yakoreshejwe cyane mu kuvura SARS mu kugabanya ubukana bw'ingaruka z'uburwayi.
Icyakora, imiti ya Steroids mu rugero rwo hejuru ntiyagize akamaro ku barwayi ba SARS na COVID-19 bafite ibikomere bikomeye by'ibihaha.
Ahubwo, bishobora guteza ingaruka zikomeye, cyane cyane indwara yo mu ngingo z'amagufa, bigatuma umuntu atabona neza uko azabyitwaramo.
Nyamara, ingamba ngufi za kortikosteroide mu miti yo hasi kugeza ku miti yo mu rwego rwo hejuru zasabwe gukoreshwa mu bwitonzi ku barwayi ba COVID-19 barwaye cyane.
Kugeza ubu nta muti wa virusi wemeza ko ugira ingaruka nziza.
Icyakora, guterwa umuti mu mitsi na remdesivir, ikoranabuhanga rya nucleotide, byagaragaye ko ari ingirakamaro ku murwayi wo muri Amerika urwaye COVID-19.
Remdesivir ni umuti mushya urwanya virusi watangijwe na Gilead mu buryo bw'ibanze mu kuvura indwara ziterwa na Ebola na Marlburg.
Nyuma yaho, remdesivir yagaragaje ko ishobora kubuza izindi virusi z'ubwoko bumwe za RNA zirimo MERS na SARS.
Ishingiye kuri ibi, Gilead yatanze uyu muti mu Bushinwa kugira ngo ukorerwe ibizamini bibiri ku bantu banduye SARS-CoV-2, kandi ibizava mu igerageza birategerejwe cyane.
Byongeye kandi, baricitinb, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir, na ribavirin byasabwe nk'uburyo bushobora gukoreshwa mu kuvura abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero.
Gucika imyanya y'umubiri, kugira uburwayi, kuruka, kwangirika kw'impyiko, n'izindi ngaruka mbi bishobora kubaho nyuma yo gufatwa hamwe na lopinavir/ritonavir.
Imikorere y'iyi miti hamwe n'indi miti ikoreshwa ku barwayi igomba kugenzurwa neza.
Plasma y'abarwayi bakize n'igiteranyo cy'umubiri wa antikorupiyo
Gukusanya amaraso y'abarwayi bakize indwara yandura kugira ngo bavurwe n'abandi barwayi barwaye iyo ndwara cyangwa kugira ngo abantu bafite amagara mazima badakwirakwizwa iyo ndwara, bimaze igihe kirekire.
Koko rero, abarwayi bakize akenshi baba bafite intanga ngabo nyinshi mu maraso yabo zirwanya icyo cyorezo.
Abatabazi ni immunoglobulin (Ig) ikorwa na B lymphocytes mu kurwanya udukoko dutera indwara n'ibindi bintu by'amahanga kandi bamenya molekile zidasanzwe muri utwo dukoko kandi tukazica mu buryo butaziguye.
Hashingiwe kuri ibi, plasma yakusanyijwe mu maraso y'itsinda ry'abarwayi bakize COVID-19 maze ishyirwa mu miti ku barwayi 10 barwaye cyane.
Ibimenyetso byabo byagiye birushaho kuba byiza mu masaha 24, biherekejwe no kugabanuka kw'uburwayi n'ubwandu bwa virusi ndetse no kongera umwuka wa ogisijeni mu maraso.
Icyakora, kugira ngo uburyo bukoreshwe ku rugero rwagutse mbere y'uko habaho uburyo bwihariye bwo kuvura, hagomba gukorwa igenzura no gusobanura.
Byongeye kandi, bitewe n'ingaruka z'ubuvuzi, hari ibyago bimwe na bimwe bifitanye isano na plasma bigomba gusuzumwa neza.
Urugero, uduhimba tw'umubiri dushobora gutuma umubiri udashobora kurwanya indwara, bigatuma habaho indwara yo kurekura sitokine, ishobora gutuma umuntu apfa.
Ubusanzwe, amaraso aba afite ibice bike by'umubiri bigwanya iyo ndwara, kandi abarwayi barwaye indwara ikomeye baba bakeneye cyane amaraso ari mu gipimo cyo hejuru.
Biragoye gukora no gukora udukoko tw'ubwirinzi bwihariye mu buryo bwihuse bihagije kugira ngo turwanye icyorezo cyugarije isi yose.
Niyo mpamvu ari ngombwa cyane kandi byoroshye gutandukanya uturemangingo twa B mu barwayi bakize no kumenya kode z'imiterere y'umubiri zigena udukoko tw'umubiri tw'ingenzi cyangwa kureba udukoko tw'umubiri tw'ingenzi turwanya poroteyine z'ubwandu.
Muri ubwo buryo, dushobora kongera ingano y'abakoraho.
Mu Bushinwa, TCM yagiye ikoreshwa mu kuvura indwara zitandukanye mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi.
Icyakora, ingaruka zayo ahanini zishingiye ku guhuza ibice byinshi mu buryo butandukanye bitewe n'indwara iherekejwe n'ibitekerezo bya TCM.
Ibyinshi mu bice by'ingenzi bigize uwo muti biracyari ibitazwi cyangwa ntibiramenyekana neza, kubera ko bigoye kubisobanura no kugenzura ibyo bice cyangwa amahuza yabyo meza.
Muri iki gihe, kubera kubura ubuvuzi bwikora kandi bwihariye bwa COVID-19, TCM yabaye imwe mu miti y'ubundi buryo ikomeye ku barwayi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje kugeza ku bito cyangwa ku bantu bakize mu byiciro bikomeye.
Urugero, Shu Feng Jie Du capsules na Lian Hua Qing Wen capsules byagaragaye ko ari ingirakamaro mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ibipimo byo gukira cyane mu kuvura abarwayi ba COVID-19 byagaragariye mu ntara nyinshi zo mu Bushinwa zakoresheje TCM mu barwayi 87% barimo Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%), na Hunan (50%), mu gihe intara ya Hubei, yakoresheje TCM mu barwayi ba COVID-19 bagera kuri 30% gusa, yari ifite igipimo cyo gukira kiri hasi (13%).
Icyakora, uyu ni ugereranya gusa kuko hari ibindi bintu byinshi bigira ingaruka nko umubare n'uburemere bw'abarwayi bigomba gushyirwa mu igenzura.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Boli Zhang na bagenzi be basohoye ubushakashatsi bugereranya imiti y'uburengerazuba (WM) yonyine hamwe n'ubuvuzi buhuriweho bwa WM na TCM.
Basanze igihe cyo kugarura ubushyuhe bw'umubiri, kwibagirwa ibimenyetso no kujya mu bitaro ari gito cyane mu itsinda ryahawe WM+TCM ugereranyije n'itsinda ryahawe WM gusa.
Igitangaje cyane, ni uko umubare w'ibimenyetso by'indwara byunyuka (kuva ku byoroheje kugeza ku bikomeye) wari hasi cyane mu itsinda rya WM+TCM ugereranyije n'itsinda rya WM gusa (7,4% ugereranyije na 46,2%) kandi urupfu rwari hasi mu itsinda rya WM+TCM ugereranyije n'itsinda rya WM gusa (8,8% ugereranyije na 39%).
Icyakora, kugira ngo umuti wa TCM ukore neza kandi utume udakomeretsa, hagomba gukorwa ibindi bigeragezo by'ingirakamaro kandi bigenzurwa neza, bigakorwa mu rwego rwagutse no mu bigo byinshi.
Nanone kandi, byaba bishishikaje kumenya imikorere y'imikorere yayo no gusobanura neza ibice bigize uburyo bwo kuvura bwa TCM cyangwa se uko byahurizwa hamwe.
Abarwayi bakekwaho cyangwa bemejwe ko barwaye COVID-19 akenshi bagira ubwoba bwinshi bw'indwara yandura cyane ndetse ikabahitana, kandi abantu bari mu kato nabo bagira umunaniro, irungu n'uburakari.
Byongeye kandi, ibimenyetso by'ubwandu nk'ibicurane, hypoxia, no guhohoterwa, kimwe n'ingaruka mbi z'ubuvuzi nk'ibitotsi biterwa na korticosteroids, bishobora gutuma umuntu arushaho guhangayika no guhangayika mu bwenge.
Mu ntangiriro y'icyorezo cya SARS, havuzwe ibyorezo bitandukanye byo mu mutwe birimo kwiheba, guhangayika, guhungabana, gushyushya umutima, ibimenyetso by'indwara zo mu mutwe, gutenguhuka ndetse no kwiyahura.
Gukurikirana abantu bahuye n'ubwandu no kubabuza kujya mu kato, nk'igice cy'uburyo bwo kuvura COVID-19, bishobora gutuma abantu barushaho guhangayika no kwicira urubanza ku ngaruka z'ubwandu, kubabuza kujya mu kato, no gusebanya ku miryango yabo n'inshuti zabo.
Bityo, kwita ku buzima bwo mu mutwe bigomba gutangwa ku barwayi ba COVID-19, abantu bakekwaho, n'abantu bahuye na bo kimwe n'abaturage muri rusange bakeneye ubufasha.
Ubufasha mu by'imitekerereze bugomba kuba burimo gushyiraho amatsinda y'abakora mu by'ubuzima bwo mu mutwe, itumanaho risobanutse neza rifite amakuru ahoraho kandi y'ukuri ku cyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 n'imigambi yo kuvurwa no gukoresha ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki by'umwuga n'ibikoresho byo gukorana kugirango wirinde guhura cyane.
Inkingo z'ingirakamaro ni ngombwa mu guhagarika umurongo w'ikwirakwizwa kuva ku nyamaswa z'ibanze n'abantu banduye kugera ku batware bashobora kuvurwa, kandi akenshi zirimo gukoreshwa mu kurwanya indwara ziterwa na virusi nshya.
Hakozwe imbaraga zo gukora inkingo zishingiye kuri poroteyine ya S kugira ngo haboneke udukoko tw'ubwirinzi tw'igihe kirekire kandi dufite imbaraga kandi tubangamira SARS-CoV.
Inkingo z'ubuzima zaragabanutse zasuzumwe ku bikoresho by'inyamaswa bya SARS.
Icyakora, mbere yo gutangira igerageza ry'ubuvuzi, nta kindi kimenyekanye ku birebana n'ubushobozi bw'izo nkingo mu bantu bageze mu za bukuru n'izitera indwara z'ubwandu bw'ibinyabuzima, ndetse n'ubwirinzi bwazo ku ndwara ziterwa na virusi z'ibinyabuzima.
Ibi bishobora kuba biterwa n'uko SARS yazimye mu myaka 17 ishize kandi kuva icyo gihe nta muntu mushya wongeye kwandura.
Ku rundi ruhande, abantu batandukanye n'amatsinda ya MERS bakomeje kugaragara mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, kandi bakwirakwira mu tundi turere bitewe n'uko inyamaswa z'ibinyamanswa zikomeje kugaragara mu turere dufite indwara z'ubwandu.
Hateguwe uburyo bwo gukingira MERS hakoreshejwe virusi itariho, plasmide ya ADN, imikorere ya virusi, nanoparticles, ibice bisa na virusi na poroteyine zisanzwe kandi bimwe byasuzumwe ku bikoresho by'inyamaswa.
Gutegura urukingo rukomeye kandi rukomeye rwo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 ku bantu badafite ubushobozi bwo kwirinda ni igikorwa cyihutirwa kandi cy'ingenzi mu kugenzura icyorezo gikomeje.
Icyakora, biragoye kunesha ibyo bibazo bitewe n'igihe kirekire (kimwe n'amezi 18) gikenewe mu gukora urukingo n'ubundi buryo bwo guhinduka kw'imiterere y'imikorere ya CoV.
Nk'indwara nshya, COVID-19 itangiye kugaragaza uburyo bwayo bwose mu barwayi babarirwa mu bihumbi.
Mu bihe byinshi, abarwayi bashobora gukira buhoro buhoro nta ngaruka z'ingaruka.
Icyakora, kimwe na SARS na MERS, COVID-19 nayo ifitanye isano no kurwara cyane no gupfa mu barwayi bafite ibibazo bikomeye.
Ku bw'ibyo, kubaka uburyo bwo kumenya uko indwara ishobora guhinduka ni iby'ingenzi kugira ngo inzego z'ubuvuzi zihe serivisi zazo umwanya wa mbere, cyane cyane mu turere dufite amikoro make.
Dushingiye ku bipimo by'ubuvuzi byatangajwe kugeza ubu, ibi bikurikira bishobora kugira ingaruka cyangwa bigaterwa n'ubushakashatsi bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 (Imbonerahamwe (Imbonerahamwe33):
Imyaka: Imyaka ni yo yari ingenzi cyane mu kumenya indwara ya SARS, kandi ni na ko bimeze kuri COVID-19.
COVID-19 yibonekeje cyane cyane ku bantu bafite imyaka 30-65 aho 47.7% by'abo barwayi bari hejuru y'imyaka 50 mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 8,866 nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru.
Abarwayi basabwaga kwitabwaho cyane bari bafite ibyago byinshi byo kugira indwara zihuriyeho n'izindi n'ibibazo kandi bari bakuze cyane kurusha abatabifite (ku myaka 66 kuri 51), ibyo bikaba byerekana ko imyaka ari yo igena uko abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazagenda.
Igitsina: SARS-CoV-2 imaze kwandura abagabo benshi kurusha abagore (0.31/100,000 ugereranyije na 0.27/100,000), nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru.
Indwara zihurizwa hamwe n'impamvu: Abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane baba bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara umutima cyane no kugira ikibazo cyo kudahosha kw'umuriro.
Ibyago by'umutima nabyo byari impamvu y'ibanze y'urupfu mu barwayi ba SARS.
Hari amakuru avuga ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no guhuza na cholangiocytes ifite ACE2, ibyo bikaba bishobora gutuma umurwayi wa COVID-19 agira ikibazo cy'ubuhumekero.
Ni iby'ingenzi kumenya ko imyaka n'indwara umuntu arwaye bifitanye isano rya bugufi, kandi ko bishobora kugira ingaruka ku muntu.
Ibyavuye mu bipimo byo mu mavuriro: Umubare w'urumuri C-reactive (CRP) mu maraso ugaragaza uburemere bw'ubwugarizi cyangwa imvune y'uruhu, kandi byavuzwe ko bishobora kuba ari byo bihamya indwara, uko umuntu yitabira ubuvuzi, n'uko nyuma y'igihe ashobora gukira.
Hari kandi igitekerezo cyo guhuza urugero rwa CRP n'uburemere bwa COVID-19 n'uburyo ishobora gukira.
Byongeye kandi, kongera lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), alanine aminotransferase (ALT), na creatine kinase (CK) nabyo bishobora gufasha mu guhanura ibisubizo.
Izi enzymes zishyirwa mu bice byinshi by'umubiri, cyane cyane mu mutima no mu gifu, kandi zirekurwa mu gihe hari ibikomere by'imikorere y'umubiri.
Ku bw'ibyo, ni ibimenyetso bisanzwe bigaragaza ko umuntu afite ibibazo by'umutima cyangwa by'umura.
Ibimenyetso by'ingenzi by'uburwayi: Radiographie y'igituza n'iterambere ry'ibipimo by'uburwayi bigomba gusuzumwa hamwe n'ibindi bibazo byo guhanura ingaruka n'impungenge za COVID-19.
Gukoresha imiti ya Steroide: Nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, imiti ya Steroide ni imiti yo kurwanya indwara zandura ikoreshwa mu buvuzi bw'indwara zandura kugira ngo igabanye ubukana bw'ibikomere by'uburwayi.
Kubera ko ingano yo hejuru ya kortikosteroide yakoreshejwe cyane mu barwayi ba SARS ikomeye, abenshi mu barokotse barwaye avascular osteonecrosis bafite ubumuga bw'ubuzima bwose n'ubuzima bubi.
Bityo, niba ari ngombwa, steroid zigomba gukoreshwa mu minini kandi mu gihe gito ku barwayi ba COVID-19.
Ihangane ryo mu mutwe: Nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19, abarwayi benshi bagize imihangayiko idasanzwe kuko akenshi bihanganiraga igihe kirekire cyo kwigunga no kutagira icyizere kandi babonaga urupfu rw'abagize umuryango wabo ba bugufi na bagenzi babo barwaye.
Ni ngombwa gutanga inama z'imitekerereze n'ubufasha burambye kugira ngo aba barwayi bakire stress no gusubira mu buzima busanzwe.
Nk'uko ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu kugeza ubu, COVID-19 isa n'aho ifite ibintu bitandukanye n'ibya SARS.
Usibye kwiyongera mu bice by'ubuhumekero, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwiyongera mu bice by'ubuhumekero byo hejuru kandi igatera ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa nta bimenyetso mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubwandu, bisa n'ibindi CoV bitera imbeho isanzwe.
Ku bw'ibyo, abarwayi banduye mu gihe cy'icyiciro cya mbere cyangwa igihe cyo kuboneza urubyaro bashobora gukora virusi nyinshi mu gihe cy'ibikorwa bya buri munsi, bigatuma bigora cyane kugenzura icyorezo.
Icyakora, kwanduzwa kwa SARS-CoV byafashwe nk'aho bibaho iyo abarwayi barwaye cyane, mu gihe kwanduzwa kwinshi kutaba mu cyiciro cya mbere.
Bityo, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiriho ubu kirakomeye cyane kandi biragoye kugenzura kurusha icyorezo cya SARS.
Muri iki gihe, mu Bushinwa hari ibikorwa bikomeye birimo gukingirwa Wuhan n'imijyi ihakikije no gukomeza gushyira abantu mu kato hafi ya bose mu byiringiro byo guhagarika ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2.
Nubwo ibyo bikorwa byangije cyane ubukungu n'ibindi bice by'igihugu, umubare w'abarwayi bashya urimo uragabanuka, bigaragaza ko icyorezo cyagabanutse.
Ubushakashatsi bwemeza ko iki cyorezo kizarangira muri Werurwe, kandi ko icyiciro cyo kugabanuka kizamara amezi 3-4.
Icyakora, hari abandi bahanga batagira icyizere nk'icyo.
Paul Hunter, et al., bagereranyije ko COVID-19, isa n'iyandura cyane kurusha SARS, itazarangira mu 2020.
Ira Longini, et al., yashyizeho uburyo bwo guhanura ingaruka z'icyorezo kandi avuga ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura bibiri bya gatatu by'abatuye isi.
Itsinda ryo muri Canada ryatangaje ko SARS-CoV-2 yagaragaye mu bipimo byo hagati mu muhogo no mu muhogo by'abarwayi bakize bagasiga ibitaro mu byumweru bibiri mbere, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko virusi iherutse kumenyekana ishobora guhinduka icyorezo gisa n'icy'ibicurane.
Icyakora, ibimenyetso by'ibyiringiro byagaragariye mu Bushinwa bishingiye ku kubura umubare w'abanduye bashya, bigaragaza ko ingamba ziriho ubu zishobora kuba zaragize icyo zigeraho.
Mu mizo ya mbere, byari byarahanuwe ko Ebola yari kuzandura abantu bagera kuri miriyoni imwe, ikahitana abantu bagera kuri miriyoni magana atanu.
Icyakora, binyuze mu gushyira abantu mu kato no kubabuza kujya mu bindi bihugu, amaherezo indwara yaje kugenzurwa.
Birashoboka, kimwe na SARS-CoV, ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugabanuka mu kwandura kandi amaherezo ikaza gupfa cyangwa ikaba virusi idakwirakwiza indwara nyinshi ihuriyeho n'abantu.
Igereranya ry'icyorezo cya COVID-19 n'icya SARS na MERS ritangwa hasi (Igishushanyo (Igishushanyo cya 55).
