Uburyo bwa mbere bwo kwirwanaho bushobora gukoreshwa mu kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura ni ugutwara udupfukamunwa; gukoresha udupfukamunwa two kubaga n'udupfukamunwa two guhumeka N95 (urukurikirane # 1860s) bifasha kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu.
