Uretse udupfukamunwa, abaganga bagomba kwambara imyenda yo kwiherera kugira ngo barusheho kugabanya ubwandu bwa virusi.
Nanone virusi ishobora kwandura umuntu binyuze ku maso.
Ku ya 22 Mutarama 2020, umuganga yanduye SARS-CoV-2 nubwo yari yambaye agapfukamunwa ka N95; virusi ishobora kuba yarinjiye mu mubiri we binyuze mu maso ye yanduye.
Ku bw'ibyo, abaganga na bo bagombye kwambara udupfukamunwa cyangwa indorerwamo mu gihe bakorana n'abarwayi.
Ku baturage muri rusange mu turere twanduye cyangwa dushobora kwandura, birasabwa cyane ko buri wese yakwiyuhagira intoki n'isabune z'ubumara bwandura kenshi kurusha uko bisanzwe, kugerageza kuguma mu nzu kugira ngo yiyicunge kandi agabanya imikoranire n'abantu bashobora kwandura.
Abantu bashobora gutandukana n'umurwayi ku ntera imwe.
Izi ngamba ni uburyo bwiza bwo kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura no gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Nubwo SARS-CoV-2 yaje nk'ubwandu bushya ku isi y'abantu, kuba ifite imiterere ihwanye cyane na SARS-CoV nkuko byatangajwe ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020 byagombye kuba byaratumye Ubushinwa buhagarika cyane bitewe n'ibyibukwa byimbitse by'icyorezo cya SARS mu 2003.
Icyakora, kugeza tariki ya 19 Mutarama 2020 ni bwo umuyobozi w'Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura indwara cya Wuhan yahumurije abaturage avuga ko virusi nshya ifite ubwandu buke kandi ko ishobora kubyara ku bantu gusa kandi ko kwirinda no gukumira iyi ndwara atari ikibazo.
Ubu butumwa bworoheje cyane abantu, cyane cyane igihe igihugu cyose cyiteguraga Umunsi Mukuru w'Imvura, kandi igihe gikomeye cyo gukumira iyi ndwara ku kigero gito cyane muri Wuhan cyarapfuye.
Inzego zishinzwe kurwanya indwara zo mu Bushinwa zishobora kuvana isomo kuri ibyo bintu bikomeye maze zikagira ibyo zinonosora mu gihe kizaza.
Urugero, izo nzego zagombye (1) kuba zirushaho kwitonda mu gihe zitangaza ku mugaragaro kuko buri jambo ryose rifite agaciro ku baturage kandi rishobora guhindura imyifatire yabo n'imyanzuro yabo; (2) kurushaho kwita ku makuru adasanzwe aturuka mu bigo by'ubuvuzi aho gutegereza raporo z'abaganga cyangwa abayobozi; (3) kurushaho gushyiraho imipaka mu guhashya icyorezo gishobora kwaduka mu gihe kiri mu cyiciro cyacyo cya mbere aho kugerageza guhumuriza abaturage; (4) kurushaho gutanga imyitozo igamije kandi ikora ku buryo bw'ibanze kugira ngo abaturage barusheho kumenya iby'indwara ziterwa n'ibyorezo no kugerageza no kunoza uburyo bwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo mu rwego rw'umuryango.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatewe na virusi nshya ya SARS-CoV-2 cyatangiye mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019.
Mu gihe kitageze ku mezi abiri, imaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa hose no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi hose mu gihe twandika iyi nkuru.
Kubera ko virusi isa cyane na SARS-CoV kandi ibimenyetso na byo bisa hagati ya COVID-19 na SARS, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatumye habaho kumva ko SARS yongeye kugaruka.
Icyakora, hari itandukaniro rikomeye hagati ya COVID-19 na SARS, ari ngombwa mu gukumira icyorezo no kuvura abarwayi.
COVID-19 yibasira abantu bakuze kurusha urubyiruko, abagabo benshi kurusha abagore, kandi ubukana n'umubare w'abapfa nabyo biri hejuru mu bantu bakuze kurusha urubyiruko.
SARS ifite igipimo cyo hejuru cy'abapfa kurusha COVID-19 (10.91% kuri 1.44%).
Abarwayi ba COVID-19 batandukana virusi n'ubwo baba badafite ibimenyetso mu gihe abarwayi ba SARS babikora iyo barwaye cyane, ibyo bigatuma gukwirakwira kwa COVID-19 bigorana cyane kuruta SARS.
Ibi bisobanura mu rugero runaka impamvu SARS-CoV-2 ikwirakwira cyane kandi mu buryo bwagutse kurusha SARS-CoV.
Iperereza rya RNA isanzwe ya SARS-CoV-2 rishobora kuba ridakira mu barwayi bamwe na bamwe ba COVID-19.
Ku rundi ruhande, abarwayi bakize bashobora kongera kugaragaza ko banduye.
Ibi byatangajwe byongera cyane ibyago byo gukwirakwiza virusi.
Bitewe n'iterambere rihuta mu bushakashatsi kuri COVID-19, ibibazo byinshi bikomeye biracyakemurwa, bikurikira:
SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse he?
Nubwo 96% by'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima by'ubwoko bumwe byabonetse hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na CoV ebyiri zisa na SARS z'imbeba, ntiturashobora kugera ku mwanzuro w'uko SARS-CoV-2 ituruka ku myamba.
Ni ikihe gikoko cya mbere cyageze kuri virusi, ikava ku muntu wa mbere, ni ukuvuga umukangara?
Iyo tutazi ibisubizo by'ibibazo bya mbere n'ibya kabiri, ntidushobora guhagarika ku buryo bw'ingirakamaro ikwirakwira ry'iyo ndwara, kandi ishobora kongera kwaduka igihe icyo ari cyo cyose.
Nubwo ingamba zo gukora imiterere ya molekile n'ibipimo bya biochimique byagaragaje ko SARS-CoV-2 ifata ACE2, ni gute virusi yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo zo mu muyoboro w'ubuhumekero igateza impinduka zikurikiraho mu byerekeye indwara?
Ese iyo virusi ishobora no guhuza ingirabuzimafatizo z'izindi ngingo?
Iyo tutabonye ibisubizo byumvikana by'ibyo bibazo, ntidushobora kumenya uko umuntu ahita avurwa cyangwa ngo tumenye uko twavura umuntu.
Iyo ndwara izamara igihe kingana iki?
Ni gute virusi ikura mu buryo bw'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima mu gihe ikwirakwira mu bantu?
Mbese, kizaba icyorezo ku isi hose, kigacika nka SARS cyangwa kigasubira mu buryo nk'ubw'ibicurane?
Ni ngombwa ariko bishobora gufata igihe runaka kugira ngo ushakishe ibisubizo by'ibyo bibazo byavuzwe haruguru n'ibindi byinshi.
Icyakora, uko amafaranga yaba angana kose, nta kundi twabigenza uretse guhagarika iki cyorezo vuba uko bishoboka kose, maze ubuzima bwacu bugasubira mu buryo busanzwe.
Inkomoko ya zoonotic ya virusi ya corona y'umuntu
Guhinduka no guhuza ibintu byateye ko virusi ya corona (CoV) n'abayirimo, harimo n'abantu, bihura mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi.
Mbere ya 2003, abantu babiri bafatwaga nk'inzoka (HCoVs) bari bazwiho gutera indwara zidakomeye, urugero nk'ibicurane.
Ibimenyetso by'indwara y'ubuhumekero bw'ibicurane (SARS) n'indwara y'ubuhumekero bw'ibura ry'umuriro (MERS) byahinduye isura y'icyuma kugira ngo bigaragaze ukuntu ubwandu bwa HCoV bushobora kuba bubi cyane kandi bugateza akaga ubuzima.
Igitaramo cya SARS-CoV-2 mu Bushinwa hagati mu mpera za 2019 cyongeye gushyira CoVs mu ruhame kandi cyadutangaje kubera uburyo butandukanye ikwirakwira ariko ikaba ifite ubukana buke ugereranyije na SARS-CoV mwene nyina.
Uwandu bwa HCoV ni indwara y'ibinyabuzima kandi gusobanukirwa inkomoko y'ibinyabuzima bya HCoVs byadufasha cyane.
HCoVs nyinshi zituruka ku mbogo aho zitandura.
Ibigo by'abaturanyi b'abashakanye bya bamwe mu ba HCoVs nabyo birazwi.
Kumenya inyamaswa zitera indwara bigira ingaruka mu buryo butaziguye mu gukumira indwara z'abantu.
Gusuzuma imikoranire ya CoV-host mu nyamaswa bishobora no gutanga ibisobanuro by'ingenzi ku bijyanye na CoV pathogenesis mu bantu.
Muri iyi nkuru, turatanga isesengura ry'ubumenyi buriho ku byerekeye HCoVs ndwi, twibanda ku mateka y'ibyavumbuwe hamwe n'inkomoko yazo zoonotic no gukwirakwiza ubwoko.
Icy'ingenzi, turagereranya kandi tugashya HCoVs zitandukanye dukurikije iterambere rya virusi no kongera guhuriza hamwe genome.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cy'ubu kiri kuganirwaho muri iyi nkuru.
Byongeye kandi, ibisabwa kugira ngo haboneke impinduka nziza mu gutwara abantu n'ingaruka z'ihindagurika ry'ubwandu ku buremere bw'indwara nabyo byashimangiwe.
Coronaviruses (CoVs) ni zo mu muryango wa Coronaviridae, ugizwe n'itsinda ry'indwara z'ubwoko bumwe z'ubwoko bumwe za RNA zifite uruhu rumwe, zifite ibimenyetso by'uko zitandura.
Izi virusi zifite genom nini cyane iri hagati ya 26 na 32 kilobases mu virusi za RNA byiswe CoVs kubera imiterere isa n'ikamba mu kigereranyo cya mikorosikopi ya elegitoroniki.
Mu buryo bw'ibanze, CoV zifite genomes zitagira ibice zigira urwego rumwe.
Hafi bibiri bya gatatu bya genome birimo ibice bibiri binini by'ibisobanuro by'ibisobanuro (ORF1a na ORF1b), bihindurwa mu poroteyine za pp1a na pp1ab.
Polyproteins zikomeza gutunganywa kugira ngo ziterwe poroteyine 16 zitagira imiterere, zitwa nsp1~16.
Igice gisigaye cya genome kirimo ORFs z'ama poroteyine y'ibanze, harimo spike (S), enveloppe (E), membrane (M) na nucleoprotein (N).
Hariho poroteyine zinyuranye z'ibanze z'ubwoko runaka nazo zandikwa n'ubwoko butandukanye bwa CoV.
Hashingiwe ku itandukaniro riri mu mikoranire y'umushongi, CoVs zashyizwe mu miryango ine (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV na delta-CoV), muri yo beta-CoVs irimo HCoVs nyinshi kandi igabanyijemo imiryango ine (A, B, C na D).
Ibimenyetso byerekana ko inyamaswa z'ibinyamushongo n'iz'inguge ari zo zikomoka ku gitsina cy'abantu benshi bafite virusi ya alpha-CoV na beta-CoV, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zikomoka ku gitsina cy'abantu bafite virusi ya gamma-CoV na delta-CoV.
Mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi, CoVs zakomeje kunyura mu nzitizi z'amoko, kandi zimwe muri zo zagiye zigaragara nk'indwara z'ingenzi zitera indwara ku bantu.
Kugeza ubu, hamaze kumenyekana abantu barindwi bafite virusi ya CoV (HCoVs).
Muri byo HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63 ni alpha-CoVs.
Izindi beta-CoV eshanu zirimo HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, coronavirus y'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (SARS-CoV), coronavirus y'indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS-CoV) na SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63 ubusanzwe bitera ibimenyetso byoroheje, nk'ibicurane bisanzwe n'isukari.
Mu buryo bunyuranye, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 iherutse kumenyekana ni indwara ziterwa n'uburwayi, zitera indwara ikomeye yo mu nzira yo mu nda mu barwayi benshi bafite amahirwe menshi yo kugira indwara y'ubuhumekero (ARDS) no kugaragaza indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Ubwa mbere ubwoko bwa HCoV-229E, B814, bwavumbuwe mu byuka byaturukaga mu mazuru y'abarwayi bari barwaye indwara y'ibicurane hagati mu myaka ya za 60.
Kuva icyo gihe, ubumenyi bwinshi bwakozwe binyuze mu bushakashatsi bunini ku cyorezo cya HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, byombi bitera ibimenyetso byigenga.
Mu by'ukuri, igitekerezo cyakiriwe cyane ko ubwandu bwa HCoVs muri rusange nta cyo butwaye kugeza igihe SARS itangiriye.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyabaye mu 2003 ni kimwe mu byangije cyane mu mateka y'iki gihe, cyanduje abantu barenga 8.000 ku gipimo cy'abapfa kiri hafi 10%.
Imyaka icumi nyuma yaho, icyorezo cy'indwara ifata imyanya y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS), cyatumye habaho icyorezo gikomeje kwiyongera mu karere ka Arabiya, kigakwira hirya no hino ku isi.
HCoV nshya yo mu 2019 (2019-nCoV), yaje kwitwa SARS-CoV-2, ni yo iteza icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,120 no kwandura abantu barenga 91,000 kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020.
Umutekano urimo kugenda wiyongera kandi isi igomba kwitegura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kigiye kwaduka.
HCoVs zose uko ari ndwi zifite inkomoko ya zoonotic ituruka ku mbunda, imbeba cyangwa inyamaswa zo mu rugo.
Ibimenyetso byinshi bishyigikira inkomoko y'ihindagurika ya HCoVs zose zituruka ku bibugu, aho virusi zisanzwe zisanzwe kandi zidafite indwara ariko zigaragaza itandukaniro rinini ry'ibinyabuzima.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateye ibibazo bikomeye mu buvuzi, mu bya siyansi, mu by'imibereho n'umuco mu Bushinwa no ku isi.
Gukurikirana inkomoko ya zoonotic ya HCoVs bitanga urufatiro rwo gusobanukirwa amateka y'ibanze, imbaraga zituma ubwoko bujya hejuru n'ibintu bibubuza.
Ibi kandi bishobora kuyobora cyangwa koroshya ubushakashatsi ku byuma, hagati n'ibikomeza inyamaswa zitanga SARS-CoV-2, bigira ingaruka zikomeye mu gukumira gusakaza mu gihe kizaza.
Muri iyi nkuru, turatanga isesengura ry'inkomoko ya zoonotic, ikwirakwira hagati y'amoko n'imiterere y'indwara ziterwa na HCoVs.
By'umwihariko, turashyira ahagaragara kandi tukaganira ku ngingo rusange ivuga ko virusi z'ababyeyi za HCoVs ubusanzwe zidateza indwara mu barwayi bazirimo ariko zikaba ziteza indwara nyuma yo kwanduzwa hagati y'amoko ku murwayi mushya.
Nanone kandi, dusuzuma imiterere y'ihindagurika rya HCoV aho kwiyongera kw'ubwandu akenshi bijyana no kugabanuka kw'imiterere y'indwara.
Ingaruka z'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 gikomeje kuganirwaho muri iyi gahunda.
CoV z'inyamaswa zamenyekanye kuva mu mpera z'imyaka ya za 30.
Mbere yo gutandukanya bwa mbere ubwoko bwa HCoV-229E B814 mu byuka byaturukaga mu mazuru y'abarwayi bari barwaye indwara y'ibicurane, habonetse ubwoko butandukanye bwa CoV mu nyamaswa zitandukanye zanduye, harimo inkoko, imbeba, inka, ingurube, injangwe n'imbwa.
Mu myaka ibarirwa muri za mirongo ishize, hamaze kumenyekana virusi zirindwi za HCoV.
Isubiramo rito ry'amateka y'ibyavumbuwe kuri HCoV mu buryo bw'igihe (Igishushanyo cya 1) ryaba rifite amakuru kandi ryigisha.
Ubwa mbere ubwoko bwa HCoV-229E bwavumbuwe mu buryo bw'ubuhumekero bw'abarwayi bafite ubwandu bwo mu bice byo hejuru by'ubuhumekero mu mwaka wa 1966, nyuma buza gukoreshwa mu buryo bwo gukurira mu maraso y'ibihaha bya WI-38.
Abarwayi banduye HCoV-229E bagaragaje ibimenyetso bisanzwe by'ibicurane, birimo umutwe, kwiyuha akuya, kumva nabi no kuribwa mu muhogo, hamwe n'umuriro n'inkorora byabonetse mu 10~20% by'abanduye.
Nyuma mu 1967, HCoV-OC43 yavanywe mu buhinzi bw'intanga ndetse n'inyongera y'ibinyabiziga mu bwonko bw'imbeba.
Ibimenyetso by'indwara ya HCoV-OC43 bisa n'aho bisa n'ibyaterwe na HCoV-229E, bidatandukanye n'indwara ziterwa n'izindi virusi zandura mu mihumekero, urugero nk'indwara ya grippe A na rhinovirus.
HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 byombi bikwirakwizwa ku isi hose, kandi bikunze gukwirakwizwa cyane cyane mu gihe cy'imbeho mu bihe by'ubushyuhe.
Ubusanzwe, igihe cyo kuboneza urubyaro kuri izi virusi zombi kiba ari munsi y'icyumweru kimwe, gikurikirwa n'igihe cy'uburwayi cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko bigaragazwa n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu bitangiye gukora, abantu bafite amagara mazima banduye HCoV-229E, bagize ikibazo cy'ibicurane byoroheje.
Abarwayi bake gusa bafite ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri ni bo bagaragaje indwara ikomeye yo mu bwonko bwo hasi.
SARS, nanone izwi nka atypical pneumonia, ni yo yari icyorezo cya mbere cyanditswe neza cyatewe na HCoV mu mateka y'abantu kandi icyorezo cyatewe na SARS-CoV, ni cyo cya gatatu cyavumbuwe.
Umuntu wa mbere wahuye na SARS, yavumbuwe mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2002 mu ntara ya Guangdong mu Bushinwa.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyateje abantu 8,096 banduye ndetse 774 barapfa, cyakwirakwira mu bihugu byinshi no ku migabane myinshi.
