Hafi 20-30% by'abarwayi nyuma yaho, bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane no guhumeka.
Usibye mu nzira yo mu nda, imyanya myinshi harimo n'imyanya y'ubuhumekero, impyiko n'impyiko nabyo bishobora kwandura muri ibi bihe bikomeye, ubusanzwe bikagendana n'umuyaga w'imiti yitwa cytokine, ishobora kwica cyane cyane mu barwayi bafite ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri.
Virusi yabonetse bwa mbere mu isuzuma ry'ibihaha ryakozwe ku muntu wo mu muryango w'umurwayi wavuye i Guangzhou akajya i Hong Kong.
Kuva icyo gihe, hashyizweho imbaraga nyinshi mu bushakashatsi kuri HCoV.
HCoV-NL63 yavanywe ku mwana w'amezi 7 wo mu Buholandi mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2004.
Mu ntangiriro byagaragaye ko ari bwo bwagaragaye cyane mu bana bato, abageze mu za bukuru n'abarwayi bafite uburwayi bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero bafite uburwayi bufite ubushobozi bwo kwirinda indwara.
