Nubwo yamenyekanye mu Buholandi, mu by'ukuri ikwirakwizwa ku isi hose.
HCoV-NL63 bivugwa ko ari yo iteza hafi 4.7% by'indwara zisanzwe z'ubuhumekero, kandi ubwandu bwayo bukomeye cyane buba mu ntangiriro z'impeshyi, mu mpeshyi no mu itumba.
HCoV-NL63 ifitanye isano na laryngitis ifata umuntu mu gihe ari mu cyumba cy'umubiri, nanone izwi nka croup.
Muri uwo mwaka, HCoV-HKU1 yavanywe ku mugabo w'imyaka 71 wari warakomerekejwe na pneumonia na bronchiolitis i Hong Kong.
Usibye indwara y'ibicurane n'indwara y'ibicurane, HCoV-HKU1 yavuzwe ko ifitanye isano no gukubita cyane kw'ibicurane.
Kimwe na HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 yabonetse ku isi hose, ituma habaho indwara z'ubuhumekero zidakomeye.
Izi HCoV enye zose zageze mu baturage zagiye zihinduka neza ku bantu kandi muri rusange ntizishobora guhinduka ngo zitere indwara ziterwa n'indwara nyinshi, nubwo impanuka zabaye ku mpamvu zitazwi nk'uko byagenze mu bihe bidasanzwe by'ubwoko bw'ubwoko bw'ubwoko bwa HCoV-NL63, buherutse kuvugwa ko butera indwara ikomeye yo mu muhogo wo hasi mu Bushinwa.
Ubusanzwe, iyo izi HCoV zageze ku bushobozi bwo kwanduza neza no gukomeza kwizigamira mu bantu, na zo zituma zidakira cyane cyangwa ngo zigire indwara nyinshi.
MERS-CoV yabonetse bwa mbere mu 2012 mu bihaha by'umurwayi w'imyaka 60 wari ufite indwara y'ibicurane ikaze n'igwingira muri Arabiya Sawudite.
Mu gihe abenshi mu bantu bemejwe na laboratoire bakomoka mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, abinjijwe mu bihugu by'i Burayi na Tuniziya bagiye batangazwa ko hari n'abanduye mu bihugu bitandukanye by'i Burayi.
Indi ndwara ya kabiri yabonetse muri Koreya y'Epfo mu 2015 aho habonetse abarwayi 186.
Ibimenyetso by'indwara ya MERS bisa n'iby'indwara ya SARS, ibonekamo uburwayi bw'ibihaha bw'ibicurane bujya mbere.
Bitandukanye na SARS, abarwayi benshi bafite MERS nabo bagize uburwayi bw'impyiko bukomeye, kugeza ubu ari bwo bwonyine bwa MERS mu ndwara ziterwa na HCoV.
Abarenga 30% by'abarwayi bagaragaza ibimenyetso byo mu gifu, nk'ibicurane no kwitsamura.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, abasaga 2500 bemejwe n'ibiro by'ubushakashatsi, babonetse, umubare w'abapfa ukaba uri 34.4%, ibyo bikaba bituma MERS-CoV iba imwe muri virusi zangiza cyane abantu bazi.
Hagati kugeza mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019, amatsinda y'abarwayi ba pneumonia bazwi ko bafitanye isano n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 babonetse i Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko icyorezo cy'ubwandu bwo mu myanya yo hasi y'ubuhumekero cyatewe na SARS-CoV-2 ari ikibazo cy'ubutabazi bw'abaturage ku rwego mpuzamahanga, ndetse ryita n'icyo cyorezo COVID-19.
Kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020, ku isi hose hamaze kugaragara abantu 90,053 banduye, aho umubare w'abapfuye wari 3.4%.
By'umwihariko, urupfu rw'abarwayi muri Hubei, mu Bushinwa ni 4,2%, mu gihe urw'abari hanze yayo ari 1,2%.
SARS-CoV-2 itera indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zigaragara nk'ibicurane, icyiho no guhumeka nabi.
Hari n'abarwayi bagira ikibazo cy'ibihaha.
Pneumonia ni kimwe mu bimenyetso bikomeye cyane kandi bishobora gutera imbere vuba bikavamo syndrome y'ubuhumekero bukomeye.
Nubwo SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 bisa cyane bitewe n'ubwoko bwa nucleotide bwa 82%, byinjiye mu mashami atandukanye mu giti cy'ibanze.
SARS-CoV-2 bigaragara ko idatera indwara nyinshi ariko ko yandura cyane ugereranyije na SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Abantu batagaragaza ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bavuzwe kandi bashobora kugira uruhare mu gukwirakwira kwayo mu buryo bwihuse ku isi hose.
Kugereranya no gutandukana SARS-CoV-2 n'izindi HCoV esheshatu bigaragaza isano n'itandukaniro bishishikaje cyane.
Icya mbere, igihe cyo kuboneza urubyaro n'igihe cy'indwara ya HCoV ni kimwe.
Muri iyi ngingo, SARS-CoV-2 ikurikiza imiterere rusange ya izindi HCoV esheshatu.
Icya kabiri, ubukana bw'ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 buri hagati ya SARS-CoV na HCoVs enye zanduye mu baturage (ni ukuvuga HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63).
Ku ruhande rumwe, SARS-CoV-2 yerekana ibimenyetso bikunze kugaragara cyane mu gihe cy'ubwandu bw'imiterere ya HCoVs, harimo kugaragaza ibimenyetso bidasanzwe, byoroheje cyangwa nta bimenyetso.
Ku rundi ruhande, igice gito cy'abanduye COVID-19 gikomeye na cyo gishobora kubonwa nk'uko bimeze ku ndwara ya SARS-CoV, nubwo igipimo ari gito.
Icya gatatu, ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 rigaragaza uburyo bushishikaje bwihariye kuri HCoVs zanduye mu baturage na SARS-CoV.
Ku ruhande rumwe, uburyo SARS-CoV-2 yandurira abantu ni bwinshi cyane nko mu bwoko bwa HCoVs ziboneka mu baturage.
Ku rundi ruhande, biracyari kugenzurwa niba ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bugabanuka nyuma yo kunyura mu bantu nk'uko bimeze kuri SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Amaherezo, kimwe n'izindi HCoVs, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuboneka mu bipimo by'imyanda.
Niba gutandukana kwa SARS-CoV-2 binyuze mu guteka bifite uruhare runini nko mu gihe cya SARS-CoV nibura mu bihe bimwe na bimwe biracyari kugenzurwa n'ubushakashatsi buzakorwa mu gihe kizaza.
Ni byiza cyane kureba niba SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugaragaza ibihe nk'uko bimeze ku bantu banduye HCoVs.
Nyamara, ibintu biranga SARS-CoV-2 harimo uburyo ikwirakwira, ubukana bw'indwara n'uburyo ikwirakwira mu buryo burambye nyuma yo kwanduza abantu bizagira ingaruka ku byiringiro by'imperuka by'icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje.
HCoVs enye zose zanduye mu baturage zitera ibimenyetso byoroheje zagiye zihinduka neza ku bantu.
Urebye mu bundi buryo, birashoboka ko abantu bahinduye neza iyi virusi uko ari ine.
Mu yandi magambo, byombi bishobora kuba ari abacitse ku icumu ry'icyorezo cya HCoV cya kera.
HCoVs zitera indwara zikomeye ku bantu n'abantu bafite indwara zikomeye za HCoVs zaramaze gukurwaho.
Kugira ngo ibi bibe, HCoVs zigomba kwigana mu bantu mu rugero rwuzuye kugira ngo zitume habaho kwiyongera kw'impinduka zisanzwe zifasha kurwanya ibintu bituma umurwayi aguma mu cyiciro cy'ubudehe.
Muri ubwo buryo, uko icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kigenda kirushaho gukomera kandi kigakwirakwira abantu benshi, ni na ko amahirwe yo kuba cyajya gihuza n'abantu agenda arushaho kuba menshi.
Niba ihindura neza, kwandura kwayo ku bantu ntibyoroshye guhagarika mu gihe habaho gahunda yo kubarinda cyangwa izindi ngamba zo kurwanya ubwandu.
Mu gihe cy'imyaka myinshi, CoV enye z'abantu zagiye zigenda mu bantu, zitera imbeho mu bantu bafite ubushobozi bwo kwirinda indwara.
Izo virusi ntizikeneye ibinyabuzima.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ibyo, SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV ziterwa indwara nyinshi ntizihindutse neza ku bantu kandi ntizishobora gukwirakwira mu bantu.
Bagomba gukomeza no kwiyongera mu birunga byabo bya zoonotic kandi bagashaka amahirwe yo kwanduza abantu bashobora gukomereka, bishoboka binyuze mu murwayi umwe cyangwa benshi bahuza kandi bakongera imbaraga.
SARS-CoV-2 ifite ibintu bisa na SARS-CoV/MERS-CoV na HCoV enye zanduye mu baturage.
Ni indwara yandura cyane nka HCoVs zandura mu baturage, nibura kugeza ubu.
Icyakora, ni indwara nyinshi kurusha HCoVs zandura mu baturage kandi ntizigera zandura cyane kurusha SARS-CoV cyangwa MERS-CoV.
Biracyari kugenzurwa niba izashobora guhuza neza n'abantu kandi igakwirakwira mu bantu nta cyuzi cyangwa inyamaswa z'ibanze.
Mbere yo kuganira ku nkomoko y'inyamaswa za HCoVs, byaba byiza tuganiriye ku bisobanuro n'ibiranga abarwayi ba HCoVs bahinduka, ibidukikije, ibinyabuzima, abafite ubushobozi bwo hagati n'abafite ubushobozi bwo kongera imbaraga.
Inyamaswa ikora nk'ikiremwa cy'ihindagurika cya HCoV iyo ifite umukurambere ufitanye isano rya bugufi usangiye homologie yo hejuru ku rwego rwa nucleotide.
Virusi ya ba sogokuruza ubusanzwe ihinduka neza kandi ntabwo ari indwara muri uyu murwayi.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, ikigega cy'ubutaka kiba gifite HCoV mu buryo buhoraho kandi mu gihe kirekire.
Muri ibyo bihe byombi, abarwayi barandura mu buryo busanzwe kandi ni bo batwara HCoV cyangwa virusi y'ababyeyi bayo.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ibyo, niba HCoV iherutse kwinjizwa mu murwayi w'igitsina gabo mbere gato cyangwa hafi yaho, ntabwo ihinduka neza ku murwayi mushya kandi akenshi irandura indwara.
Iyi nyamaswa y'imiterere ishobora kuba isoko y'ubwandu bw'abantu kandi igakora nk'inyamaswa y'imiterere ikomeza, ikemerera virusi kwihindura mu buryo bw'igihe gito hanyuma ikaza kuyikwirakwiza ku bantu kugira ngo ikure ubwandu ku bantu.
HCoV ishobora kwandura mu gihe idashobora gukomeza kwanduzwa mu murwayi w'imbere.
Ahubwo, HCoVs ishobora no guhuza n'umunyamuryango w'igihembwe ndetse igashyiraho ubukana bw'igihe kirekire.
Muri icyo gihe, ikigo cy'ubutabazi cyaba ikigo cy'ibanze cy'ibikoresho.
Amakuru y'indwara z'ibyorezo yagaragaje ko mu gihe cya SARS, umuntu wa mbere yahuye n'inyamaswa zo mu gasozi.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe nyuma y'aho bwagaragaje ko abacuruzi b'amatungo bafite umubare munini w'abandura SARS-CoV IgG ugereranyije n'abaturage muri rusange.
Ibikeri by'amababi (Paguma larvata) n'imbwa y'ibishyimbo mu masoko y'amatungo ariho byamenyekanye bwa mbere ko bitwara virusi zisa na SARS-CoV hafi ya zose zisa na SARS-CoV.
Ibi byemejwe mu buryo butaziguye n'uko nta bindi bya SARS byatangajwe nyuma yo kwica ibyana byose by'ingore mu masoko.
Icyakora, byatangajwe ko udusimba tw'amaboko twambaye agapfukamunwa twavuye mu ishyamba cyangwa mu mirima tutari twagaragarijwe amasoko y'amatungo mazima, twateye SARS-CoV intege nke cyane, ibyo bikaba byerekana ko udusimba twambaye agapfukamunwa dushobora gusa kuba ari two dutuma SARS-CoV ikomera ariko atari yo ituma habaho SARS-CoV.
By'umwihariko, kubera ko 80% by'inyamaswa zitandukanye ziri ku masoko mu mujyi wa Guangzhou zifite anti-SARS-CoV, ntibishoboka ko amoko menshi y'ibinyabuzima bito bishobora no kuba ari byo bikomeza SARS-CoV.
Ibi byose bisa n'aho ari byo bikingira SARS-CoV.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe nyuma yo gushaka inyamaswa zisanzwe ziterwa na SARS-CoV, bwerekanye ko hari ubwoko bw'agakoko kitwa Rhinolophus bat CoV HKU3 (SARSr-Rh-BatCoV HKU3), gafite isano rya hafi n'agakoko kitwa SARS-CoV, kaboneka mu gakoko kitwa horseshoe bat ko mu Bushinwa.
Izi mbunda zemeza ko hari uduhanga tw'umubiri tw'umwanya wa SARS-CoV n'ubwoko bwa SARSr-Rh-BatCoV HKU3.
Iyi na izindi CoV z'imbeba zifite 88-92% z'ubwoko bwa nucleotide buhuje na SARS-CoV.
Ubwo bushakashatsi bwashyizeho urufatiro rw'igitekerezo gishya cy'uko udukoko dutera indwara abantu.
Hari kandi virusi zisa na SARS (SL-CoVs) zagiye zimenyekana mu bibugu, ariko nta na imwe uretse imwe yiswe WIV1 ishobora gutandukanywa nk'ubwandu buzima.
Enzyme ihindura angiotensin mu bantu 2 (ACE2) izwiho kuba ari yo ikira SARS-CoV.
WIV1 yakuwe mu cyuma cy'imbeba yagaragaye ko ikoresha imbeba, civet n'umuntu ACE2 nk'umufatabuzimafatizo wo kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Igitangaje ni uko intanga z'abarwayi ba SARS bari mu gihe cyo gukira zabashije guhosha WIV1.
Kugeza ubu, WIV1 ni yo ya mbere ya SARS-CoV mu byatsi, ifite 95% y'imiterere y'imiterere ya nucleotide.
Nubwo hari isano iri hagati y'iyi virusi ebyiri, muri rusange bizwi ko WIV1 atari virusi y'ababyeyi ba SARS-CoV kandi ko udukoko atari two dukingira SARS-CoV.
Isesengura ry'ibinyabuzima ryashyize MERS-CoV mu matsinda amwe na CoV-HKU4 na CoV-HKU5 y'ibinyugunyugu.
Bat CoV-HKU4 na MERS-CoV zikoresha uburyo bumwe bwo kwakira, dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4), mu kwinjira kwa virusi.
Urukurikirane rwa RNA polymerase rw'imiterere ya MERS-CoV rwashyizwe mu rwego rwa phylogenetics hafi y'urw'imiterere ya beta-CoVs z'imbeba zavumbuwe mu Burayi no muri Afurika.
Kugeza ubu, nta MERS-CoV nzima ishobora kuboneka mu bibugu byo mu gasozi.
MERS-CoV na CoV-HKU25 yo mu muryango wayo wa hafi cyane, bihuje 87% gusa by'urugero rw'imikorere ya nukleyotide.
Bityo, imbeba zishobora kuba atari zo zikoresha MERS-CoV.
Ku rundi ruhande, ubushakashatsi bwakorewe mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati bwagaragaje ko ingamiya z'inkona ziterwa na MERS-CoV-specific neutralizing antibodies, kimwe n'ingamiya zo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati zikomoka mu bihugu byinshi bya Afurika.
MERS-CoV nzima ihuriye na virusi yabonetse mu bantu yavanywe mu bipimo by'amaso by'ingamiya z'ingamiya, byongera kugaragaza ko ingamiya ari zo zikora nk'izikoresha neza MERS-CoV.
Birakwiye kandi kuzirikana ko mu buryo busanzwe ibimenyetso byoroheje ariko virusi nyinshi ziterwa na kamelo zanduye MERS-CoV mu igerageza.
Igitangaje ni uko ingamiya zanduye zitandura virusi binyuze mu nzira z'ubuhumekero gusa, ahubwo zitangurira no mu nzira z'amaraso n'umunwa, ari na yo nzira y'ibanze ituma udukoko dutandura virusi.
Icyakora, hari ibibazo bikiriho kuko abenshi mu bantu bemejwe ko banduye MERS batigeze bahura n'ingamiya mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira, ibyo bikaba byaterwa n'uko umuntu yandurira ku wundi muntu cyangwa se inzira zitamenyekana z'ubwandu z'inyamaswa zitamenyekana ko zanduye MERS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano ya 96.2% ya nucleotide na CoV RaTG13 y'ikirura cya Rhinolophus affinis.
Kimwe no mu gihe cya SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, itandukaniro ry'urugero hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na RaTG13 rirakomeye cyane ku buryo umuntu atabasha guha umubyeyi umubyeyi.
Ni ukuvuga ko udukoko dushobora kutaba ari two dukingira SARS-CoV-2 keretse gusa mu gihe kiri imbere habonetse udukoko tw'indwara z'ubwandu tw'imbeba zingana.
Birashoboka ko inyamaswa z'ibanze zanduza SARS-CoV-2 zigomba kuba ziri mu nyamaswa z'inyamaswa zagurishijwe kandi ziciwe ku isoko rya Huanan ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja, aho abenshi mu bantu ba mbere banduye COVID-19 bari bafitanye isano, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko bishoboka ko inyamaswa zandurira ku bantu.
Ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa bushingiye ku buryo bwo kugenzura metagenomic bwatanze igitekerezo cy'uko itsinda ry'ibinyabuzima bito biri mu kaga bita pangolins (Manis javanica) rishobora kuba rifite beta-CoVs z'abakurambere bifitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2.
Izi genomes nshya za CoV z'ibinyamushongo zifite 85-92% y'ubumwe bw'urugero rwa nukleyotide na SARS-CoV-2.
Icyakora, bifitanye isano rya bugufi na RaTG13 hamwe na 90% y'ubumwe ku rwego rwa nucleotide.
Zishyira hamwe mu miryango ibiri ya virusi zisa na SARS-CoV-2 mu giti cy'ibanze, imwe muri zo ikaba ifite urubuga rw'ibanga (RBD) rw'ibanga (receptor binding domain) rusa na SARS-CoV-2, ifite 97.4% ya amino acid.
Mu buryo butandukanye cyane, RBD za SARS-CoV-2 na RaTG13 ziratandukanye cyane, nubwo zifite urwego rwo hejuru rw'ubumwe bw'urugero mu bwoko bw'ibinyabuzima.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere ku ngona zirwaye kandi bwagaragaje ko habonetse virusi ziterwa n'imikorere y'ibicurane mu bipimo by'ibihaha, byaje kugaragara ko bifitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2.
Ubu bushakashatsi bwakoresheje uburyo butandukanye bwo guteranya no gukusanya intoki kugirango butange urutonde rw'ibinyabuzima by'igice kigizwe na 86.3% by'ibinyabuzima by'ubwoko bwose bwa virusi.
Ntabwo dushobora guca ukubiri n'ubushobozi bw'uko ingona ari imwe mu nyamaswa z'igitsina gabo z'indembe z'indembe za SARS-CoV-2.
Icyakora, muri iki gihe nta gihamya igaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse ku nyamaswa y'ingona bitewe n'uko imiterere y'inyamaswa y'ingona y'ingona SARS-CoV-2 itandukanye n'iyo ngona y'ingona SARS-CoV-2.
Byongeye kandi, intera iri hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na RaTG13 ni ngufi cyane ugereranyije n'iyo hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na pangolin SARS-CoV-2 bifitanye isano na beta-CoVs.
Inzira y'amahinduka ya SARS-CoV-2 mu mbogo, mu nyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa pangolin n'izindi nyamaswa zinyamaswa iracyari gushyirwaho.
Mu gihe urutonde rwo hejuru rwasanganywe mu RBD hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na pangolin, beta-CoVs zijyanye na SARS-CoV-2, SARS-CoV-2 na RaTG13 zisangiye urutonde rwo hejuru mu bwoko bwa genome.
Hariho ibitekerezo byinshi ko urugero rwo hejuru rw'ubumwe hagati ya RBD z'indwara z'ubwoko bwa SARS-CoV-2 zifitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2 zituruka ku guhinduka kw'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima.
Hari indi ngingo igamije kongera guhuza beta-CoV ifitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2 ya pangolin na RaTG13 mu bwoko bwa gatatu bw'inyamaswa zo mu gasozi.
Nk'imbaraga zituma habaho ubwihindurize, kongera guhuza birakwirakwira cyane mu bwoko bwa beta-CoVs.
Abacamanza baracyari hanze ku nkomoko ya zoonotic ya SARS-CoV-2.
Usibye HCoVs ziterwa indwara cyane, hagiye hakorwa ubushakashatsi ku nkomoko ya zoonotic ya HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-NL63 na HCoV-HKU1.
Ibimenyetso byerekana ko HCoV-NL63 na HCoV-229E byombi bishobora kuba byaturutse kuri CoVs z'ibinyugunyugu, mu gihe virusi z'ababyeyi za HCoV-OC43 na HCoV-HKU1 zabonetse mu bikoko.
Byamenyekanye ko ubwoko bw'umuswa wa CoV witwa ARCoV.2 (Appalachian Ridge CoV) bwabonetse mu muswa w'amabara atatu wo muri Amerika y'Amajyaruguru bwagaragaje isano ya hafi na HCoV-NL63.
Ku rundi ruhande, HCoV-229E yari ifitanye isano na CoV y'ikinyugunyugu, yitwa Hipposideros/GhanaKwam/19/2008, yagaragaye muri Ghana, mu gihe ibirura nabyo bikekwa ko ari byo byayibereyeho.
Kugira ngo bisobanuke neza, ubumenyi buriho ku byerekeye inkomoko y'inyamaswa ya HCoVs zizwi, bwasobanuwe muri Figure 1 na Table 2.
Isesengura ry'ibinyabuzima ryatanze ibimenyetso by'ibyabaye mu kwanduza ubwoko bw'imiterere ya HCoVs mu mateka.
Igihe HCoV-OC43 yambukiranyaga amoko kugira ngo yandure abantu mu matungo yo mu ngo ahagana mu 1890, habaye icyorezo cy'ubwandu bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
Amateka y'imikorere y'ubwandu bw'ubwoko bw'ubwoko bwa HCoV-229E ntabwo asobanutse neza.
Habonetse alpha-CoVs z'ibinyugunyugu bifitanye isano ya hafi na HCoV-229E.
Hagati yabo hari alpha-CoV ya alpaca.
Hari ibimenyetso byinshi byemeza ko virusi ishobora kwandurira ku bantu iturutse ku mpungenge.
Icya mbere, abantu ariko atari alpaka bashobora kuba bafitanye imishyikirano n'imbeba mu karere kamwe.
Ahubwo abantu baba bafitanye imishyikirano ya bugufi n'izo nyamaswa.
Icya kabiri, alpha-CoVs z'ibinyugunyugu bifitanye isano na HCoV-229E ziratandukanye kandi ntizitera indwara mu binyabuzima, mu gihe alpaca alpha-CoV yateje icyorezo cy'indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero mu nyamaswa zanduye.
Ku bw'ibyo, alpaca alpha-CoV ntabwo yigeze iboneka mu nyamaswa z'inkazi.
Bityo, ntibishoboka ko alpaka zishobora kubona alpha-CoV ifitanye isano na HCoV-229E iturutse ku bantu.
Mu by'ukuri, imbeba ni zo zitera virusi zitera indwara z'abantu, harimo virusi y'ibicurane, Ebola, Nipah na Hendra.
Ku bw'ibyo, ntibitangaje cyane ko udukoko dushobora kwanduza HCoV-229E ku bantu.
Ubundi, mu gihe alpha-CoVs z'imbeba zikora nk'ibinyabuzima bya HCoV-229E, alpacas na dromedary camels zishobora gukora nk'abaturanyi ba mbere batanga virusi ku bantu, nk'uko byagenze kuri MERS-CoV.
MERS-CoV ni urugero rwiza rwo kwanduzanya ubwoko butandukanye kuva ku mbogo kugeza ku ngamiya z'ingamiya no kuva ku ngamiya z'ingamiya kugera ku bantu.
Inkomoko y'ubwihindurize bwa MERS-CoV ituruka ku mbogo irazwi mu gihe cy'umwimerere kandi yongeye gushimangirwa n'ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe nyuma.
