Ku bw'ibyo, ntibishoboka gutamba ingamiya zose mu kurwanya MERS, nk'uko byagenze mu masoko y'inyamaswa zo mu ishyamba mu Bushinwa mu kwirinda ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2.
Kugira ngo haboneke umuti wo kurwanya MERS, hakwiye gushyirwaho uburyo bw'ubwisanzure bwo gukingira MERS-CoV ku ngamiya, hakoreshejwe n'izindi ngamba zo kurwanya indwara.
Kubera ko tudashobora kurandura izo virusi, hari ubwo hazabaho ubwoko bushya bw'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima butuma habaho indwara.
Hari ubwoko bwinshi bwa zoonotic CoVs zikomeje gukwirakwira mu gasozi.
By'umwihariko, CoV z'ibinyugunyugu zifite ubushobozi bwo gutera zoonotic ziratandukanye cyane.
Hari uburyo bwinshi bwo ko izi CoV z'ibinyabuzima zihinduka kandi zikongera guhuza, bigatuma haboneka izindi CoV nshya zishobora kwandura cyane kandi/cyangwa zikaba ziteye urupfu mu bantu mu gihe kizaza.
Umuco wo kurya inyamaswa z'inkazi mu duce tumwe na tumwe tw'u Bushinwa wagombye kureka kugira ngo abantu n'inyamaswa batagirana imishyikirano idakenewe.
Kubera ibigeragezo bya SARS, MERS na COVID-19, gahunda nziza yo kwitegura no kwitabira igomba gushyirwa mu bikorwa.
Mu by'ukuri, virusi nyinshi zabayeho ku isi mu gihe kirekire cyane.
Ziguma mu mazi yazo bwite kugeza igihe habonetse uburyo bwo kuzisasa.
Nubwo udukoko dufite ibintu byinshi bituma habaho ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu, dushobora kugabanya cyane cyane abantu bashobora guhura n'udukoko n'ibindi biremwa byo mu gasozi, turamutse twigishije abantu kutwitarura.
Kugenzura guhoraho mu nyamaswa zinyamanswa ni ngombwa kugirango dusobanukirwe neza ibidukikije bya CoVs n'abaturanyi bayo, bizagaragara ko ari ingirakamaro mu gukumira kwanduzanya inyamaswa n'abantu no mu gihe kizaza.
Mu gusoza, uburyo bwiza cyane bwo kwirinda virusi ya zoonosis ni uko abantu bakomeza kuba kure y'aho virusi za zoonosis zibera.
Ibice byinshi by'ikibazo cy'inkomoko ya zoonotic ya SARS-CoV-2 biracyari ubusa.
Icya mbere, niba udusimba twanduza virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ku nyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa pangolin, bizashimisha kureba mu bihe bidukikije udusimba n'inyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa pangolin bishobora kugira aho bihuriye mu by'ibidukikije.
Icya kabiri, niba udukoko tugize uruhare mu buryo butaziguye mu gukwirakwiza indwara ku bantu, uburyo abantu bagirana imishyikirano n'udukoko bwagombye kugaragazwa.
Icya gatatu, niba inyamaswa ya gatatu ifite ibinyabuzima by'ibanze, uburyo ikorana n'amoko atandukanye, harimo abantu, imbeba n'ibinyamushongo, bigomba gusobanurwa.
Amaherezo, kubera ko inyamaswa nyinshi ziryamye harimo n'amatungo yo mu rugo zishobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2, hagomba gukorwa igenzura no gupima.
Niba ari umukangara, ingona cyangwa ikindi kinyamaswa cy'ibyara, byitezwe ko SARS-CoV-2 cyangwa virusi z'ababyeyi bayo zingana hafi cyane zizagaragara mu barwayi bayo bo mu buryo bw'ibanze mu gihe kizaza.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeje muri aka gace buzatuma haboneka inzira y'ihindagurika rya SARS-CoV-2 mu nyamaswa, bigira ingaruka zikomeye mu gukumira no kugenzura COVID-19 mu bantu.
Ni ngombwa kuvugurura ibipimo byo gupima COVID-19 ukekwaho kuba ariwe  no kwizezwa ko ariwe 
Ku ya 6 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ryacu ryasohoye amabwiriza yihuse yo gusuzuma no kuvura icyorezo cya coronavirus nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV), kandi aya mabwiriza yatugejejeho ubunararibonye kandi atuma turushaho kurwanya iki cyorezo ku isi hose.
Nyamara, indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) ni indwara nshya, ubumenyi bwacu n'ubumenyi bwacu bigenda byiyongera buhoro buhoro bishingiye ku byo ubushakashatsi bukomeje kugeraho n'ubunararibonye mu buvuzi; bityo, ingamba zo gupima no kuvura nazo zikomeza kuvugururwa.
Muri iyi baruwa, twashubije igitekerezo kimwe ku mabwiriza yacu kandi dutanga ibipimo bishya byo gupima ukekwaho ubwandu no ukekwaho ubwandu hakurikijwe amabwiriza mashya yo gupima no kuvura COVID-19 (igice cya karindwi) cyatanzwe na Komite y'igihugu y'ubuzima ya Repubulika y'Abashinwa.
Mu Ukuboza 2019, coronavirus nshya (2019-nCoV) yatumye habaho icyorezo, ubu cyitwa coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) kandi iyi virusi yiswe severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, OMS yagaragaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 yanduye, itsinda ryacu ryakoze amabwiriza yihuse kandi yashyizwe ahagaragara kuri interineti mu kinyamakuru Military Medical Research ku wa 06 Gashyantare 2020.
Kuva yasohoka, abantu benshi barayishishikaje.
Ariko kandi, wibuke ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, ubumenyi bwacu n'ubumenyi bwacu bigenda byiyongera buhoro buhoro bishingiye ku byo ubushakashatsi bukomeje kugeraho n'ubunararibonye mu buvuzi; bityo, ingamba zo gusuzuma no kuvura nazo zikomeza kuvugururwa.
Urugero, Amabwiriza yo gupima no kuvura COVID-19 yashyizweho na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'Abaturage y'Ubushinwa (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), hagati ya 16 Mutarama 2020 na 3 Werurwe 2020, yashyizweho mu bitabo birindwi, aho bimwe mu bikubiyemo byahinduwe cyane.
Ubu ubuyobozi bwacu bwarakiriwe na Zhou et al., batanze igitekerezo cyoroshye cyo kubara bashingiye ku byaranze clinique yabo.
Ibikorwa byabo byongereye ibihamya bishya kubyo twigishije kandi biranagira akamaro cyane muri iki cyorezo ku isi hose.
Dushyigikiye umurimo wabo w'ingenzi kandi turabashimira.
Icyakora, akazi kabo gakeneye kuvugururwa hakurikijwe amabwiriza mashya yo gupima no kuvura COVID-19 (Igerageza ku ncuro ya karindwi) n'ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'icyegeranyo cya karindwi (3 Werurwe 2020), kugira ngo hemezwe ko umuntu akekwaho indwara, hagomba guhuzwa ikintu kimwe cyose cy'amateka y'indwara n'ibintu bibiri by'ubura bw'uburwayi kugira ngo hakorwe isesengura rirambuye, cyangwa hagomba guhuzwa n'ibintu bitatu by'ubura bw'uburwayi mu gihe nta mateka y'indwara y'uburwayi asobanutse:
Amateka y'indwara: (1) amateka y'ingendo cyangwa gutura mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'uturere tuwugose, cyangwa mu yindi midugudu aho abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari baratangajwe mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira; (2) amateka y'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 (binyuze mu gupima aside ya nukleyiki yemeza); (3) amateka y'ubwandu bw'abarwayi bafite umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'uturere tuwugose, cyangwa mu yindi midugudu aho COVID-19 yari yaratangajwe mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira; (4) amateka y'ubwandu bw'abarwayi bemejwe (imibare 2 y'abarwayi bafite umuriro cyangwa/cyangwa ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero byabonetse mu byumweru 2 mu duce duto, nk'inzu, ibiro, ishuri, n'ibindi).
Ibimenyetso by'uburwayi: (1) umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka; (2) bifite ibimenyetso byerekana ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) imibare yose y'amaraso yera yerekana imibare isanzwe, igabanuka cyangwa igabanuka ry'ibinyabuzima by'amaraso mu gihe cy'uburwayi bwa mbere.
Gushakisha icyorezo cyemejwe bigomba gushingira ku kibazo gikekwaho kimwe cy'ibimenyetso by'indwara cyangwa se byo mu bwoko bwa virusi bikurikira: (1) isuzuma rya PCR mu gihe nyacyo ryerekana ko SARS-CoV-2 ari nziza; (2) gukwirakwiza imiterere ya virusi yose yerekana ko ifite ubukana bwinshi ku virusi nshya za coronavirusi; (3) kugaragaza ko IgM yihariye n'igihangana IgG kuri SARS-CoV-2 mu isuzuma rya serum; cyangwa guhindura IgG yihariye ya SARS-CoV-2 kuva ku yindi ikajya ku yindi, cyangwa se ikinyuranyo cyayo kizamuka inshuro ≥4 mu cyiciro cyo gukira kirenze icy'icyiciro gikomeye.
Dushobora kubona ko ibipimo bya PCR mu gihe nyacyo by'umwimerere ku byerekeye aside ya nucleic mu mitsi cyangwa mu maraso byongerewe ku cyiciro cya kabiri (18 Mutarama 2020) n'icya gatatu (22 Mutarama 2020).
Ibimenyetso by'indwara ziterwa n'amaraso byongerewe ku ncuro ya kane (27 Mutarama 2020) no ku ya gatanu (8 Gashyantare 2020); hanyuma ibimenyetso bya seroloji byongerwa ku ncuro ya karindwi.
Izi mpinduka zishingiye ku gikorwa cy'abashakashatsi cyo gushaka igikoresho cyiza cyo gupima aside ya nucleic kugirango hamenyekane vuba, kimwe n'ibipimo byo mu nzira zo guhumeka harimo no gufata amaraso, byongereye uburyo bwo kubona ibipimo bitandukanye, kandi byashyigikiye kuzana icyemezo cy'umwanya w'umubiri mu bipimo byemejwe.
Byongeye kandi, hari ibimenyetso byinshi bidufasha kuzirikana ko tugomba kugira amakenga mu gihe dufata abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso bidasanzwe n'abatabifite.
Niyo mpamvu, igishushanyo mbonera cya Zhou et al. kigomba kuvugururwa, kuko bashyize mu byiciro umuntu udafite ibimenyetso by'uburwayi nk'umuntu ufite ibyago bito.
Iyi gahunda yo kubara ikeneye kandi kwemezwa mu bindi bikorwa by'ubuvuzi n'ubushakashatsi.
Mu gusoza, twizeye ko hari ibindi bimenyetso bifatika bizagaragara, kandi turasaba abasomyi gutanga ibitekerezo byabo.
Ku bijyanye no gusuzuma abatekereza ko banduye na abemejwe ko banduye, tubagira inama yo gukurikiza amabwiriza mashya y'ibihugu byabo.
Itsinda ryacu rizongera gusubiramo amabwiriza yacu mu gihe gikwiriye kugira ngo ritange ubufasha.
Bangladesh yatangaje abantu bashya batanu bapfuye bazira COVID-19, umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye buri munsi
Ejo, Bangladesh yemeje abantu bashya batanu bapfuye bishwe na COVID-19 kuri uwo munsi.
Iyi ni imibare y'abantu benshi bapfuye mu munsi umwe kubera virusi.
Kugeza ejo, Ikigo cya Epidemiology, Disease Control and Research (IEDCR) cyo muri Bangladesh cyatangaje ko umubare w'abanduye wazamutse, harimo 114 bakirwaye n'abamaze gukira 33 bari mu rugo.
Abantu 17 bapfuye.
Mu kiganiro cy'itangazamakuru cyabaye kuri internet, umuyobozi wa IEDCR, Dr Meerjady Sabrina Flora, yavuze ko mu bapfuye harimo abagabo bane n'umugore umwe.
Dr Meerjady yavuze ko abantu babiri bari bafite imyaka iri hejuru ya 60, babiri bari hagati ya 51 na 60, n'undi umwe wari ufite imyaka iri hagati ya 41 na 50.
Yavuze kandi ko babiri mu baguye muri iyo mpanuka bakomokaga i Dhaka.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe.
Umuyobozi w'ibitaro yabwiye Anadolu Agency, ikinyamakuru cy'amakuru cyo muri ako gace, ko umwe mu bapfuye ari Jalal Saifur Rahman, umuyobozi wa Komisiyo yo kurwanya ruswa muri Bengali, wari urwariye mu bitaro bya Kuwait Maitree.
Ku wa Gatandatu, mu itangazo ry'amashusho ku rubuga rwa interineti, Minisitiri w'Umuhanda n'Ibiraro muri Bangladesh, Obaidul Quader, yavuze ko imodoka z'abaturage zizamara igihe kirekire kirenze icya mbere giteganyijwe, kugeza ku wa Gatandatu utaha.
Iyi gahunda yo guhagarika ingendo mu nzego z'ubucuruzi yatangiye ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, ikaba yari iteganyijwe kurangira ku wa Gatandatu tariki ya 4 Mata.
Itwara ibintu by'ibanze - nk'imiti, lisansi n'ibiribwa - ryakomeje kwemererwa.
Abantu ba mbere banditswe banduye COVID-19 muri Bangladesh byabaye ku ya 8 Werurwe, mu bantu babiri bagarutse bavuye mu Butaliyani ndetse n'umugore wa umwe muri bo.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 19 Werurwe, abo batatu bari bamaze gukira.
SARS-CoV-2 irenga miliyoni y'ubwandu ku isi
Ku wa kane, umubare w'abanduye SARS-CoV-2 coronavirus warenze miliyoni imwe ku isi yose, nk'uko byatangajwe n'amakuru ya kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins.
Nibura abantu ibihumbi 52 bapfuye bashingiye kuri COVID-19, indwara yatewe na coronavirus.
Iki gikorwa cyabaye umunsi umwe Malawi yemeje ubwandu bwa mbere bwa coronavirus na Zambia ifite urupfu rwa mbere rufitanye isano na coronavirus.
Koreya ya Ruguru yavuze ko kugeza ku wa kane, ari kimwe mu bihugu bike bikiri bitanduye coronavirus.
Ku munsi w'ejo, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko abarwayi 1,051,635 bamaze kwandura, harimo 79,332 mu masaha makumyabiri n'ane yabanjirije saa kumi za mu gitondo ku isaha ya Buraya bwo hagati (0800 UTC) ku itariki ya 4 Mata.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, abanduye coronavirus barenga ibihumbi 244 nibo banditswe, bivanye n'imiburiburi abantu 5,900 bapfuye.
Amakuru ya CBS, yerekana amakuru y'ikigo cya Johns Hopkins, yavuze ko abantu barenga 1000 bapfuye muri Amerika ku wa gatatu, biturutse ku ndwara ya coronavirus.
Hirya no hino ku isi, ibihugu byatangaje ko bizashyiraho ingamba zikomeye kugira ngo birinde ko iyo ndwara ikwirakwira.
Ku wa kane, Sergei Sobyanin, umuyobozi w'umujyi wa Moscou, yongeyeho igihe cyo gufunga umujyi kugeza ku itariki ya 1 Gicurasi.
Ku rwego rw'igihugu, Perezida Vladimir Putin yatangaje ko Abarusiya bazakomeza guhembwa badafite akazi kugeza ku itariki ya 30 Mata.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Porutugali yemeye ko igihe cy'ubutegetsi bw'ikirenga cyongerwaho iminsi 15, maze amatora aba ku majwi 215, 10 ntiyabyemera, naho undi umwe arabyanga.
Arabiya Sawudite yongereye amasaha yo gutaha mu mijyi yera ya Mecca na Medina ku buryo azamara umunsi wose; mbere yaho, amasaha yo gutaha yari hagati ya saa tatu z'umugoroba na saa kumi n'ebyiri za mu gitondo gusa.
Igihugu cya Tayilande cyateganyaga gushyiraho amasaha y'umukwabu hagati ya saa kumi n'ebyiri z'umugoroba na saa yine za mu gitondo.
Guverineri wa Ohio, Mike DeWine, yatangaje ko leta yongereye igihe cyo kuguma mu rugo kugeza ku ya 1 Gicurasi.
Amaduka yo muri Ositaraliya yagabanyije umubare w'ibyangombwa by'isuku ku gihe cy'ubucuruzi
Ku cyumweru no ku wa gatandatu nimugoroba, amaduka yo muri Ositaraliya ya Woolworths na Coles yagabanyije imipaka yo kugura impapuro z'isuku ku buryo buri gicuruzwa cyagombaga kugura impapuro ebyiri n'imwe mu maduka yose yo mu gihugu.
ALDI kandi yashyizeho igipimo cy'ipakire rimwe, ku wa mbere.
Ibi bihano byashyizwe ku mbuga nkoranyambaga, no ku mbuga za Facebook z'amasosiyete.
Bivugwa ko abaguzi bari guhaha kubera ubwoba bwa COVID-19 mu gihe abantu bagomba kwisanzura.
Ku wa gatatu, Woolworths kandi yagabanyije kugura impapuro z'isuku zo gutumiza mu rugo ku gikapu kimwe kuri buri cyemezo.
Izi mpinduka zakurikiye ibyangombwa bya mbere by'ibikoresho bine kuri buri gikorwa byashyizweho na Woolworths na Coles ku ya 4 na 5 Werurwe.
Coles, mu itangazo ryayo ryo ku wa 8 Werurwe, yatangaje ko kubera ko hari ibitabo bine byemewe, "amaduka menshi aracyagurishwa mu gihe cy'isaha imwe nyuma yo gutanga", ndetse avuga ko ibyo biciro "bitigeze bibaho", mu gihe ALDI, mu butumwa yoherereje kuri Facebook ku wa Kabiri, yabyise "bitunguranye".
Igicuruzwa cyazamutse "ku buryo bukomeye" mu cyumweru gishize, nk'uko bivugwa n'umuvugizi wa Woolworths.
Ububiko bwa Costco muri Canberra nabwo bwagabanyije umubare wemewe ku mapaketi abiri mu cyumweru gishize.
Kugira ngo bongere kugabanya ibura ry'ibikoresho, Coles yategetse ibicuruzwa binini ku batanga ibicuruzwa kandi yongera inshuro byo gutumiza, Woolworths yategetse ibicuruzwa by'inyongera, mu gihe ALDI yatumye ibicuruzwa by'umunsi wa gatatu byateganyijwe ku munsi wa gatatu biboneka hakiri kare.
Russell Zimmerman, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishyirahamwe ry'abacuruzi bo muri Ositaraliya, yavuze ko abacuruzi bagerageza gukusanya ibicuruzwa, ariko ko amategeko y'akarere abuza abantu gutumiza ibicuruzwa mu modoka bituma bigorana.
Yiteze ko ibiciro by'umusaruro bizamuka, kuko abacuruza bagerageza guhaza ibyifuzo, kandi n'ibiciro by'ibicuruzwa bidasanzwe bigabanuke.
Ku wa Kabiri, ALDI yatangaje ko nyuma yo gusohora mbere y'igihe ibicuruzwa, hari amaduka adashobora gukora ibirori byihariye byo ku wa Gatatu.
Mu nkuru ya News.com.au, Dr Gary Mortimer, impuguke mu by'ubucuruzi muri Kaminuza ya Queensland y'ikoranabuhanga, yavuze ko amaduka yuzuza ibicuruzwa buri joro.
Yavuze ko impapuro z'isuku ari ikintu kinini, bigatuma umubare w'ibicuruzwa uba muke, kandi iyo ziguze, zigasiga ibyumba byinshi by'ububiko bitabaye, bigatuma abantu bumva ko hari ikibazo cy'ibura.
Russell Zimmerman wavuze kuri ABC News, yagize ati "Coles na Woolworths babona ko niba hari ibintu byinshi ku isanduku, niba hari ibicuruzwa nk'ibitabo by'isuku n'ibisukura bishobora [kugurwa] kandi bikaba biriho mu bwinshi, ushobora kugabanya ubwoba".
Umukozi ukora impapuro z'isuku zikoreshwa mu buryo busubitse, witwa Who Gives a Crap, yavuze ko ku wa gatatu w'icyumweru gishize bari bagiye kubura ibitabo.
Kimberly-Clark, ikora Kleenex Toilet Tissue, na Solaris Paper ikora Sorbent, byashimangiye ko bakora 24h/24 kugira ngo bakomeze gutanga ibyo bikoresho, nk'uko raporo ya News.com.au ibivuga.
Urubuga rwa Domain.com, ruvuga ko hari abacuruzi b'imitungo batanze urupapuro rw'isuku ku buntu ku muntu wa mbere wari watangaga igitekerezo mu cyamunara i Melbourne, mu gihe hari abantu bake bari batanze amaturo kubera ko abaguzi bari bafite igihe cyo kuruhuka mu mpera z'icyumweru kirekire z'umunsi mukuru w'abakozi.
Ikinyamakuru cyo muri Darwin cyitwa NT News cyo ku wa Kane, cyanditseho agapapuro k'amapaji umunani kari kagomba gutemwa maze kakoreshwa nk'impapuro z'isuku.
Amaduka yabanje kwanga gushyiraho ingamba, nk'uko raporo ya ABC Australia yo ku wa 3 Werurwe yabitangaje, aho bavugaga ko nta gahunda bafite yo gushyiraho ingamba ku byo bagura.
Russell Zimmerman yongeyeho ko ibindi bicuruzwa nabyo bikenewe cyane, harimo udupfukamunwa, umuti wo guhanagura, ibicuruzwa byumye, gukaraba intoki n'ifu.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, hanze ya Ositaraliya, ku mugoroba wo ku cyumweru, muri sosiyete y'ubucuruzi yo mu Bwongereza ikora kuri interineti yitwa Ocado, habonetse abantu bagura gusa amakarita abiri y'ibitabo by'isuku byitwa Andres.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyugarije isi
Ku wa gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19  indwara yatewe na coronavirus SARS-CoV-2  ari icyorezo.
N'ubwo ijambo "icyorezo" ryerekeza gusa ku kuntu indwara yakwirakwiriye cyane, ntabwo ari uburyo abantu runaka bagaragaraho uburwayi bafite akaga, OMS yagaragaje ko ari ngombwa gushishikariza leta kugira icyo zikora:
"Ibihugu byose biracyafite ubushobozi bwo guhindura icyorezo.
Mu gihe ibihugu byagerageje, bigerageza, bikita ku bantu, bikumira, bikurikirana kandi bigashyira abaturage babyo mu bikorwa, " nk'uko Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS yabivuze.
"Dutewe impungenge cyane n'ubwiyongere buteye ubwoba n'uburemere bwabwo ndetse n'ubwiyongere buteye ubwoba bw'ubushomeri".
Dukurikije uko Dogiteri Tom Frieden wahoze ari umuyobozi w'Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara no Kuzirinda yabivuze, iki cyorezo "nta ho cyari cyigeze kiboneka".
Yavuze mu magambo yashyizwe ahagaragara na CNN muri Gashyantare, ati "uretse ibicurane, nta wundi mugera wo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero wigeze urebwa kuva watangira kugeza ukomeje gukwirakwira ku isi hose".
Ghebreyesus yagaragaje igitekerezo nk'icyo, avuga ko "nta cyorezo cyatewe na coronavirus twigeze tubona".
Yakomeje agira ati "kandi nta cyorezo na kimwe twigeze tubona gishobora kugenzurwa icyarimwe".
Iyi ndwara nshya y'icyorezo ikurikira icyemezo cya OMS cyo gutangaza ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo cyugarije isi yose.
Umuyobozi w'Ikigo cy'Igihugu cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Indwara Zandura n'Abaganga, Dr. Anthony Fauci, yavuze ko iki cyorezo "kizagenda kirushaho kuba kibi".
Kugeza ku wa kane, Associated Press yatangaje ko nibura hari abantu 126,000 banduye COVID-19 ku isi hose, bituma hapfa abantu barenga 4,600.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019-20 ni icyorezo gikomeje cy'indwara ya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe na coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
