Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bidasanzwe kandi abantu banduye bashobora kuba badafite ibimenyetso.
Ibimenyetso bibiri bikunze kugaragara cyane ni umuriro (88%) n'inkorora (68%).
Ibimenyetso bidakunze kugaragara cyane harimo umunaniro, gutakaza umwuka, kubura impumuro, guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu ngingo no mu misatsi, kuribwa mu muhogo, kuribwa n'umutwe, kugira ubwoba, kuruka, kurwara amaraso, gucibwamwo cyangwa cyanoze. OMS ivuga ko hafi umuntu umwe kuri batandatu arwara cyane kandi agahumeka nabi.
Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyashyize ku rutonde ibimenyetso by'ubutabazi nko guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu gatuza cyangwa gukandamiza, urujijo rutunguranye, kugorana kubyuka, no kurasa ubururu mu maso cyangwa ku munwa; ubuvuzi bwihuse burasabwa niba ibi bimenyetso bihari. Iterambere ry'iyi ndwara rishobora gutuma umuntu arwara icyorezo cy'ibicurane, indwara yo guhumeka nabi cyane, sepsis, gufatwa n'indwara y'ubwandu bw'amaraso ndetse n'urupfu.
Bamwe mu barwaye bashobora kuba badafite ibimenyetso, nta bimenyetso by'ubuvuzi bafite ariko bafite ibisubizo by'ibizamini byemeza ko barwaye, bityo abashakashatsi batanze inama ko abahuye cyane n'abantu barwaye bakwiriye gukurikiranwa byimbitse no gusuzumwa kugira ngo birinde kwandura.
