Ingamba zo gutandukanya abantu ku mubiri nazo zirasabwa kugira ngo birinde kwandura. Leta nyinshi zahagaritse cyangwa zigasaba ko ingendo zose zidakenewe zijya cyangwa ziva mu bihugu no mu turere twugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Icyakora, virusi imaze kugera ku rwego rwo gukwirakwira mu bice byinshi by'isi.
Ibi bivuze ko virusi ikwirakwira mu baturage, kandi bamwe mu baturage ntibazi aho cyangwa uko banduye. Abashinzwe ubuzima bita ku muntu ushobora kuba yanduye basabwa gukoresha ingamba zisanzwe zo kwirinda, kwirinda guhura n'umuntu, no kurinda amaso. Gukurikirana abantu bahuye n'umuntu ni uburyo bw'ingenzi ku nzego z'ubuzima bwo kumenya inkomoko y'ubwandu no kwirinda ko bwongera kwanduzwa.
Gukoresha amakuru y'aho umuntu ari kuri telefoni zigendanwa na za leta muri iyo gahunda, byatumye abantu bahangayikishwa n'ibanga ryabo, aho Amnesty International n'izindi nzego zirenga 100 zasohoye itangazo risaba ko habaho imipaka ku buryo bwo kugenzura.
Porogaramu zitandukanye za mobile zashyizwe mu bikorwa cyangwa zasabwe gukoreshwa ku bushake, kandi kuva tariki ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda y'impuguke asaga cumi n'abiri arimo akora ku bisubizo by'ibanga, nko gukoresha Bluetooth kugira ngo umuntu agere kuri telefoni zigendanwa.
Abakoresha noneho bahabwa ubutumwa niba bahuye n'umuntu wafashwe na COVID-19.Ibitekerezo bibi birimo gukwirakwira ku buryo bwo kwirinda kwandura; urugero, gukaraba izuru no gukaraba mu kanwa n'amazi yo kumesa ntibikora.
Nta rukingo rwa COVID-19 rubaho, nubwo imiryango myinshi ikora kugira ngo irushyiremo.
Gukaraba intoki ni byiza mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo.
Ikigo cy'Ukurwanya Indwara z'Abatera SIDA gitanga inama y'uko abantu bakwiriye gukaraba intoki kenshi bakoresheje isabune n'amazi nibura amasegonda makumyabiri, cyane cyane iyo bamaze kujya mu bwiherero cyangwa iyo intoki zabo zanduye mu buryo bugaragara; mbere yo kurya; na nyuma yo guhumeka, gukorora cyangwa kwiyuha.
Ibyo biterwa n'uko iyo virusi ivuye mu mubiri w'umuntu, yicwa n'isabune yo mu rugo, igatwika icyo kibumbano cyayikingiraga.
CDC yongeraho ko ukoresha umuti wo gusukura intoki ukoresheje inzoga nibura 60% by'inzoga iyo nta sabuni n'amazi biboneka.
OMS igira abantu inama yo kwirinda gukora ku maso, ku zuru cyangwa ku kanwa bakoresheje intoki zitahumutse.
Uturere dushobora gukingurwa hakoreshejwe umuti (mu minota imwe nyuma yo gukoreshwa umuti wo gukonona udukoko ku butaka bw'icyuma kitagira ingese), harimo 62% ya etanol, 50% ya isopropanol, 0,1% ya sodium hypochlorite, 0,5% ya peroxide ya hydrogène, na 0,27% ya povidone-iode.
Ibindi bisubizo, urugero nka benzalkonium chloride na chrohexidine gluconate, ntibikora neza.
CDC iratangaza ko mu gihe hari umuntu ukekwaho cyangwa wemejwe ko arwaye COVID mu kigo nk'ibiro cyangwa uburinzi bw'abana, ahantu hose nko mu biro, mu byumba by'ubwiherero, ahantu abantu basanzwe basangira ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki nk'ibikoresho bya tablet, touch screen, ibyuma by'ibanga, ibyuma byo kugenzura kure, na ATM zikoreshwa n'abarwayi, bigomba gukoreshwa mu gukingira indwara.
Amashami y'ubuzima yasabye abantu ko iyo bakoroye cyangwa bakanyuzamo, bagombye gukingiriza umunwa n'amazuru bakoresheje umufuka cyangwa umufuka, kandi bakirinda uwo mufuka uwo ari wo wose.
Abantu bashobora kwandura, basabwa kwambara udupfukamunwa two kubaga, kuko kwambara udupfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya ingano n'urugendo rw'amazi aturuka mu mwuka atambutse iyo uvuga, witsamura cyangwa witsamura.
OMS yatanze amabwiriza ku gihe n'uburyo bwo gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
Stephen Griffin, umuhanga mu by'imiti y'ubwandu muri Kaminuza ya Leeds, yagize ati "kwambara agapfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya uburyo abantu bakunze gukorakora mu maso, ari na cyo kintu cy'ingenzi cyatuma abantu barwara indwara iyo badafite isuku y'amaboko".
OMS yasabye abantu bafite amagara mazima kwambara udupfukamunwa gusa mu gihe bafite ibyago byinshi, nk'abita ku muntu urwaye COVID-19, nubwo bemeza ko kwambara udupfukamunwa bishobora gufasha abantu kwirinda gukorakora mu maso.
Ibihugu byinshi byatangiye gushishikariza abaturage gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
Muri Amerika, CDC irasaba kwambara agapfukamunwa kitari icy'ubuvuzi gakorewe mu mwenda. Ubushinwa bwasabye mu buryo bwihariye abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza gukoresha agapfukamunwa gashyirwa ku ruhande, cyane cyane iyo bahuye hafi n'abandi bantu (metero 1 cyangwa munsi yayo).
Hong Kong irasaba kwambara agapfukamunwa mu gihe utwaye imodoka za Leta cyangwa mu gihe uri ahantu hahurira abantu benshi.
Abashinzwe ubuzima muri Thailand barimo gushishikariza abantu gukora udupfukamunwa tw'umwenda mu rugo no kuzajya tuzikaraba buri munsi.
Repubulika ya Tchèque na Slovakiya byamaganye gusohoka mu ruhame utambaye agapfukamunwa cyangwa utwikiriye amazuru n'umunwa.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Vietnam yasabye abantu bose kwambara agapfukamunwa iyo bagiye ahantu hahurira abantu benshi kugira ngo bibarinde n'abandi.
Guverinoma ya Otirishiya yategetse ko umuntu wese winjira mu iduka ry'ibiribwa agomba kwambara agapfukamunwa.
Isiraheli yasabye abaturage bose kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bari mu ruhame.
Tayiwani, imaze gukora udupfukamunwa miliyoni icumi ku munsi kuva hagati muri Werurwe, yasabye abagenzi mu gari ya moshi na bisi z'imijyi gutwara udupfukamunwa ku itariki ya 1 Mata.
Panama yashyizeho itegeko ryo kwambara agapfukamunwa igihe cyose ugiye hanze, ariko nanone igasaba ko abantu badashobora kugura agapfukamunwa bagakoresha mu rugo.
Amasako y'urukozasoni yakoreshejwe cyane mu Buyapani, Koreya y'Epfo, Maleziya na Singapuru.
Gukurikirana intera hagati y'abantu (uzwi kandi nka physical distancing) bikubiyemo ibikorwa byo kurwanya ubwandu bigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara binyuze mu kugabanya imikoranire ya hafi hagati y'abantu.
Bimwe mu byo bakora harimo gushyira abantu mu kato, guhagarika ingendo, gufunga amashuri, aho bakorera, ibibuga by'imikino, amazu y'imikino cyangwa amazu y'ubucuruzi.
Abantu bashobora gukurikiza uburyo bwo gutandukanya abantu baguma mu rugo, kugabanya ingendo, kwirinda ahantu hahurira abantu benshi, gukoresha amagambo yo gusuhuza abantu batagira uwo bahuye, no kwitandukanya n'abandi.
Ubu leta nyinshi zirimo gutegeka cyangwa zikanasaba abantu kwirinda mu turere twugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Ingano y'abantu benshi cyane bateranye yagaragajwe n'inzego za leta z'Amerika n'inzego z'ubuzima, yagabanyijwe vuba cyane kuva ku bantu 250 (niba nta cyorezo cya COVID-19 cyamenyekanye mu karere) kugera ku bantu 50, nyuma y'aho bagera ku bantu 10.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe 2020, Ubudage bwabujije guteranira mu ruhame abantu barenga babiri. Abantu bakuru n'abafite ibibazo by'uburwayi nk'igisukari, indwara z'umutima, indwara z'ubuhumekero, umuvuduko ukabije w'amaraso, n'uburwayi bw'ubwirinzi bufite ibibazo, bahura n'ibyago byo kurwara indwara zikomeye n'impungenge kandi CDC yabasabye kuguma mu rugo uko bishoboka kose mu duce twugarijwe n'icyorezo. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, OMS n'izindi nzego z'ubuzima zatangiye gusimbuza ikoreshwa ry'ijambo "gukomeza gutandukana mu muryango" "gukomeza gutandukana ku mubiri", kugira ngo bisobanuke ko intego ari ukugabanya imibonano mpuzabitsina mu gihe bakomeza kugirana imishyikirano, haba mu buryo busanzwe cyangwa kure.
Gukoresha ijambo "kuva kure" byatumye abantu bagombye kwiherera mu bantu, aho kubatera inkunga yo gukomeza gushyikirana n'abandi hakoreshejwe ubundi buryo. Abayobozi bamwe batanze amabwiriza y'ubuzima bw'imyororokere yo gukoreshwa muri iki gihe cy'icyorezo.
Muri byo harimo inama yo kugirana imibonano mpuzabitsina n'umuntu mubana gusa, udafite virusi cyangwa ibimenyetso byayo.
Kwigumira mu rugo byasabwe ku bantu basanganywe COVID-19 n'abakeka ko banduye.
Inzego z'ubuzima zatanze amabwiriza arambuye yo kwitandukanya neza. Guverinoma nyinshi zategetse cyangwa zasabye abantu bose baba mu turere twugarijwe n'iki cyorezo kwitandukanya.
Amabwiriza akomeye yo kwikumira yatanzwe ku bantu bari mu matsinda y'ibyago byinshi.
Ababa baragaragaye ku muntu ufite COVID-19 n'ababa baherutse kujya mu gihugu cyangwa akarere kagize ubwandu bukomeye bagiriwe inama yo kwicungira mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 uhereye igihe basanzwe basanzwe basanganywe.
Uburyo bwo kurwanya icyorezo ni ukucyumira cyangwa kucyicisha, no kucyicisha.
Gukumira indwara bikorwa mu bihe bya mbere by'icyorezo kandi bigamije gushakisha no gutandukanya abanduye no gushyiraho ubundi buryo bwo kugenzura indwara no gukingira kugira ngo indwara ihagarare mu bandi bantu.
Iyo bitagishoboka gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iyi ndwara, imihati ihita ijya mu cyiciro cyo kugabanya ubukana bwayo: hafatwa ingamba zo kugabanya ikwirakwira ryayo no kugabanya ingaruka zayo ku rwego rw'ubuzima n'umuryango.
Hateganyijwe ko hazakorwa ibikorwa byo guhagarika no kugabanya ibiza mu gihe kimwe.
Gukumira bisaba ingamba zikomeye cyane kugirango uhindure icyorezo ugabanya umubare w'ibanze wo kubyara munsi ya 1.Kimwe mu byo gukemura icyorezo cyandura ni ugushaka kugabanya icyorezo, bizwi nka flattening the epidemic curve.
Ibi bigabanya ibyago byo kurengera serivisi z'ubuzima kandi bigatuma haboneka igihe gihagije cyo gukora inkingo n'uburyo bwo kuvura.
Ingamba z'ubuvuzi zishobora gucunga iki cyorezo zirimo ingamba zo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye, nko kugira isuku y'amaboko, kwambara udupfukamunwa no kwishyira mu kato; ingamba z'abaturage zigamije gutandukanya abantu nk'amashuri gufunga no guhagarika ibikorwa byo guteranira hamwe; uruhare rw'abaturage mu gushishikariza abantu kwemera no kwitabira bene ibyo bikorwa; hamwe n'ingamba z'ibidukikije nko gusukura ubutaka. Ingamba zikomeye kurushaho zigamije gukumira iki cyorezo zafashwe mu Bushinwa ubwo ubukana bw'iki cyorezo bwagaragaye, nko gushyira mu kato imijyi yose no gushyiraho amategeko akomeye yo kubuza ingendo.
Ibindi bihugu nabyo byashyizeho ingamba zitandukanye zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho ibipimo by'abantu benshi no gushyira abantu mu kato, kandi itanga imiburo ku bijyanye n'aho abantu banduye bajya.
Singapuru yatanze inkunga y'amafaranga ku bantu banduye bari biyemeje kwigenga kandi yashyizeho amande menshi ku batabikoze.
Taiwan yongeye umusaruro w'ibirashe byo mu maso kandi ihana kubika ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi. Ibipimo byakozwe ku Bwongereza no muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika bigaragaza ko kugabanya (kugabanya ariko kudakuraho ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo) no kucyimura (guhindura icyorezo cyakomeje kwiyongera) bifite ibibazo bikomeye.
Amategeko yo kugabanya ubukana bw'indwara ashobora kugabanya umubare w'abajya mu bitaro mu gihe cy'ibihe bikomeye ku kigero cya 2/3 n'abapfa bagagabanukaho kimwe cya kabiri, ariko bikaguma bituma abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi amagana bapfa kandi gahunda z'ubuzima zikagorwa.
Gucika birashobora gutangwa ariko bigomba gukomeza igihe cyose virusi ikomeje gukwirakwira mu baturage (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rubonetse, niba ari rwo ruza mbere), kuko ubundi kwanduza byihuta iyo ingamba zisuzumwe.
Gufata ingamba z'igihe kirekire zo guhashya icyorezo bitera ingaruka ku bukungu no ku mibereho y'abaturage.
Nta miti yihariye yo kurwanya virusi yemewe kuri COVID-19, ariko ibikorwa byo kuyikoresha birimo gukorwa, harimo no gupima imiti iriho.
Gufata imiti ya murandasi, kunywa amazi no kuruhuka bishobora kugabanya ibimenyetso by'iyo ndwara.
Bitewe n'uburemere bw'iyo ndwara, bishobora kuba ngombwa ko umuntu afata umwuka wa ogisijeni, akanywa amazi mu maraso, kandi agahumeka.
Gukoresha imiti ya Steroide bishobora gutuma ingaruka z'iyo ndwara zirushaho kuba mbi.
Imyinshi mu miti yari yaremewe mbere gukoreshwa mu kuvura izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi irimo gukorwaho ubushakashatsi kugira ngo ikoreshwe mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS kandi yavuze ko hari "imiti gakondo n'imiti yo mu rugo" ishobora koroshya ibimenyetso byatewe na SARS-CoV-19.
Kongera ubushobozi no guhindura uburyo bwo kwita ku buzima ku byo abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye bivugwa na OMS nk'ingamba z'ibanze zo guhangana n'icyorezo.
ECDC n'ibiro by'akarere by'u Burayi bya OMS byasohoye amabwiriza ku bitaro n'imirimo y'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze yo kwimura umutungo ku byiciro byinshi, harimo gushyira imbaraga mu gukora ibizamini bya COVID-19, guhagarika ibikorwa by'amatora igihe cyose bishoboka, gutandukanya no gutandukanya abarwayi ba COVID-19 bafite uburwayi, no kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 binyuze mu guhugura abakozi no kongera umubare w'ibikoresho byo guhumeka no kuryama.
Hari ibitekerezo binyuranye ku birebana n'aho ikibazo cya mbere (cyitwa umurwayi wa zeru) gishobora kuba cyarakomotse.
Umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanye ko yanduye coronavirus nshya ashobora kuba yongeye kugaragara ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan, Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi kumwe, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubei wiyongereye buhoro buhoro.
Ibi ahanini byari bifitanye isano n'isoko rya Huanan ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja, ryagurishaga n'amatungo ari muzima, kandi hari igitekerezo cy'uko virusi yavuye muri imwe muri izi nyamaswa; cyangwa, mu yandi magambo, ifite inkomoko ya zoonotic.Igiterwa cya pneumonia kitaramenyekana cyibonekeye ku ya 26 Ukuboza kandi cyitabwaho n'umuganga Zhang Jixian mu bitaro by'intara ya Hubei, wamenyesheje CDC ya Wuhan Jianghan ku ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ku ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan baburiye bagenzi babo ko hari "coronavirus imeze nka SARS".
Abaganga umunani muri bo, harimo na Li Wenliang, polisi yabahaye igihano kubera ko bakwirakwije ibihuha, naho undi witwa Ai Fen, abacamanza be baramuhanaga kubera ko yari yahagurukije abantu.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Umugi wa Wuhan nyuma yaho yasohoye itangazo ku mugaragaro ku wa 31 Ukuboza, maze imenyesha OMS.
Abategetsi b'ubuzima muri Wuhan bari babonye imibare ihagije y'uburwayi bw'ibicurane butaramenyekana kugira ngo hatangirwe iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama. Mu bihe by'intangiriro z'icyorezo, umubare w'abanduye wikubye kabiri hafi buri minsi irindwi n'igice.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yakwirakwiriye mu zindi ntara z'Ubushinwa, ifashwa n'impunzi z'Ubushinwa z'umwaka mushya ndetse na Wuhan ari umuhanda w'ingendo n'umuhanda munini w'ibyuma.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwatangaje abantu bashya bagera kuri 140 banduye mu munsi umwe, barimo abantu babiri i Beijing n'umwe muri Shenzhen.
Nyuma amakuru yemewe agaragaza ko abantu 6,174 bari bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020.Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zarenze Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani ku mubare munini w'abamaze kwandura.Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, abanduye barenga miliyoni 1.61 baramaze kumenyekana ku isi hose; abantu barenga 97,000 barapfuye, abandi barenga 364,000 barakize.
Ibihugu n'uturere bigera kuri 200 byagize nibura umuntu umwe wafashwe.
Kubera icyorezo cyugarije Uburayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije urujya n'uruza rw'abantu no gushyiraho igenzura ry'imipaka.
Ibisubizo by'igihugu byaranzwe n'ingamba zo kwirinda nk'amabwiriza yo kuguma mu rugo (azwi nka stay-at-home orders, shelter-in-place orders, cyangwa lockdown) n'amasaha yo gutaha. Kugeza ku ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300, cyangwa hafi 90% by'abaturage, bari mu buryo runaka bwo gufunga muri Amerika, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 bari mu gihome muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 59 bari mu gihome muri Afurika y'Epfo, n'abantu miliyari 1.3 bari mu gihome mu Buhinde.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi hose bari mu buryo runaka bwo gufunga, biyongera ku bantu miliyari 2.6 nyuma y'iminsi ibiri, ni ukuvuga hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko yanduye COVID-19 yagaragaye ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan; raporo imwe itaremezwa igaragaza ko umuntu wa mbere wanduye ari ku itariki ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Muganga Zhang Jixian yabonye itsinda ry'abantu barwaye indwara y'ibicurane ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, ibitaro bye bikaba byamenyesheje Wuhan Jianghan CDC ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ibizamini bya mbere by'imiterere y'urugero rw'umurwayi ku ya 27 Ukuboza 2019 byagaragaje ko hari virusi ya SARS isa na coronavirus.
Itangazo ry'umuturage ryashyizwe ahagaragara na Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Umurenge wa Wuhan ku wa 31 Ukuboza.
OMS yabimenyeshejwe kuri uwo munsi.
Mu gihe ibyo bimenyeshamakuru byabaga, abapolisi baburiye abaganga bo muri Wuhan ko "bakwirakwiza ibihuha" ku cyorezo.
Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa yabanje kuvuga ko nta "gihamya igaragara" y'uko umuntu ashobora kwandura indwara.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bukomeye nyuma y'aho buvugwa n'umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa Xi Jinping nk'"intambara y'abaturage" yo gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Mu byavuzwe ko ari "igihembwe kinini mu mateka y'abantu", ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama hatangajwe ko habaho uruzitiro rw'ubuzima ruhagarika ingendo zijya n'izisohoka i Wuhan, rwagutse ku mijyi 15 muri Hubei, rwerekeza ku bantu bagera kuri miriyoni 57.
Gukoresha imodoka z'abantu ku giti cyabo byari bibujijwe muri uwo mujyi.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza Umwaka Mushya w'Abashinwa (25 Mutarama) byahagaritswe ahantu henshi.
Abayobozi batangaje kandi ko bagiye kubaka ibitaro by'agateganyo, bitwa Huoshenshan Hospital, byararangiye mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hubatswe ikindi bitaro, ari cyo Leishenshan Hospital, kugira ngo kijye cyakira abandi barwayi.
Usibye ibitaro biherutse kubakwa, Ubushinwa bwongeye guhindura ibindi bigo 14 i Wuhan, nk'ibigo by'amakoraniro n'ibibuga by'imikino, mu bitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yashyizeho izindi ngamba zo gukumira icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga itangazo ry'ubuzima ku bantu bakora ingendo no kongera iminsi mikuru y'impeshyi.
Kaminuza n'amashuri hirya no hino mu gihugu nabyo byarafunzwe.
Uturere twa Hong Kong na Macau twashyizeho ingamba zitandukanye, cyane cyane ku bijyanye n'amashuri na za kaminuza.
Ingamba zo gukora mu buryo bwa kure zashyizweho mu turere twinshi tw'Ubushinwa.
Imihango yo gutembera yashyizweho mu mujyi wa Hubei no hanze yawo.
Imodoka za Leta zahinduwe, kandi amazu ndangamurage yo mu Bushinwa yose arafungwa by'agateganyo.
Igenzura ry'urugendo rwa rubanda ryakoreshejwe mu mijyi myinshi, kandi byemejwe ko abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bahanganye n'uburyo runaka bwo guhagarika imirimo yo hanze. Nyuma y'uko icyorezo cyinjiye mu cyiciro cyacyo ku isi muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda ko virusi "yinjira" mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho iminsi 14 yo guhagarika by'agateganyo ingendo zose z'amahanga zinjira mu mujyi. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Ubushinwa bwari bwanduriye umuntu umwe gusa mu gihugu mu minsi itanu yabanjirije, muri iki gihe binyuze ku muntu wari uvuye i Istanbul agarutse i Guangzhou.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubushinwa Li Keqiang yatangaje ko ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu bwanduye mu gihugu cyabo ryahagaritswe kandi ko icyorezo cyagenzurwa mu Bushinwa.
Kuri uwo munsi, ingamba zo gutembera zarorohejwe muri Hubei, usibye Wuhan, nyuma y'amezi abiri itegeko ryo gufunga rishyiriweho. Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ku wa 26 Werurwe 2020 ko kwinjira ku bafite viza cyangwa ibyangombwa byo gutura bizahagarikwa guhera ku wa 28 Werurwe, nta makuru arambuye yerekeye igihe iyi politiki izarangirira.
Abashaka kwinjira mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba viza muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsulati z'Ubushinwa.
Guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yashishikarije ubucuruzi n'inganda kongera gufungura ku ya 30 Werurwe, kandi itanga gahunda zo gukangurira ibigo. Inama ya Leta yatangaje umunsi wo kurira utangira ku munota wa gatatu wo guceceka ku rwego rw'igihugu ku ya 4 Mata saa kumi n'ebyiri, uhura n'umunsi mukuru wa Qingming, nubwo guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yasabye imiryango guha icyubahiro ku rubuga rwa interineti mu kubahiriza intera hagati y'abantu kugira ngo birinde kongera kwandura COVID-19.
COVID-19 yemejwe ko yakwirakwiriye muri Koreya y'Epfo ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020 ivuye mu Bushinwa.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare habaye ukwiyongera kw'abanduye, ahanini biterwa n'ikoraniro ryabereye i Daegu ry'umuteguro mushya uzwi nka Shincheonji Church of Jesus.
Abashumba ba Shincheonji basuye Daegu baturutse i Wuhan bakekwaho kuba aribo batumye iki cyorezo gitangira.
Kugeza ku wa 22 Gashyantare, mu bayoboke 9,336 b'iri torero, 1,261 cyangwa 13% bavuze ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko igipimo cyo kwihuta kiri hejuru ku wa 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abantu barenga 2000 bemejwe ko banduye muri Koreya, ku ya 29 Gashyantare bari bageze ku 3150.
Ibigo byose bya gisirikare bya Koreya y'Epfo byashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'ibizamini byemeje ko abasirikare batatu banduye virusi.
Amatariki y'indege nayo yagize ingaruka bityo arahinduka. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho gahunda yafashwe nk'iyari nini kandi yateguwe neza ku isi yo gupima abaturage kugira ngo basangire virusi, no gushyira mu kato abantu bose banduye, no gushakisha no gushyira mu kato abahuye na bo.
Uburyo bwo gupima harimo no gutanga amakuru ku bimenyetso by'abantu bashya bageze mu mahanga binyuze kuri porogaramu ya telefoni, gupima virusi mu modoka n'ibisubizo biboneka ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima kugirango abantu bagera ku 20.000 bapimwe buri munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo ifatwa nk'iyatanze umusaruro mu kugenzura icyorezo nubwo nta mijyi yose yashyizwe mu kato. Mu mizo ya mbere, abaturage ba Koreya y'Epfo bari batandukanye ku buryo Perezida Moon Jae-in yitabiriye iki cyorezo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba ko Moon yafungwa kubera ibyo bavugaga ko ari uburyo bubi leta yakoresheje mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo, cyangwa se bashima uko yabyitwayemo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Koreya y'Epfo yari ifite umubare muto w'abanduye umunsi umwe mu byumweru bine bishize.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe byatangajwe ko guhera ku ya 1 Mata abantu bose bashya bageze mu mahanga bazajya bashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko itangazamakuru ryabitangaje ku ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yakiriye ubusabe bw'ubufasha mu gupima virusi buturutse mu bihugu bitandukanye 121.
Irani yatangaje ko abantu ba mbere banduye SARS-CoV-2 byemejwe kuwa 19 Gashyantare i Qom, aho Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi bw'Ubuvuzi yavuze ko abantu babiri bapfuye nyuma y'uwo munsi.
Ingamba za mbere zatangajwe na leta harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, siporo, amasengesho yo ku wa gatanu, gufunga kaminuza, ibigo by'amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani yashyize muri gahunda miriyari eshanu z'amafaranga y'u Rwanda yo kurwanya virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ku wa 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato uturere twibasiwe n'icyorezo, kandi ko abantu bonyine ari bo bazajya bashyirwa mu kato.
Imyiteguro yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi yatangajwe muri Werurwe, nubwo urujya n'uruza rwinshi hagati y'imijyi mbere y'umwaka mushya wa Nowruz mu Buperesi rwakomeje.
Ahantu hatagatifu ha Shia i Qom hagumye hagaragara ku bantu bajya gusengera kugeza tariki ya 16 Werurwe 2020. Irani yabaye ihuriro ry'ikwirakwira rya virusi nyuma y'Ubushinwa muri Gashyantare.
Hagati y'ibyifuzo byo guhisha igipimo cy'icyorezo muri Irani, ibihugu birenga icumi byari byongeye kugaragaraho abarwayi babo muri Irani ku ya 28 Gashyantare, byerekana ko igipimo cy'icyorezo gishobora kuba gikomeye kuruta 388 byatangajwe na leta ya Irani kuri iyo tariki.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe, aho 23 mu banyamuryango bayo 290 bavugwa ko basuzumwe basanga bafite virusi ku ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku itariki ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani kurekura byimazeyo abarwanashyaka b'uburenganzira bwa muntu bafunzwe bazira imyivumbagatanyo y'amahoro, no kurekura by'agateganyo imfungwa zose zifite uburenganzira.
Yavuze ko hari ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwira kwa virusi mu bigo bifunze nk'ibigo byo gufungirwamo, nabyo bidafite ubuvuzi buhagije.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye ku munsi umwe, ari bo benshi mu gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Nibura abanyapolitiki 12 cyangwa abahoze ari abanyapolitiki ba Irani n'abategetsi ba leta bapfuye bazize iyi ndwara ku ya 17 Werurwe.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yari ifite abarwayi bashya 50 buri saha n'urupfu rushya buri minota icumi kubera coronavirus.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umukozi wa OMS, mu gihugu cya Irani hashobora kuba hari abantu benshi cyane kurusha uko bivugwa.
Hari kandi abavuga ko ibihano bya Amerika kuri Irani bishobora kuba bigira ingaruka ku bushobozi bw'igihugu mu by'ubukungu bwo guhangana n'icyorezo cya virusi.
Komiseri Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku burenganzira bwa muntu yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu bigabanywa ku bihugu byibasiwe cyane n'icyorezo, harimo na Irani.
Icyorezo cyemejwe ko cyakwirakwiriye mu Butaliyani ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubwo ba mukerarugendo babiri b'Abashinwa bageragereshwaga ko banduye SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Abanduye batangiye kwiyongera cyane, ibyo bituma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose zijya n'izava mu Bushinwa kandi itangaza ko hari ikibazo cy'ubukene.
Nyuma yaho, haje kugaragara itsinda ry'abantu banduye COVID-19, batangiye kwandura 16 muri Lombardie ku ya 21 Gashyantare. Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rishya ryo gukumira iki cyorezo, harimo no gushyira mu kato abantu barenga 50.000 baturutse mu mirenge 11 itandukanye yo mu majyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte yagize ati "Mu bice byugarijwe n'icyorezo, kwinjira no gusohoka ntibizatangwa.
Gufunga ibikorwa by'akazi n'imikino byamaze gutangwa muri utwo turere".Ku ya 4 Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na kaminuza bifungwa burundu mu gihugu hose kuko Ubutaliyani bwageze ku 100 bapfuye.
Ibirori byose by'imikino ikomeye, harimo imikino ya Serie A, byari biteganyijwe ko bizabera mu nzu z'abakinnyi kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe, siporo yose yahagaritswe burundu nibura ukwezi kumwe.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conte yategetse guhagarika ibikorwa hafi ya byose by'ubucuruzi usibye amaduka manini n'amafashini. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ikigo cy'Ubutaliyani gishinzwe ubuvuzi, ubuvuzi, guhugura no kwita ku barwayi bakomeye (SIAARTI) cyasohoye inama z'ubuvuzi ku bijyanye n'amabwiriza y'ubuvuzi ashobora gukoreshwa.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, Ubutaliyani bwirutse Ubushinwa nk'igihugu gifite umubare munini w'abapfuye bazira coronavirus ku isi nyuma yo gutanga amakuru y'abantu 3,405 bishwe n'icyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Uburusiya bwohereje indege icyenda za gisirikare zitwaye ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Kugeza ku ya 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hari abantu 128,948 bamaze kwandura, 15,887 bapfuye, na 21,815 bakize, abenshi muri abo bantu bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardie.
Raporo ya CNN yagaragaje ko kuba mu Butaliyani hari abantu benshi bageze mu za bukuru kandi bakaba batarabasha gupima abantu bose bafite virusi kugeza ubu, bishobora kuba ari byo bituma habaho umubare munini w'abahitanwa na yo.
Igisubizo cy'u Bwongereza kuri virusi cyabanje kugaragara nk'igihugu cyaruhutse cyane mu bihugu byibasiwe, kandi kugeza tariki ya 18 Werurwe 2020, leta y'u Bwongereza ntiyigeze ishyiraho uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo gutandukanya abantu cyangwa ingamba zo gushyira abantu mu kato ku baturage bayo.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko leta yanenzwe kubera ko yabonye ko nta ntera n'ubushishozi ifite mu gusubiza ibibazo by'abaturage. Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatangaje ko abantu batagomba gukora ingendo z'ingenzi cyangwa gushyikirana n'abandi, asaba abantu gukora bari mu rugo aho bishoboka kandi bakirinda ahantu nko mu tubari, muri resitora no mu mazu y'imikino.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, guverinoma yatangaje ko ibigo byose by'imyidagaduro nka pubs na gyms bigomba gufungwa vuba bishoboka, kandi isezeranya kwishyura kugeza kuri 80% by'umushahara w'abakozi ku gipimo cya £2,500 ku kwezi kugirango birinde ubushomeri mu bihe by'ibibazo. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo gutandukanya abantu, kubuza guteranira abantu barenga babiri no guhagarika ingendo n'ibikorwa byo hanze kubyo bifatwa nk'ibikenewe cyane.
Bitandukanye n'ingamba zabanje, izi mbogamizi zakurikizwaga na polisi binyuze mu gutanga amande no gutatanya amateraniro.
Ubucuruzi bwinshi bwategetswe gufunga, uretse ubucuruzi bwabonwaga ko ari "ngenzi", harimo amasupamaketi, amaduka y'imiti, amabanki, amaduka acuruza ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi, sitasiyo za lisansi n'amazu y'imodoka.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanye ko yanduye COVID-19 yemejwe mu ntara ya Washington mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bw'inyanja ya Pasifika, mu mugabo wari watashye avuye i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Itsinda ry'abashinzwe kurwanya Coronavirus ryashyizweho ku itariki ya 29 Mutarama.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko habaye ikibazo cy'ubutabazi mu rwego rw'ubuzima rusange, kandi bushyiraho imipaka ku kwinjira ku bantu baturuka mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura indwara - ikigo cy'ubuvuzi cya leta ya Amerika - cyatangaje ko cyakoze igikoresho cyacyo cy'igerageza.
Nubwo Amerika yabigenje ityo, yatangiye gutangira gupima vuba, ibyo bikaba byaratumye abantu batabona neza uko icyorezo cyari giteye icyo gihe.
Ibizamini byarakomerekejwe n'ibikoresho by'ibizamini by'amakosa byakozwe na leta muri Gashyantare, kubura kwemerwa na leta y'igihugu ku bikoresho by'ibizamini bitari ibya leta (n'amashuri, ibigo n'ibitaro) kugeza mu mpera za Gashyantare, n'ibipimo by'ingengabuzima abantu bagomba kubahiriza kugirango bemererwe gukora ikizamini kugeza mu ntangiriro za Werurwe (nyuma yaho hakenewe icyemezo cya muganga).
Ku itariki ya 27 Gashyantare, ikinyamakuru cyitwa The Washington Post cyatangaje ko muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika hakozwe ibizamini bitarenga 4.000.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru cyitwa The Atlantic cyatangaje ko hateganyijwe ibipimo bitarenga 14.000.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, Associated Press yatangaje ko "abantu benshi bafite ibimenyetso n'amabwiriza ya muganga bategereje amasaha cyangwa iminsi yo gupimwa". Nyuma y'urupfu rwa mbere muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika rwamenyekanye muri leta ya Washington ku itariki ya 29 Gashyantare, Guverineri Jay Inslee yatangaje ko hari imimerere y'ubutabazi, igikorwa cyaje gukurikiraho n'izindi leta.
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yahagaritse amasomo ku ya 3 Werurwe, kandi mu kwezi kwa gatatu hagati, amashuri yo mu gihugu hose yari afunze. Ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zabwiwe ibijyanye n'ingaruka z'icyorezo cya coronavirus gishya ku gihugu n'itsinda ry'abahanga mu by'indwara z'ibyorezo bo muri Imperial College London.
Kuri uwo munsi Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ryo kwitegura no gusubiza Coronavirus, ryatanze miliyari 8.3 z'amadolari yo gushyigikira mu buryo bwihutirwa inzego z'ubutegetsi bwa leta mu guhangana n'icyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe yashyizeho amategeko agenga ingendo abakozi bakoraga, avanaho inama, kandi ashishikariza abakozi gukora bari mu rugo.
Ibirori bya siporo n'ibirori by'umwaka byarahagaritswe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko hari gahunda yo guhagarika ingendo mu bihugu byinshi by'i Burayi, uretse Ubwongereza, mu gihe cy'iminsi 30, kuva ku ya 13 Werurwe.
Ku munsi wakurikiyeho, yongeyeho ko u Bwongereza na Irilande na byo byari bibujijwe kwinjira muri icyo gihugu.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ikibazo cy'ubukungu bw'igihugu, cyatumye amafaranga ya leta agaragara kugira ngo iki kibazo gikemuke.
Guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ibigo byinshi by'ubucuruzi byafunze cyangwa bigabanyije amasaha muri Amerika yose mu kugerageza kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyari cyemejwe mu ma leta yose 50 no mu Karere ka Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko umujyi wa New York wari ufite abantu 10.700 banduye coronavirus, barenga umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, guverineri yavuze ko gutandukanya abantu bisa n'aho ari byo bigira ingaruka, kuko imibare y'abandura ikomeje kugabanuka kuva ku minsi 2.0 ikagera ku minsi 4.7.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Werurwe, mu mujyi wa New York hari hamaze kugaragara abantu 32,308 banduye, naho 672 bahitanywe n'iyi virusi. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yatangaje ko ifite abantu benshi banduye coronavirus kurusha ibindi bihugu byose ku isi, harimo u Bushinwa n'Ubutaliyani. Kugeza ku ya 8 Mata, muri Amerika hamaze kugaragara abantu 400,335 banduye, naho abantu 12,841 bamaze gupfa.
Nk'uko itangazamakuru ryabitangaje ku wa 30 Werurwe, Perezida Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kwirinda abantu kugera ku wa 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bwitwaga USNS Comfort, bwari bufite ibitanda bigera ku 1.000, bwashyize inkingi i New York.
Ku ya 3 Mata, Amerika yabonye umubare munini w'abantu 884 bapfuye bazize coronavirus mu gihe cy'amasaha 24.
Muri leta ya New York, abanduye barenze 100,000 ku ya 3 Mata. Inzu y'Umurenge yahawe igitutu cyo gupfobya ibyago no kugenzura ubutumwa binyuze mu gutegeka abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu bya siyansi guhuza imvugo n'ibitabo bya rubanda bifitanye isano na virusi n'ibiro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence.
Kwemera muri rusange uburyo Trump yakemuye iki kibazo byatangiye gutandukana hakurikijwe impande z'amashyaka.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Amerika n'abatanga ibitekerezo banenze Amerika kubera ko yishingikiriza ku gutumiza ibikoresho by'ingenzi, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi by'ibanze, bivuye mu Bushinwa.
Isesengura ry'uburyo ingendo zo mu kirere zikorwamo ryakoreshejwe mu gupima no guhanura uburyo zikwirakwira kandi ryasohotse mu kinyamakuru The Journal of Travel Medicine mu kwezi kwa Mutarama 2020.
Dukurikije amakuru yo mu 2018 yatanzwe n'Ishyirahamwe Mpuzamahanga ry'Inyambukiragutabara, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei ni byo bihugu byagize umubare munini w'abagenzi baturutse i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byatangajwe ko ari ahantu hakunzwe cyane n'abantu bavuye i Wuhan.
Bali yavuzwe ko ari yo ifite ubushobozi buke mu mijyi 20 ikunzwe cyane mu bijyanye no kwitegura, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Ositaraliya yabonetse ko ifite ubushobozi bwinshi.Australia yasohoye gahunda yo guhangana mu buryo bwihutirwa na Coronavirus (COVID-19) ku ya 7 Gashyantare.
Yavuze ko hari byinshi bitaramenyekana kuri COVID-19, kandi ko Australia izashyira imbaraga mu kugenzura imipaka no gutumanaho mu gisubizo cyayo cy'icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, muri Ositaraliya hatangajwe ko abantu bafite ikibazo cy'umutekano muke.
Kubera ko imodoka z'abaturage zahagaritswe mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei, ibihugu byinshi byateguye gukura abaturage babyo n'abakozi ba dipolomasi muri ako karere, cyane cyane binyuze mu ndege z'igihugu cyabo, abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bakaba barabitangiye.
Kanada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, u Buyapani, u Buhindi, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, u Bufaransa, Arijantine, u Budage na Tayilande, ni bamwe mu bantu ba mbere bateganyije ko abaturage babo bakurwa mu byabo.
Pakisitani yavuze ko itazakura umuturage uwo ari we wese mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Burezili yakuye Abarazili 34 cyangwa abagize imiryango yabo, hiyongeraho Abanyapolonye bane, Umunyayini umwe n'Umunyamerika.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, mu Bushinwa no mu Buhindi bavuye muri Polonye, aho indege yo muri Brezili yahagaritse mbere yo gukomeza urugendo rwayo yerekeza muri Brezili.
Abaturage ba Brazil bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare hafi ya Brasília.
Kuri uwo munsi, Abakanada 215 (176 bari mu ndege ya mbere, na 39 bari mu ndege ya kabiri yari yaraguzwe na leta ya Amerika) bakuwe i Wuhan bajyanwa muri CFB Trenton kugira ngo bajye mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye Abakanada 185 baturutse i Wuhan yageze ku kibuga cy'indege cya CFB Trenton.
Abayobozi ba Australia bakuye abaturage 277 ku itariki ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare, babajyana mu kigo cya Christmas Island, cyari cyarahinduwe ahantu ho kuba mu kato, aho bamaze iminsi 14.
Indege yo guhungisha abantu yo muri Nouvelle Zélande yageze i Auckland ku ya 5 Gashyantare; abagenzi bayo (harimo bamwe baturutse muri Ositaraliya no muri Pasifika) bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cy'abasirikare mu mazi i Whangaparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko zizakura Abanyamerika bari mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abagenzi 129 b'Abanyakanada bari bavuye muri Diamond Princess yageze i Trenton, Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'Ubuhinde yatangiye gukura abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airways yari yaraguzwe na leta y'Afurika y'Epfo yasubije mu gihugu abaturage 112 b'Afurika y'Epfo.
Igenzura ry'ubuvuzi ryakorewe mbere yo kugenda, kandi abantu bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragazaga ibimenyetso bya coronavirus basigaye inyuma kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago.
Abaturage ba Afurika y'Epfo gusa bagaragaje ko badafite ibimenyetso by'indwara, ni bo basubijwe mu gihugu cyabo.
Ibyavuye mu igerageza byemeje ko abanyafurika y'Epfo bose, harimo abasirikare, abapilote, abakozi ba hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari muri iyo misiyo y'ubutabazi, bose bagumye mu rwego rwo kwirinda, baguma mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 muri The Ranch Resort.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zatangiye gukura ingabo zayo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, minisiteri y'ububanyi n'amahanga y'Ubushinwa yavuze ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarusi, Pakisitani, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byoherereje u Bushinwa imfashanyo.
Bamwe mu banyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri kaminuza z'Abanyamerika bifatanyije mu gufasha kohereza imfashanyo mu bice by'Ubushinwa byibasiwe na virusi, aho itsinda ry'abashyize hamwe mu karere ka Chicago ryamenyekanye ko ryabashije kohereza udupfukamunwa 50.000 twa N95 mu bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku wa 30 Mutarama. Umuryango w'ubutabazi Direct Relief, ufatanyije na FedEx, wohereje udupfukamunwa 200.000 hamwe n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku giti cyawe, harimo intoki n'imyenda, binyuze mu ndege yihutirwa yo kohereza ku bitaro bya Wuhan Union ku wa 30 Mutarama.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje impano ya miliyoni 100 z'amadolari y'Amerika zo gushyigikira OMS mu bushakashatsi ku rukingo no mu bikorwa byo kuvura, hamwe no kurinda "abaturage bari mu kaga muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Amajyepfo".
Interaksyon yatangaje ko guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 muri Philippines ku ya 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'uko Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku itariki ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapore yatangaje ko izohereza imfashanyo ya miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni imwe muri Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwohereje toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Wuhan, Maleziya yatangaje ko yatanze imyenda y'ubuvuzi miliyoni 18 mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwatanze ibikoresho bitandukanye by'ubuvuzi birimo imyenda 10,000 ya Hazmat, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zitanga toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa ndetse zasezeranya inkunga y'amafaranga y'amadolari y'Amerika y'amadolari y'Amerika y'Amerika ku bihugu byibasiwe n'icyorezo. Nyuma y'uko abarwayi mu Bushinwa basaga n'aho bakomeje kwiyongera, iki gihugu cyakomeje kohereza imfashanyo ibihugu bitandukanye byibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'impuguke zo gufasha Ubutaliyani guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima miriyoni 1,1, udupfukamunwa miriyoni 6, n'imyambaro yo kurinda 60,000 i Addis Abeba muri Ethiopia kugira ngo bitangirwe n'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bwa Afurika.
Nyuma yo kohereza ibikoresho byo gupima 5,000, udupfukamunwa 100,000 n'ibikoresho 5 byo guhumeka mu mubiri muri Panama.
Ma kandi yatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Canada. Ubuholandi, Esipanye, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Czech bagaragaje impungenge zabo ku bigunira n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yakuye ibikoresho 58 000 byo gupima coronavirus byakozwe mu Bushinwa bifite igipimo cy'ubwiringiro cya 30% gusa, mu gihe Ubuholandi bwo bwakuye 600,000 by'udupfukamunwa tw'Abashinwa twari dufite inenge.
U Bubiligi bwasubije inyuma udupfukamunwa 100.000 tutakoreshwa, twibukwa ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Colombia.
Ku rundi ruhande, imfashanyo y'Ubushinwa yakiriwe neza mu bice bimwe na bimwe bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije ibikorwa by'ubutabazi byihutirwa ku bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimye imbaraga abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bashyizeho mu gucunga no gukumira iki cyorezo.
OMS yagaragaje itandukaniro riri hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004, aho abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bashinjwaga ibanga ryabujije ibikorwa byo kwirinda no gukumira, n'ikibazo kiriho ubu aho leta nkuru "yatanga amakuru buri gihe kugira ngo yirinde ubwoba mbere y'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya w'ukwezi".
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza ku cyemezo cy'ubuyobozi bw'igihugu cyo gushyiraho itegeko ribuza ingendo muri Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS Gauden Galea yavuze ko nubwo "nta gushidikanya atari inama yatanzwe na OMS", ariko kandi ari "ikimenyetso cy'ingenzi cyane cyerekana ko biyemeje gukumira icyorezo ahantu cyiganje cyane" maze avuga ko ari "ikintu kitigeze kibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange".Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemezwa ko abantu bahurira ku bandi hanze y'Ubushinwa no kwiyongera kw'umubare w'abandura mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubutabazi bw'ubuzima rusange (PHEIC), kikaba ari icyiciro cya gatandatu cya PHEIC kuva icyo cyorezo cyatangira gukoreshwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube cya 2009.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko PHEIC yatewe n'uko "ishobora gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amafaranga make cyangwa ari hagati mu mafaranga, bidakoresha uburyo bwiza bwo kwita ku buzima.
Mu gusubiza ku ishyirwa mu bikorwa ry'amategeko agenga ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gushyiraho ingamba zitagira icyo zitwaye ku ngendo mpuzamahanga n'ubucuruzi" kandi ko "OMS idasaba ko ubucuruzi n'ingendo byashyirwa mu kaga".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gushyigikira ibikorwa byo kwitegura mu bihugu bifite amafaranga make, ivuga ko ari ngombwa gushyigikira ibihugu "bitafite uburyo bwo kumenya abantu banduye virusi, n'iyo yaba yongeye kugaragara".
Tedros yakomeje avuga ko "dukomeye cyane nk'aho turi mu gice cy'ubudehe" kandi asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "kushora imari uyu munsi cyangwa kwishyura byinshi nyuma".Ku wa 11 Gashyantare, OMS mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru yashyizeho COVID-19 nk'izina ry'indwara.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni, António Guterres, yemeye gutanga "imbaraga z'umuryango w'abibumbye wose mu gusubiza".
Itsinda rya ONU ryita ku bibazo by'ingorane ryashyizweho nk'ingaruka, ryemerera guhuza ibisubizo byose by'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, WHO ivuga ko bizabatuma "bita ku gisubizo cy'ubuzima mu gihe izindi nzego zishobora gushyiraho ubumenyi bwabo ku ngaruka rusange z'imibereho, ubukungu n'iterambere by'icyorezo".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'ubutumwa bufatanyije riyobowe na OMS hamwe n'Ubushinwa ryashyizweho kugira ngo rihe impuguke mpuzamahanga na OMS ku butaka mu Bushinwa gufasha mu buyobozi bw'imbere mu gihugu no gupima "uburemere n'ubwandu bw'iyi ndwara" binyuze mu kwakira amahugurwa n'inama n'inzego z'ingenzi ku rwego rw'igihugu no gukora ingendo zo ku butaka kugira ngo bapime "ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo gusubiza ku rwego rw'intara n'intara, harimo n'imijyi n'imidugudu".Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ko "isi igomba gukora byinshi kugira ngo yitegure icyorezo cy'icyorezo cya coronavirus", ivuga ko nubwo hakiri kare cyane kucyita icyorezo, ibihugu bigomba ariko "kuba mu cyiciro cyo kwitegura".
Mu gusubiza icyorezo cyagendaga kigaragara muri Irani, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'ubutumwa bufatanyije muri Iran ngo rigenzure uko ibintu bimeze. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko icyorezo cya coronavirus ku rwego rw'isi kizazamurwa kiva ku "cyinshi" kijye ku "cyinshi cyane", iki kikaba ari cyo kigero cyo kwihuta cyane n'icy'ibyago.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye Ryita ku Buzima, mu itangazo yatanze, yatanze umuburo agira ati "iyi ni inama ya buri butegetsi bwose ku isi: Nimukanguke.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba iri mu nzira kandi ugomba kwitegura", asaba ko ingamba zo gusubiza neza zishobora gufasha isi kwirinda "ibibi cyane kurusha ibindi".
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru ariho ubu atemeza ko abayobozi b'ubuzima bw'abaturage batangaza icyorezo ku isi, avuga ko gutangaza bene ako kageni bizaba bisobanura "mu by'ukuri twemera ko buri muntu wese ku isi azahura n'iyo virusi".
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi Mukuru yavuze ko OMS "ihangayikishijwe cyane n'ubwiyongere n'uburemere by'icyorezo, ndetse n'ubwiyongere bw'ubushomeri".OMS yahuye n'ibitekerezo bikomeye ku byo abantu babona ko ari ugukemura neza icyorezo, harimo gutangaza vuba ikibazo cy'ubutabazi mu buzima rusange no gushyira virusi mu cyiciro cy'icyorezo.
Igisubizo cy'abatavuga rumwe na leta cyagaragaje inyandiko yasabaga umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, gutanga imihoho, yashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733.000 ku itariki ya 6 Mata.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, impuguke mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu za ONU z'ibihumbi byinshi zashimangiye kubahiriza uburenganzira bwa buri muntu wese mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo gukora ibikorwa by'ubutabazi bifasha abantu kurokora ubuzima, kandi ko leta ari yo ifite inshingano yo kubikora.
Iri tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura umutungo cyangwa ubwishingizi bw'uburwayi bitagomba na rimwe kuba impamvu yo gutandukanya itsinda runaka.
Abahanga bagaragaje ko buri muntu wese afite uburenganzira ku buzima, harimo abafite ubumuga, abava mu miryango y'abagabo, abageze mu za bukuru, abimukira, abatagira aho baba, ababaho mu mimerere mibi cyane, abafunzwe, impunzi n'andi matsinda atazwi akeneye inkunga ya leta.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga ishinzwe ubutegetsi irimo gukemura ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho myiza y'abaturage ziterwa n'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Umuryango w'Ubukungu n'Iterambere watangije urubuga rwo gutanga amakuru ajyanye n'imyanzuro ya politiki mu bihugu byo hirya no hino ku isi, hamwe n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Kuva ku miyoborere yo gukomeza sisitemu y'ubuzima n'ubukungu bw'isi kugeza ku guhangana n'ingaruka zo gufunga no guhagarika ingendo, iki kigo cya digitale kirimo Country Policy Tracker, kandi kigamije gufasha ibihugu kwigira ku bindi no korohereza igisubizo cy'isi yose ku kibazo cya coronavirus.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yanenzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Minisitiri w'Ubwongereza ushinzwe Ibiro bya Minisitiri w'Intebe Michael Gove, n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Brezil Jair Bolsonaro, Eduardo Bolsonaro kubera uburyo yakemuye icyorezo cyatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei yo mu Bushinwa.
Abategetsi b'intara benshi b'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa (CPC) birukanywe kubera uburyo bakemuye ibikorwa byo gushyira abantu mu kato mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, ikimenyetso cy'uko batishimiye uko ubutegetsi bwa politiki bwashubije iki cyorezo muri utwo turere.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bemeza ko iyi ntambwe yari igamije kurinda Xi Jinping, umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti mu Bushinwa, uburakari bw'abaturage kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Abashinwa, urugero nka Zhao Lijian banze kwemera ko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatangiriye i Wuhan, bashyigikira ibitekerezo by'impimbano ku cyorezo cya COVID-19 cyaturutse muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
Ubuyobozi bwa Amerika bwa Donald Trump bwise coronavirus "virusi y'Abashinwa" cyangwa "virusi ya Wuhan" buvuga ko "kugenzura kw'Ubushinwa byongereye virusi ubu imaze guhinduka icyorezo cyugarije isi yose", ibyo bikaba byanenzwe na bamwe mu banenga ko ari ivangura ry'amoko kandi "bitesha agaciro uburyo ubutegetsi bwe bwananiwe gukumira iyi ndwara".
Ikinyamakuru Daily Beast cyabonye telegaramu ya leta ya Amerika igaragaza uburyo bwo gutumanaho bwagaragaye ko bwatangiriye mu Nama y'Umutekano w'Igihugu, aho iyo gahunda yavuzwe ko "byose byerekeranye n'u Bushinwa.
Tubwirwa kugerageza gutangaza ubu butumwa mu buryo bwose bushoboka, harimo ibiganiro by'abanyamakuru no kugaragara kuri televiziyo. "Ibinyamakuru nka Politico, Politiki y'amahanga, na Bloomberg byatangaje ko imihati y'Ubushinwa yo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byibasiwe na virusi ari kimwe mu bikorwa by'ubuvugizi byo gushishikariza abantu kugira uruhare ku isi.
Umuyobozi ushinzwe politiki y'ububanyi n'amahanga w'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, Josep Borrell, yaburiye ko hari "ikintu gihereranye na politiki yo mu rwego rw'isi, hakubiyemo no guharanira kugira uruhare binyuriye mu gukwirakwiza ibintu no 'kugira ingeso nziza.'"
Borrell yavuze kandi ko "Ubushinwa burimo butera inkunga ubutumwa bw'uko, bitandukanye na Amerika, ari umufasha ufite inshingano kandi wizewe".
Ubushinwa kandi bwasabye Amerika gukuraho ibihano byayo kuri Syria, Venezuela na Iran, mu gihe bivugwa ko yohereje imfashanyo muri ibi bihugu bibiri bya nyuma.
Jack Ma yatanze udupfukamunwa 100.000 kuri Cuba byabujijwe n'ibihano bya Amerika ku ya 3 Mata.
Abayobozi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika kandi bashinjwa ko barehereza imfashanyo zari zigenewe ibindi bihugu mu gihugu cyabo.
Hari kandi n'amakimbirane y'ibihugu by'Abadage, Abosirasi n'Abaswiss, Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani, avuga ku bijyanye n'ibanga.
Byongeye kandi, Turukiya yafashe ibikoresho bihumeka umwuka bibarirwa mu magana byari bigenewe muri Esipanye.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yanenze ko Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi udashyigikiye u Butaliyani bwazahajwe na coronavirus.
Maurizio Massari, Ambasaderi w'Ubutaliyani muri EU, yavuze ko "Ubushinwa bwonyine ari bwo bwitabiriye ku buryo bw'amajwi.
Nta gushidikanya ko ibyo atari ikimenyetso cyiza cy'ubwiyunge bw'u Burayi".
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma y'ikiganiro cya telefoni na Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubutaliyani Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'Uburusiya Vladimir Putin yateganyije ko ingabo z'Uburusiya zohereza mu Butaliyani abaganga ba gisirikare, imodoka zihariye zo guhanagura indwara, n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa cyasubiyemo amagambo yavuzwe n'"umuntu ukomeye mu bya politiki" utaramenyekana, avuga ko 80 ku ijana by'imfashanyo z'u Burusiya "zitagira umumaro cyangwa ko nta cyo zikeneye mu Butaliyani".
Uwo muyobozi yashinje u Burusiya gutangira igitero cyo "kugenzura imiterere y'isi n'ububanyi n'amahanga".
Perezida wa Lombardie, Attilio Fontana, na Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'u Butaliyani Luigi Di Maio, banze ibyo itangazamakuru ryavuze, maze bagaragaza ko bishimiye ibyo bakoze.
U Burusiya kandi bwohereje indege itwara imizigo iherekejwe n'imiti muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Peskov, yavuze ko "mu gihe [Putin] atanga ubufasha ku bakorana na we b'Abanyamerika, atekereza ko igihe abacuruzi b'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'ibikoresho byo muri Amerika bazaba bamaze gutera imbere, na bo bazaba bashobora kubikora mu gihe bibaye ngombwa".
Imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO "Defender 2020" iteganyijwe mu Budage, Polonye, n'ibihugu bya Baltique, imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO ikomeye cyane kuva intambara y'ubutita irangiye, izaba ku kigero gito.
Umunyamabanga mukuru wa Campaign for Nuclear Disarmament, Kate Hudson yanenze imyitozo ya Defender 2020 agira ati: "Muri iki gihe cy'ibibazo by'ubuzima rusange, ntabwo iteza akaga ubuzima bw'abasirikare ba Amerika n'ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi bifatanyije gusa ahubwo iteza akaga n'abaturage b'ibihugu bikoreramo". Guverinoma ya Irani yahuye cyane na virusi, aho abanyamuryango bagera kuri 20 b'inteko ishinga amategeko bayanduye ndetse n'abandi bantu 15 b'ubu cyangwa bahoze ari abanyapolitiki.
Perezida wa Irani Hassan Rouhani yandikiye abayobozi b'isi ibaruwa isaba ubufasha ku itariki ya 14 Werurwe 2020, avuga ko igihugu cye kirimo kugorwa no kurwanya iki cyorezo kubera kubura uburyo bwo kugera ku masoko mpuzamahanga kubera ibihano bya Amerika kuri Irani. Iki cyorezo cyateye Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gusaba ko yakurikiza politiki rusange mu bindi bihugu bikize, harimo kwita ku buzima bw'abantu bose, kwita ku bana bose, ikiruhuko cy'umuryango gihemba, no kongera amafaranga yo kugura ubuzima bw'abaturage.
Abasesenguzi mu bya politiki bari biteze ko bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku byiringiro bya Donald Trump byo kongera gutorwa mu matora ya perezida ya 2020. Imishyikirano ya dipolomasi hagati y'u Buyapani na Koreya y'Epfo yarushijeho kuzamba kubera icyorezo.
Koreya y'Epfo yanenze "imihati y'ubwirinzi bw'abantu benshi kandi idashyize mu gaciro" y'u Buyapani nyuma y'uko u Buyapani butangaje ko umuntu wese uzava muri Koreya y'Epfo azashyirwa mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri mu duce twashyizweho na leta.
Mu mizo ya mbere, abaturage bo muri Koreya y'Epfo bari batandukanye bitewe n'uko Perezida Moon Jae-in yabyitwayemo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba ko Moon yafungwa kubera ibyo bavuga ko ari uburyo leta itarimo gukemura neza iki cyorezo, cyangwa se bashima uko yabyitwayemo. Icyorezo cyatumye ibihugu byemerera amategeko y'ubutabazi mu gusubiza.
Hari abantu bamwe na bamwe bavuze ko icyo cyemezo cyatumaga ubutegetsi bukomeza kwifatira ubutegetsi.
Muri Hongiriya, inteko ishinga amategeko y'icyo gihugu yemeye ko Minisitiri w'Intebe, Viktor Orbán, ashobora gutegeka ku bw'itegeko mu gihe kitarondoreka, guhagarika inteko ishinga amategeko ndetse n'amatora no guhana abafatwa nk'abatanze amakuru y'ibinyoma ku byerekeye virusi n'uburyo leta yafashe iki kibazo.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus cyagaragaye ko aricyo cyateje ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibikoresho, bitewe n'uko ku isi hose hakoreshejwe ibikoresho byinshi mu kurwanya icyo cyorezo, abantu bagura mu buryo bwo guhungabana, ndetse n'ibikorwa by'inganda n'ibikorwaremezo bikangirika.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyatanze imiburo ku kibazo cy'ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitewe n'ikomeje kwiyongera k'ibyifuzo by'abakiriya n'ihungabana ry'ababicuruza.
Mu bice bitandukanye, abantu baguye mu kantu bagura ibicuruzwa, bituma abantu batakaza ibicuruzwa by'ibanze nk'ibiribwa, impapuro z'isuku n'amazi yafunzwe mu mazi, bituma habaho ibura ry'ibikoresho.
Uruganda rw'ikoranabuhanga rwatangiye kuburira abantu ku gutinda gutumiza ibicuruzwa bya elegitoroniki.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS witwa Tedros Adhanom yavuze ko umubare w'abantu bakeneye ibikoresho byo kwirinda wikubye inshuro 100.
Ibyo byatumye ibiciro byiyongeraho inshuro zigera kuri makumyabiri z'ibiciro bisanzwe ndetse bituma n'ibicuruzwa by'ubuvuzi bitinda gutangwa mu gihe cy'amezi ane cyangwa atandatu.
Nanone kandi, byatumye ku isi hose habaho ikibazo cy'ibikoresho byo kwirinda, kandi OMS yatanze umuburo w'uko ibyo bishobora gushyira mu kaga abakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima.
Muri Ositaraliya, icyorezo cyatanze amahirwe mashya ku bagura daigou kugurisha ibicuruzwa byo muri Ositaraliya mu Bushinwa.
Iki gikorwa cyateje ikibazo cy'ibura ry'amafunguro y'abana mu maduka manini amwe n'amwe, nyuma y'aho leta ya Australia irabyanga. Nubwo abantu benshi banduye COVID-19 mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu karere ka Wuhan, ndetse n'ibyifuzo byinshi by'ibyokurya, utwo turere twombi twaracitse intege kubera ibura ry'ibiribwa.
Ingamba z'u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani zo kurwanya ubucuruzi butemewe n'amategeko bw'ibikomoka ku bicuruzwa by'ingenzi zagize icyo zigeraho, bituma hatabaho inzara ikomeye y'ibiribwa yari yitezwe mu Burayi no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
U Butaliyani bw'amajyaruguru bufite umusaruro munini w'ubuhinzi ntibwagize igabanuka rikomeye, ariko ibiciro bishobora kwiyongera nk'uko abahagarariye inganda babivuga.
Amashuka y'ibiribwa yabonetse gusa by'agateganyo, ndetse no mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu gihe abayobozi ba leta y'Ubushinwa bashyiraga hanze inyama z'ingurube kugira ngo abaturage babone ibyokurya bihagije.
Mu Butaliyani na ho hari amategeko nk'ayo asaba abahinzi b'ibiribwa kubika ibyokurya mu gihe habaye ibintu nk'ibyo byihutirwa.
Ibyangiritse ku bukungu bw'isi byibonekeje mu Bushinwa: dukurikije raporo y'itangazamakuru yo ku wa 16 Werurwe, ubukungu mu Bushinwa bwahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020 kubera ingamba zafashwe na leta zo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi, ndetse n'igurisha ryagabanutseho 20,5%.
Kubera ko Ubushinwa ari igihugu gifite ubukungu bukomeye n'ikigo cy'inganda, icyorezo cya virusi cyagaragaye ko ari cyo gitera guhungabanya ubukungu bw'isi.
