Gukaraba intoki, nanone bizwi ko ari isuku y'intoki, ni igikorwa cyo gukaraba intoki kugira ngo umuntu akureho umukungugu, ibinure, mikorobe cyangwa ibindi bintu bidakenewe.
Gukaraba intoki buri gihe mu "bihe bikomeye" mu munsi birinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'ibicurane na kolera, byandurira mu byondo.
Abantu bashobora kandi kwandura indwara z'ubuhumekero nka grippe cyangwa ibicurane, urugero, iyo badakarabye intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, ku zuru cyangwa ku kanwa (ni ukuvuga mu maso).
Ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi mu munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ingenzi harimo: mbere na nyuma yo gutaha, nyuma yo gusukura umwana cyangwa guhindura impapuro z'ibinyugunyugu, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya na mbere na nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gukorana n'inyama mbi, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Niba nta mazi n'isabune biboneka, ushobora gukaraba intoki ukoresheje ivu.
