Nyuma yo guhumeka, gukorora cyangwa kwiyuha akuya.
Nyuma yo gukora ku matungo, ku biribwa by'amatungo cyangwa ku myanda yayo.
Isuku y'amaboko mu by'ubuvuzi yerekeza ku bikorwa by'isuku bifitanye isano n'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukoresha imiti cyangwa kuvurwa bishobora gukumira indwara cyangwa kugabanya ikwirakwira ryayo.
Intego nyamukuru yo gukaraba intoki mu buvuzi ni ukuzikuramo udukoko dutera indwara (bakteriya, virusi cyangwa ibindi binyabuzima by'ibanze bishobora gutera indwara) n'ibikoresho by'ubumara bishobora gutera indwara cyangwa se kwangiza.
Ibi ni ingenzi cyane ku bantu bakoresha ibiribwa cyangwa bakora mu buvuzi, ariko kandi ni ingenzi ku bantu muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kenshi ku buzima, harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ibicurane, coronavirus, n'izindi ndwara zandura; gukumira indwara zandura ziterwa n'ibicurane; kugabanya indwara z'ubuhumekero;
no kugabanya umubare w'abana bapfa mu gihe cyo kubyarira mu ngo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2013 bwagaragaje ko iyo abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu bakomeje gukaraba intoki, bishobora gutuma barushaho gukura.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, umubare w'abana bapfa bazize indwara z'ubuhumekero n'ibicurane ushobora kugabanuka binyuriye mu guhindura imyitwarire y'abana, urugero nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Ibyo byoroheje bishobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa bazize izo ndwara hafi 50%.
Gushyiraho ingamba zo gukaraba intoki bishobora kugabanya ibyorezo by'ibicurane hafi na kimwe cya gatatu, kandi ibyo bishobora kugereranywa no gutanga amazi meza mu turere dufite abaturage bake.
48% by'abagira ikibazo cy'ibicurane bishobora guterwa no gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni bwo buryo bwonyine bw'ingirakamaro kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda ibicurane n'indwara z'ubuhumekero (ARI), nk'uko bikorwa mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu baturage hirya no hino ku isi.
Icyorezo cy'ibicurane, ari na cyo cyibasira cyane abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu, ni cyo kiza ku mwanya wa mbere mu bituma abana bagera kuri miriyoni 1.8 bapfa buri mwaka.
Indwara y'ibicurane n'iy'ibicurane bihitana abana bagera hafi kuri miriyoni 3,5 buri mwaka.
