Gukaraba intoki ubusanzwe bijyana n'ibindi bikorwa by'isuku mu rwego rw'amazi, isuku n'isuku (WASH).
Gukaraba intoki kandi birinda impetigo yandurira mu buryo butaziguye binyuze mu kugirana imibonano mpuzabitsina.
Ingaruka nto mbi yo gukaraba intoki ni uko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora gutera kwangirika kw'uruhu bitewe no kuruma kw'uruhu.
Ubushakashatsi bwakorewe muri Danimarike mu mwaka wa 2012, bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutuma umuntu agira ikibazo cy'uruhu rw'intoki, cyitwa eczema cyangwa indwara y'uruhu rw'intoki, cyane cyane mu baganga.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi cyane na byo bifatwa nk'ikimenyetso cy'indwara yo guhangayika cyane (OCD).
Hari ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi mu munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ngombwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara mu cyondo: nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero (gusukura, guteka), nyuma yo gusukura umwana (guhindura impapuro z'ibise), mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya na mbere/nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gukorana n'inyama mbi, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Mu bindi bihe umuntu agomba gukaraba intoki neza kugira ngo yirinde kwandura indwara, harimo mbere na nyuma yo kuvura igisebe cyangwa igikomere; nyuma yo kwitsamura, gukorora cyangwa guhumeka; nyuma yo gukora ku bintu by'inyamaswa cyangwa gukorakora ku nyamaswa; na nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, abantu ntibakunda gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune.
