Abantu benshi bita ku buzima bwabo, bagiye bashishikarizwa gukoresha amasabune arwanya mikorobe.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya igaragaza ko gukoresha imiti yica udukoko cyangwa imiti yo kugabanya ubwandu bifasha mu kurwanya udukoko twandura.
Icyakora, amasabune arwanya mikorobe arimo imiti isanzwe irwanya mikorobe, urugero nka triclosan, ifite urutonde rw'imitwe y'ibinyabuzima idashobora kuvurwa.
Bityo rero, n'iyo imiti idashobora kurwanya mikorobe yaba itaratoranyijwe n'amasabune arwanya mikorobe, ishobora kuba idakora neza nk'uko byamamazwa.
Usibye igifasha gukora ku mubiri no kurinda uruhu, uburyo buhanitse bushobora kuba burimo aside (acide acétique, asidi ya ascorbic, acide lactique) nk'umuyobora wa pH, aside ya benzoic ikora ku mikorobe n'ibindi bifasha mu gusukura uruhu (aloe vera, vitamine, menthol, ibyaturutse mu bimera).Iperereza ryimbitse ryakozwe na Kaminuza ya Oregon School of Public Health ryerekanye ko amasabune asanzwe afite akamaro nk'amasabune yo mu rwego rw'abakiriya arwanya mikorobe arimo triclosan mu gukumira indwara no gukuraho mikorobe mu biganza.
Amazi ashyushye umuntu ashobora gukaraba intoki, ntaba ashyushye bihagije ku buryo ashobora kwica za mikorobe.
Iyo umubiri ufite ubushyuhe bwo hejuru cyane (37 °C), mikorobe zikura vuba cyane.
Icyakora, amazi ashyushye arimo isabune arushaho gukira amavuta kamere aba mu butaka n'udukoko kurusha amazi ashyushye arimo isabune.
Icyakora, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abahanga bwagaragaje ko gukoresha amazi ashyushye nta cyo byamariye intoki.
Umutoza w'intoki cyangwa umuti wo kugabanya ubukana bw'intoki ni umuti utariho amazi.
Mu mpera z'imyaka ya za 90 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, imiti yo gukaraba intoki itarimo amazi (nanone izwi nka rubs z'intoki zishingiye kuri alcohol, rubs z'intoki z'ubumara, cyangwa sanitizers z'intoki) yatangiye gukundwa cyane.
Inyinshi zibakikije isopropyl alcohol cyangwa ethanol zashyizwe hamwe n'ikinyabutabire nka Carbomer (polymer ya acrylic acid) mu gipimo cya gel, cyangwa humectant nka glycerin mu buryo bw'umwikubo, cyangwa busa kugira ngo bikorohere gukoresha no kugabanya ingaruka zo gukama kwa alcohol.
Kongeramo idorojeni-peroxide itoshye byongera ikindi gikorwa cyo kurwanya mikorobe. Amazi yo gusukura intoki arimo nibura 60 kugeza kuri 95% by'inzoga ni umuti wica udukoko.
Imiti yo guhanagura imyanda ikoreshwa mu kunywa inzoga yica mikorobe, mikorobe zidashobora kuvurwa n'imiti myinshi (MRSA na VRE), igituntu, na za virusi zimwe na zimwe (harimo virusi itera sida, herpes, RSV, rhinovirus, vaccinia, grippe na hepatite) n'imicongi.
Imiti yo guhanagura intoki irimo inzoga 70% yica 99,97% (3.5 log igabanuka, isa n'igabanuka rya 35 decibel) ya bagiteri ku biganza nyuma y'amasegonda 30 nyuma yo kuyishyiraho na 99,99% kugeza kuri 99,999% (4 kugeza kuri 5 log igabanuka) ya bagiteri ku biganza nyuma y'iminota 1 nyuma yo kuyishyiraho. Imiti yo guhanagura intoki ni ingirakamaro cyane ku bagiteri ariko ntiyifasha cyane ku mikorobe imwe n'imwe.
Imiti yo guhanagura intoki irimo inzoga ntifasha cyane mu kurwanya virusi z'ubwoko bwa norovirus (cyangwa Norwalk), ikaba ari yo mpamvu ikunze gutera indwara z'ubuhumekero. Ugomba gukoresha imiti yo guhanagura intoki cyangwa inzoga bihagije kugira ngo wanduze neza intoki cyangwa uzitwikire.
Imbere n'inyuma y'amaboko yombi, hagati y'intoki zose n'impande zazo, bisukurwa mu gihe cy'amasegonda agera kuri 30 kugeza igihe amazi, urumuri cyangwa umujyo biba byumye.
Inshuro z'intoki zigomba gukaraba neza, ukazisiga mu biganza byombi. Ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara gitanga inama yo gukaraba intoki hejuru y'ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki, cyane cyane iyo intoki zanduye.
Gukoresha izi nkingo bikomeje kwiyongera bishingiye ku buryo byoroshye kuzikoresha no ku buryo byihuse bica udukoko duto; ariko, ntibigomba gusimbura gukaraba intoki mu buryo bukwiriye keretse gusa iyo nta sabuni n'amazi bihari.
Gukoresha kenshi imiti yo guhanagura intoki irimo inzoga bishobora gutuma uruhu rugira umwanda keretse iyo hari imiti yo koroshya imitsi cyangwa se imyuka yo guhanagura imitsi y'uruhu yongewe mu buryo bw'ibyokurya.
Ingaruka zo gukama za alubumu zishobora kugabanuka cyangwa kuzimanganywa hiyongereyeho glycerin na/cyangwa ibindi bintu bihumuriza mu buryo bw'umuti.
Mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi, imiti yo guhanagura intoki irimo inzoga irimo imyunyunyu ituma uruhu rutera umwotsi n'umwotsi bike ugereranyije n'amasabune cyangwa imiti yo guhanagura intoki.
Indwara yo mu maso ituma umuntu agira irungu, indwara yo mu maso ituma umuntu agira urticaria cyangwa se umuntu akagira ibyiyumvo byo kurenza urugero ku nzoga cyangwa ku bindi bintu biboneka mu mikorobe y'intoki irimo inzoga, ni ibintu bidakunze kubaho.
Kuba abantu batakundaga gukaraba intoki bakoresheje amazi n'isabune, byatumye batakaza ibyago byo kurwara indwara z'uruhu ziterwa no guhura n'umuntu.
N'ubwo ari ingirakamaro, imiti itarimo amazi ntiyakuraho ibintu bihumanya mu ntoki, ahubwo iba ari umuti wo kuzirinda.
Ni yo mpamvu imiti yo guhanagura intoki idakora neza nk'isabune n'amazi mu gukumira ikwirakwira ry'udukoko twandura indwara nyinshi, kubera ko utwo dukoko dukomeza kuba ku ntoki.
Igisukika cy'amaboko kitagira inzoga cyishingira cyane ku bikoresho n'uburyo cyakoreshejwe, kandi mu mateka cyagiye kigira ingaruka mbi cyane ku nzoga no gusukura inzoga.
Mu bihe bya vuba aha, uburyo bukoresha benzalkonium chloride bwagaragaye ko bugira imbaraga zidashira kandi ziterwa na mikorobe nyuma yo kubukoresha, bitandukanye na alcohol, yagaragaye ko igira imbaraga nke nyuma yo gukoreshwa kenshi, bishoboka ko biterwa n'ingaruka ziterwa n'imikorere mibi y'uruhu.
Abantu benshi bo mu duce dufite amikoro make ntibashobora kugura isabune, bityo bakoresha ivu cyangwa ubutaka.
Umukungugu cyangwa ubutaka bishobora kugira ingaruka nziza kurusha amazi yonyine, ariko bishobora kuba bidatanga umusaruro nk'uwo isabune igira.
Hari impamvu imwe ituma abantu bahangayika, ni uko iyo ubutaka cyangwa ivu byanduye mikorobe, bishobora gutuma indwara zikwirakwira cyane aho kugabanya.
Kimwe n'isabune, ivu na ryo rigira uruhare mu gukemura indwara, kubera ko iyo rihuye n'amazi riba ryaragize umuti urimo umusemburo.
OMS yatanze inama y'uko iyo nta sabuni ihari, umuntu yakoresha ivu cyangwa umusenyi.
Uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki bukwiriye bwasabwe n'ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara mu kwirinda kwanduza indwara burimo intambwe zikurikira:
Jya wima intoki amazi ashyushye cyangwa akonje.
Ni byiza ko amazi atemba kuko ayo mu biraro ashobora kwandura, mu gihe ubushyuhe bw'amazi busa n'aho nta cyo buhindura.
Jya ukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune nyinshi, usige n'inyuma y'intoki, hagati y'intoki no munsi y'imisumari.
Isabuni ikura za mikorobe mu ruhu, kandi ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko abantu bakaraba intoki neza iyo bakoresheje isabune aho gukoresha amazi yonyine.
Jya ubyotsa nibura amasegonda 20.
Gukaraba bituma habaho guhuzagurika, bigatuma udukoko dukomoka ku ruhu tuva mu ruhu, kandi gukaraba igihe kirekire bituma udukoko dukomeza kugenda twiyongera.
Jya ubyuhira neza.
Gucukura intoki mu kibindi bishobora kongera kwanduza intoki.
Jya ukaraba neza cyangwa se ureke umwuka ukayumye.
Ibibanza bikunze kubura ni ikiganza cya mbere, intoki, hagati y'intoki, n'amaboko.
Amagi y'ibumba n'amabara y'iminwa bishobora kuba birimo mikorobe.
Kenshi, umuti wo gukaraba urakoreshwa mu gutuma intoki zituma zidakama; uruhu rukomeye rushobora kwangiza uruhu, ibyo bikaba byongera ibyago byo kwandura indwara.
Uburyo butandukanye buhendutse bushobora gukorwa kugirango byorohereze gukaraba intoki aho amazi ya tap na/cyangwa isabune bitagerwaho, urugero: gusuka amazi mu gikombe cyangwa mu kabari gifungishije imyobo ikwiriye na/cyangwa gukoresha ivu iyo bikenewe mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.Mu bihe by'amazi aciriritse (nk'amashuri cyangwa uturere two mu byaro mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere), hari ibisubizo byo kubungabunga amazi, nk' "ibikoresho byo gukaraba" n'ibindi by'igiciro gito.
Igikoresho cyo gukata ni ikoranabuhanga ryoroheje rikoresha inkono ifunze ku mugozi, n'inkoni ikoreshwa n'ibirenge kugira ngo isuke amazi make ku biganza no ku isabune.
Kumesa neza intoki ni ikintu cy'ingenzi mu birebana no kugira isuku y'intoki, ariko hari impaka ku buryo bwiza bwo kumesa intoki mu byumba bya rusange.
Ubushakashatsi bugenda bwiyongera bugaragaza ko amasahani y'impapuro arusha isuku cyane imashini zikoresha amashanyarazi yo kumesa intoki ziboneka mu byumba byinshi byo gukarabira.
Mu mwaka wa 2008, Kaminuza ya Westminster y'i Londres yakoze ubushakashatsi, kandi ikigo cy'ubucuruzi bw'ibikoresho by'impuzu cyashyigikiye ikiganiro cyitwa European Tissue Symposium, kugira ngo bagereranye ibipimo by'isuku bitangwa n'ibikoresho by'impuzu, ibyuma bikonjesha intoki mu kirere gishyushye n'ibikoresho bikonjesha intoki mu kirere bigezweho.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no kumesa intoki ukoresheje igikoresho cyo gukaraba mu kirere, basanze umubare w'ibinyabutabire byose ku ntoki wiyongereyeho 194% mu gihe ku biganza wiyongereyeho 254%.
Iyo bakoresheje imashini yo kumesa, umubare w'udukoko tw'ibanze tw'ibinyabutabire ku ntoki wiyongeraho 42% mu gihe ku biganza wiyongeraho 15%.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no kumesa intoki ukoresheje umwenda w'impapuro, umubare wose w'udukoko wagabanutse ku kigero cya 76% ku ntoki no ku biganza kugeza kuri 77%. Abahanga mu bya siyansi bakoze kandi ibizamini kugira ngo bamenye niba hari ibyago byo kwanduza abandi bakoresha ibyumba by'ubwogero n'ibidukikije by'ibyumba by'ubwogero bitewe n'ubwoko bwose bw'uburyo bwo kumesa.
Igikoresho cyo kumesa umwuka, giturutsa umwuka mu gikoresho ku muvuduko wa 180 m/s (650 km/h; 400 mph), cyari gifite ubushobozi bwo guhumeka mikorobe mu ntoki no mu gikoresho, kandi gishobora kwanduza abandi bakoresha imisarani ndetse n'aho bakorera kugeza kuri metero 2.
Gukoresha igikoresho cyo gukaraba intoki mu kirere cy'ubushyuhe byatumaga mikorobe zikwirakwira mu birometero 0,25 uvuye ku gikoresho cyo gukaraba intoki.
Amasahani y'impapuro ntiyagaragaje ikwirakwira ry'ibinyabuzima bito. Mu mwaka wa 2005, mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe na TÜV Produkt und Umwelt, hafashwe ingamba zitandukanye zo gukomora intoki.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki, habonetse impinduka zikurikira ku mubare w'udukoko:
Hari abahanga benshi bakora imashini zo kumesa intoki, kandi hari abagereranyije imashini zo kumesa intoki n'izikozwa n'utuwugi tw'impapuro.
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje impapuro z'isuku z'intoki ni ubundi buryo bwo gukora urugendo mu gihe nta sabuni n'amazi.
Umutobe wo kugabanya ubukana bw'amaboko ukoreshwa mu gusukura intoki ukoreshwa mu gusukura intoki ukoreshwa mu gusukura intoki ukoreshwa mu gusukura intoki ukoreshwa mu gusukura intoki ukoreshwa mu gusukura intoki ukoreshwa mu gusukura intoki ukoreshwa mu gusukura intoki ukoreshwa mu gusukura intoki ukoreshwa mu gusukura intoki zikoreshwa mu gusukura intoki.
Gukaraba intoki mu gihe cy'ubuvuzi byatangiye gukurikizwa nyuma y'igihe kirekire umuganga wo muri Hongiriya witwa Ignaz Semmelweis avumbuye ko ari ingirakamaro (mu wa 1846) mu kwirinda indwara mu bitaro.
Hari ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bitanga amakuru yo kwibutsa abakozi bo mu bitaro ko bagomba gukaraba intoki mu gihe bibukiwe.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwagaragaje ko gukoresha ayo mata bigabanya ubwandu.
Gukaraba intoki mu gihe cy'iminota 15 ni uburyo bwo kwivuza, ukoresha amazi menshi n'isabune cyangwa gel mu gusukura intoki no kuzisukura.
Intoki zigomba gukubitwa hamwe n'amano agashya.
Niba hari ibisigazwa munsi y'iminwa, ushobora gukoresha umufuka w'ibishyimbo kugira ngo ubikureho.
Kubera ko udukoko dushobora kuguma mu mazi ari ku biganza, ni iby'ingenzi ko ubyuhira neza hanyuma ukayihanaguza umwenda usukuye.
Nyuma yo kumesa, ukoresha umwenda w'impapuro ukaraza amazi (kandi niba ari ngombwa ukingura urugi rwo gusohoka).
Ibyo bituma intoki zidakomeza kwandura.
Intego yo gukaraba intoki mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi ni ukuvanaho udukoko dutera indwara ("mikorobe") no kwirinda ko twanduza abandi.
Ikinyamakuru kimwe (The New England Journal of Medicine) cyavuze ko mu bigo byinshi by'ubuvuzi abantu bakomeje gukena gukaraba intoki, kuko abaganga benshi n'abaforomo bakunda kwibagirwa gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku barwayi, bityo bakabakwizaho mikorobe.
Hari ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki neza n'ibindi bikorwa byoroheje bishobora kugabanya indwara zandura mu maraso zituruka ku guterwa n'inkondo z'amaraso ku kigero cya 66 ku ijana.
Inyandiko y'ibanze y'ubuyobozi bw'ubuziranenge bw'amaboko yatanzwe n'uyu muryango, ishobora kuboneka ku rubuga rwawo rwa interineti kugira ngo abantu bayisobanukirwe.
Whitby et al. bakoze isuzuma ry'icyo kibazo.
Ibikoresho by'ubucuruzi bishobora gupima no kwemeza isuku y'amaboko, niba hagikenewe kwerekana ko amategeko yubahirizwa.
