nyuma yo kwanduzwa amaraso/imyanda yo mu mubiri
mbere yo gukora igikorwa cyo kugabanya ubukana bw'imiti,
Nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi.Kongera imiti ya antiseptika mu isabune ("ibisabuni birimo imiti" cyangwa "ibikingira mikorobe") bituma umuti wo gukaraba intoki ugira ingaruka mbi.
Kugira ngo umuntu 'asukure' intoki ze mu gihe ari ku rugendo, bisaba ko agira umufuka ushobora gufunguka no guhagarara nta kuwukorakora, agakoresha chlorhexidine cyangwa iyodi, agakoresha utwuma two gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gusukura, agashyiraho n'isuku yo gukaraba intoki n'ikindi gikoresho cyo gusukura munsi y'iminwa.
Imyenda yose y'umurimbo yagombye kuvanwaho.
Iyi myitozo isaba ko umuntu akaraba intoki n'amaboko kugeza ku nkokora, ubusanzwe bikaba bimara iminota 26.
Si ngombwa ko ukoresha igihe kirekire cyo gukaraba (iminota 10).
Mu gihe cyo gukaraba, amazi ari ku biganza agomba kurindwa ngo atagaruka mu biganza.
Iyo bamaze gukaraba intoki, zikumazwa igitambaro kitagira ubukana, hanyuma bakambara ikanzu yo kubaga.
Kugira ngo udukoko dutera indwara tudakwirakwira, ni byiza ko mbere yo kwita ku muntu urwaye no nyuma yo kumwitaho, ukaraba intoki cyangwa ukoresha umuti wo kumukiza indwara.
Mu kurwanya indwara z'ubwandu bw'ibicurane mu bitaro, byagaragariye ko inyungu nyinshi cyane zo gukaraba intoki zaturutse ku 20% bya mbere byo gukaraba intoki, kandi ko inyungu y'inyongera yari nke cyane iyo gukaraba intoki byongereweho hejuru ya 35%.
Gukaraba n'isabuni isanzwe bituma indwara zandura za bakayire zikwirakwira mu byokurya zirenga inshuro eshatu ugereranyije no gukaraba n'isabuni irwanya mikorobe. Kugereranya gukaraba intoki n'umuti usanzwe ufite inzoga no gukaraba intoki n'isabuni irwanya mikorobe mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30 buri kimwe cyagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki n'inzoga byagabanyije ubwandu bwa bakayire ku kigero cya 26% kurusha isabune irwanya mikorobe.
Ariko isabune n'amazi birushaho kugira ingaruka nziza kurusha gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe inzoga mu kugabanya virusi ya H1N1 y'ibicurane A na Clostridium difficile mu ntoki.Ibikorwa byo kunoza isuku y'intoki mu bigo nderabuzima bishobora kuba bikubiyemo kwigisha abakozi gukaraba intoki, kongera uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe inzoga, no kwibutsa abakozi mu nyandiko no mu magambo.
Hakenewe ubushakashatsi bwimbitse ku birebana n'uburyo bwo kuvura bw'ingenzi kurusha ubundi mu byiciro bitandukanye by'ubuvuzi.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune ni uburyo buhendutse, kandi bw'ingenzi bwo kugira ubuzima bwiza, ndetse no kugira ibyokurya byiza.
Icyakora, kubura amazi yizewe, isabune cyangwa ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu ngo z'abantu, ku mashuri no ku kazi bituma kugera ku ngeso zo gukaraba intoki ku isi hose bitoroha.
Urugero, mu bice byinshi by'icyaro byo muri Afurika, nta macupa yo gukaraba intoki aboneka hafi y'ubwiherero bwa bwite cyangwa bwa leta, n'ubwo hari uburyo bworoheje bwo kubaka aho bakaraba intoki.
Icyakora, kudahana intoki bishobora kuba biterwa n'imyitwarire yashinze imizi aho guterwa no kubura isabune cyangwa amazi.
Guteza imbere no gushyigikira gukaraba intoki n'isabune bishobora kugira ingaruka ku myanzuro y'amategeko, gukangurira abantu kumenya akamaro ko gukaraba intoki kandi bigatuma abantu bahindura imyitwarire yabo mu gihe kirekire.
Kugira ngo ibyo bikore neza, ni ngombwa kugenzura no gusuzuma.
Isuzuma ry'ubushakashatsi 70 ryagaragaje ko uburyo bw'abaturage bukora ku gukaraba intoki mu bigo by'abadafite amikoro menshi, mu gihe gahunda zo kwamamaza ku mbuga nkoranyambaga zidakora neza. Urugero rumwe rwo guteza imbere gukaraba intoki mu mashuri ni "Inzira y'inyenyeri eshatu" ya UNICEF ishishikariza amashuri gufata ingamba zoroshye kandi zidahenze kugira ngo abanyeshuri bakarabe ko bakaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune, mu bindi bisabwa mu bijyanye n'isuku.
Iyo ibipimo by'ibanze byamaze kugerwaho, amashuri ashobora kuva ku nyenyeri imwe agera ku nyenyeri eshatu.
Kubaka ahantu ho gukaraba intoki bishobora kuba kimwe mu bikorwa byo gukangurira abantu gukaraba intoki, bigamije kugabanya indwara n'urupfu rw'abana.
Umunsi Mpuzamahanga wo Gukaraba intoki ni urundi rugero rw'ubukangurambaga bwo gukangurira abantu kugira ngo bahindure imyitwarire. Kubera icyorezo cya Coronavirus cya 2019-20, UNICEF yashishikarije abantu gukoresha ishusho yo gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi buke bwarebye ko ikiguzi cyo gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere gihanitse ugereranyije n'uburyo bwo kwirinda DALY.
Icyakora, hari ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari byo bituma umuntu abona amafaranga menshi kurusha ibindi bikorwa byo gukaraba intoki mu mazi no mu bikoresho by'isuku.
Akamaro ko gukaraba intoki ku buzima bw'abantu  cyane cyane ku bantu bafite ibibazo nk'ababyeyi baheruka kubyara cyangwa abasirikare bakomeretse mu bitaro  bwa mbere kabonetse hagati mu kinyejana cya 19 n'abapayiniya babiri mu by'isuku y'intoki: umuganga w'Umuhungari witwa Ignaz Semmelweis wakoraga i Vienne muri Otirishiya na Florence Nightingale, Umwongereza "yashinze ubuvuzi bwa none".
Icyo gihe abantu benshi bari bagikomeza kwizera ko indwara ziterwa n'impumuro mbi zitwa miasmas.
Mu myaka ya 1980, ibyorezo bituruka ku biribwa n'ubwandu bufatika mu buvuzi byatumye ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara gitera imbere cyane isuku y'amaboko nk'uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu.
Icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube mu 2009 n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu 2020 byatumye mu bihugu byinshi abantu barushaho kumenya akamaro ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune kugira ngo umuntu yirinde indwara zandura.
Urugero, mu Budage, inyandiko zigaragaza "uburyo bukwiriye bwo gukaraba intoki" zari zifungishijwe iruhande rw'ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu byumba bya rusange, mu byumba by'amazu y'ibiro n'ibibuga by'indege.
Imvugo ngo "gukaraba ibiganza" isobanura ko umuntu atagomba kwemera ko hari icyo yakoze cyangwa ngo agire uruhare muri icyo gikorwa.
Ryaturutse mu murongo wa Bibiliya wo muri Matayo aho Ponsiyo Pilato yiyuhagira ku cyemezo cyo kumanika Yesu Kristo, ariko ryahindutse imvugo ikoreshwa cyane mu moko amwe n'amwe y'Abongereza.
Muri Macbeth ya Shakespeare, Lady Macbeth atangira gukaraba intoki ku gahato mu rwego rwo kugerageza gukaraba ikizinga yibwiraga ko afite, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza umutimanama we umucira urubanza ku byaha yari yarakoze kandi akaba yarashishikarije umugabo we kubikora.
Nanone kandi, byaje kugaragara ko abantu, nyuma yo kwibuka cyangwa gutekereza ku bikorwa bidakwiriye, bakunda gukaraba intoki kenshi kurusha abandi, kandi bakishimira cyane ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki.
Byongeye kandi, abantu bemerewe gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gutekereza kuri ibyo bintu, ntibashobora gukora ibindi bikorwa byo "kwisukura", urugero nko kwitanga.
Amadini ateganya gukaraba intoki haba mu rwego rw'isuku no mu rwego rw'ikigereranyo. Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo, hakoreshejwe amazi ariko nta sabuni yo gukaraba intoki, ni kimwe mu bikorwa byo gukaraba intoki biranga amadini menshi, harimo Bahá'í, Abahindu, tevilah na netilat yadayim mu idini ry'Abayahudi, Lavabo mu Bukristo, na Wudhu muri Islamu. Amadini nayo ateganya gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'isuku, cyane cyane nyuma y'ibikorwa runaka.
Abahindu, Abayahudi n'Abayisilamu basabwa gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero.
Kandi, idini ry'Abahindu, iry'Ababuda, iry'Abasiki, iry'Abayahudi n'iry'Abayisilamu, ryasabaga ko abantu bakaraba intoki mbere y'ifunguro na nyuma yaryo.
Amabwiriza yo kurwanya COVID-19 mu kazi
Igenzura ry'ibyago byo mu kazi kuri COVID-19 ni ikoreshwa ry'uburyo bwo kwirinda ibyago byo mu kazi mu kwirinda icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Kugenzura ibyago mu kazi neza bishingiye ku kazi n'aho ukorera, hashingiwe ku gupima ibyago by'uko umuntu yagira ubwandu, ubukana bw'indwara mu baturage n'impamvu z'ibyago ku bakozi ku giti cyabo bashobora kwandura COVID-19.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'ikigo gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima mu kazi (OSHA) cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, akazi gafite ibyago bike byo kwandura gashobora gutuma umuntu atabonana n'abantu benshi cyangwa abandi bakozi, aho usanga abantu bagirwa inama yo kwirinda indwara, urugero nko gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, kubahiriza amabwiriza agenga ubuhumekero no gukora isuku buri gihe no gukemura indwara mu kazi.
Imirimo ifite ibyago byo kwandura harimo iyo isaba ko umuntu ahura kenshi cyangwa hafi n'abantu batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura bitewe no gukwirakwiza mu baturage cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Muri ibyo harimo abakozi bafatanya n'abaturage muri rusange, nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwa imirimo irimo abantu benshi, n'ahandi hacururizwa ibicuruzwa byinshi.
Mu byo aba bantu bagomba kwirinda, uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura, harimo guhumeka hakoreshejwe ibikoresho by'isuku bikora neza, kurinda abaterura, no kuba bafite ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite mu gihe umuntu arwaye COVID-19.
OSHA ibona ko abakozi bo mu nzego z'ubuzima n'abakora mu mirimo yo gupimisha abantu bagaragarijwe n'umuntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho COVID-19 bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, bikongera ibyago byo kwandura cyane iyo abakozi bakoze imikorere yo gukora aerosol ku muntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho COVID-19, cyangwa bakusanya cyangwa bagakora ibipimo by'umuntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho COVID-19.
Mu byatuma abakozi bakemura ibibazo by'akaga, harimo ibyuma byo mu rwego rw'ubwubatsi, urugero nk'ibyuma bihumanya umwuka, n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku giti cyabo bihuje n'akazi bakora.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kuba batari ku kazi bitewe n'uburwayi, kuba bagomba kwita ku bandi, cyangwa se gutinya ko bashobora kwandura.
Uburyo bwo gucuruza bushobora guhinduka, haba mu bijyanye n'ibicuruzwa bisabwa, n'uburyo bwo kubona ibicuruzwa (nk'ubucuruzi mu masaha atari ayo gufungura cyangwa binyuze mu gutanga cyangwa serivisi zo gutwara).
Icya nyuma, kohereza ibintu mu turere twibasiwe cyane na COVID-19 bishobora guhagarikwa. Gutegura indwara zandura no gukora gahunda yo guhangana nabyo birashobora gukoreshwa mu kuyobora ibikorwa byo kwirinda.
Gahunda zireba ibyago bijyanye n'aho bakorera n'imirimo itandukanye, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi, ibyago bituruka mu rugo no mu baturage, n'ibyago by'abakozi ku giti cyabo, nk'imyaka y'iza bukuru cyangwa indwara zidakira.
Nanone kandi, bigaragaza uburyo bwo kugenzura bukenewe kugira ngo ibyo byorezo bikemuke, n'imigambi yo gutabara mu gihe habaye indwara zitewe n'uko indwara z'ibyorezo zateye.
Gutegura indwara zandura no gutegura uburyo bwo guhangana na zo bishobora gushingira ku nama z'igihugu cyangwa z'akarere.
Intego zo guhangana n'icyorezo harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo guhura n'ibibazo by'ubuzima, gukomeza ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku bindi byiciro mu miyoboro yabo y'itangwa ry'ibikoresho.
Uburemere bw'indwara mu karere aho ubucuruzi bubera bigira ingaruka ku bisubizo byafashwe.
Urutonde rw'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa ni gahunda ikoreshwa cyane mu buziranenge n'ubuzima ku kazi kugira ngo ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa.
Aho ibyago bya COVID-19 bidashobora kuvanwaho, uburyo bwo kugenzura neza ni ubuhanga bwo kugenzura, hakurikirwa n'ubuyobozi, hanyuma hakagirwa ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite.
Ubugenzuzi bw'ubwubatsi burimo gutandukanya abakozi n'akaga gakomoka ku kazi, nta gushingira ku myitwarire y'abakozi, kandi bishobora kuba igisubizo cyoroshye cyane cyo gushyira mu bikorwa.
Igenzura ry'ubuyobozi ni ihinduka mu politiki cyangwa mu buryo bw'akazi bisaba ko umukozi cyangwa umukoresha agira icyo akora.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite (PPE) bifatwa nk'ibidashobora gukora neza kurusha ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi n'ibishinzwe, ariko bishobora gufasha gukumira bimwe mu byatuma umuntu ahura n'ibiza.
Ubwoko bwose bwa PPE bugomba gutoranywa hashingiwe ku kaga ku mukozi, bushyirwe neza uko bikwiye (urugero: imashini zo guhumeka), bikoreshwa buri gihe kandi neza, bigenzurwa buri gihe, bigakomeza, kandi bisimbuzwa, nibiba ngombwa, kandi bikurwaho neza, bisukurwa, bikubikwa cyangwa bikarangwa mu buryo bukwiye kugira ngo birinde kwanduzwa.
Dukurikije ibivugwa n'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Umutekano n'Ubuzima mu Mwuga (OSHA), akazi gafite ibyago bike byo kwandura gashobora gutuma umuntu atabonana n'abandi bantu cyangwa abandi bakozi.
Ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda indwara zisabwa ku kazi kose zirimo gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi mu buryo bwimbitse, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, kubahiriza amabwiriza yo guhumeka harimo no gutwikira umuntu iyo anyotewe cyangwa asese, gutanga amakariso n'ibikoresho by'ibikoresho by'imyanda, kwitegura gukora akazi ka kure cyangwa guhinduranya imyanya mu gihe bibaye ngombwa, kubuza abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi, no gukomeza isuku isanzwe no guhanagura ibidukikije by'akazi.
Kumenya vuba abantu bashobora kwandura indwara no kubashyira mu kato ni intambwe y'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi bantu bari ku kazi.
Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara no Kuzirinda (CDC), gitanga inama y'uko abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara ikomeye yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero bagomba kuguma mu rugo kugeza igihe bazaba batagifite umuriro, ibimenyetso by'umuriro, n'ibindi bimenyetso byose nibura mu gihe cy'amasaha 24, nta miti igabanya umuriro cyangwa indi miti ihindura ibimenyetso, kandi ko politiki z'ikiruhuko cyo kurwara ari izisanzwe, ko abakozi bemererwa kuguma mu rugo kugira ngo bitabe ku muntu wo mu muryango urwaye, kandi ko abakozi bazi neza izo ngamba.
Nk'uko OSHA ibivuga, akazi gafite ibyago byo kwandura harimo akazi gasaba ko umuntu ahura kenshi cyangwa hafi cyane mu ntera ya metero 1.8 n'abantu bataramenyekana cyangwa bakekwaho kuba barwaye COVID-19, ariko bashobora kuba banduye SARS-CoV-2 bitewe no gukwirakwira kw'abantu mu gace k'ubucuruzi, cyangwa bitewe n'uko umuntu aherutse gukora ingendo mpuzamahanga mu gace karimo gukwirakwiza COVID-19.
Muri abo harimo abakozi bavugana n'abaturage muri rusange nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwamo imirimo ituwe cyane, hamwe na bimwe mu bigo by'ubucuruzi by'ubucuruzi byiganjemo abantu benshi.Ibikorwa byo gucunga ubuhanga kuri aya matsinda n'ay'abari mu byiciro by'ibyago birenzeho birimo kwinjiza ibyangombwa by'umwuka bikora neza, kongera ibipimo by'umuyaga, gushyiraho inzitizi z'umubiri nk'ibikoresho byo kurinda udutsi two muri plastike, no kwinjiza idirishya ryo gutwara imodoka mu rwego rwo gufasha abakiriya.Ibikorwa byo gucunga ibi byiciro by'abakozi n'abari mu byiciro by'ibyago birenzeho birimo gushishikariza abakozi barwaye kuguma mu rugo, gusimbuza inama za buri munsi n'ibiganiro bihuza abantu benshi, gushyiraho gahunda z'imyanya, kureka ingendo z'ingenzi ku bice birimo icyorezo cya COVID-19, gushyiraho gahunda z'itumanaho zirimo gusubiza abakozi, gutanga inyigisho zigezweho n'imyitozo ku bijyanye n'impamvu z'ibyago bya COVID-19 n'imyitwarire y'abakozi, guha abakozi amasomo y'uburyo bwo gukoresha imyambaro yo kurinda no kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19, gutanga ibikoresho byo gukaraba mu buryo bwihutirwa, gukaraba ku bikoresho by'umubiri n'ibanga, gukaraba cyangwa kwambara ku ntoki ku bikoresho by'ibanga.
Abakozi bo muri iri tsinda ry'abafite ibyago bakunze gukoresha ibikoresho byo guhumeka.
Iyo umuntu arwaye mu ndege, kugenzura neza kugirango abashinzwe umutekano n'abandi bagenzi barinde abarwaye harimo gutandukanya abarwaye n'abandi ku ntera ya metero 6, gushyiraho umwe mu bagize itsinda ngo ajye amufasha, no guha umuntu urwaye agapfukamunwa cyangwa gusaba umurwayi ko yambara umwenda mu kanwa no mu mazuru iyo arimo gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura.
Abakozi bo mu modoka bagomba kwambara intoki z'ubuvuzi zikoreshwa rimwe iyo bita ku muntu urwaye cyangwa bakagira icyo bakora ku bikomoka ku mubiri cyangwa ku bice bishobora kwanduzwa, kandi bashobora kwambara ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi bw'umuntu mu gihe uwo muntu urwaye afite umuriro, agasese cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Inkweto n'ibindi bikoresho byo gukoreshwa rimwe bigomba kujugunywa mu mufuka w'ibinyabuzima, hanyuma imiterere byanduye bigakorwaho isuku no kubihanagura. Ku bwato bw'ubucuruzi, harimo ubwato bw'ingendo n'ubundi bwato bw'abagenzi, kugenzura ibyago birimo gusubika ingendo iyo urwaye, no kwishyiriraho ukwikumira no kubwira ikigo nderabuzima cyo mu ndege ako kanya mu gihe umuntu yaba afite umuriro cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso ari mu ndege.
Mu buryo bwiza, gukurikirana kwa muganga bigomba kuba mu cyumba cy'umuntu waciwe. Ku mashuri n'ibigo byita ku bana, CDC isaba gufunga igihe gito kugira ngo isukuzwe cyangwa se isukure niba umuntu wafashwe n'iyo ndwara yaba yari mu nzu y'ishuri hatitawe ku gukwirakwira kw'abantu.
Iyo hari ubwandu buke cyangwa buke mu baturage, uburyo bwo gutandukanya abantu bushobora gushyirwa mu bikorwa nko guhagarika ingendo zo mu mirima, amakoraniro, n'indi mikoranire minini nk'imyitozo ngororamubiri cyangwa amasomo ya korali cyangwa amafunguro mu kabati, kongera umwanya hagati y'ibiro, kugabanya igihe cyo kugera n'igihe cyo kwirukana, kugabanya abashyitsi batari ngombwa, no gukoresha ahantu hatandukanye ho kubakira abana bafite ibimenyetso bisa n'iby'ibicurane.
Iyo mu gace habereye ubwandu bwinshi, usibye ingamba zo kwirinda kwishyikirana, birashoboka ko abana bakwirukanwa mu ishuri. Ku bakozi bashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bakora ibikorwa bisanzwe bya buri munsi, ibyago by'ubuzima bwihuse bifatwa nk'ibito na CDC.
Abashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bagomba kuvugana n'abantu bemejwe cyangwa bakekwaho kuba barwaye COVID-19 basabwa gukurikiza amabwiriza amwe n'abakora mu by'ubuvuzi bw'ubutabazi, harimo n'ibikoresho bikwiye byo kurinda ubuzima.
Iyo abantu bafashwe bagiranye imikoranire ya bugufi, abakozi bagomba gusukura no guhanagura imyenda n'ibikoresho byabo mbere yo kongera kubikoresha bakoresheje umuti wo gusukura cyangwa umutobe wo gusukura, kandi bagakurikiza amabwiriza asanzwe yo kubika no kujugunya ibikoresho byawe bwite bikoreshwa, no kubika no kumesa imyenda.
OSHA ibona ko abakozi bamwe na bamwe bo mu nzego z'ubuzima n'abakora mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bafite ibyago byinshi cyangwa byinshi byo kwandura.
Imirimo ifite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura harimo gutanga serivisi z'ubuzima, gushyigikira, gukora mu mavuriro no gutwara abarwayi mu by'ubuvuzi, abagerwaho n'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho.
Ibi bihinduka ibyago byo kwandura cyane iyo abakozi bakoze uburyo bwo gukora aerosol ku, cyangwa gukusanya cyangwa gufata ibipimo by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho.
Mu byakorwa mu gukora Aerosol harimo guterwa umwuka, guterwa ubuhumekero, gukora bronchoscopy, gukora ibizamini bimwe na bimwe byo mu buvuzi bw'amenyo, cyangwa gutoragura ibipimo by'amenyo.
Ibikorwa byo gupima abantu bibasirwa n'indwara nyinshi harimo abakozi bakora mu gutegura imibiri y'abantu bari bazi cyangwa bakeka ko banduye COVID-19 igihe bapfaga; abo baba bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura iyo bakoze autopsie. Ibindi bikorwa byo kugenzura mu bwubatsi by'aba bantu bafite ibyago byinshi harimo ibyumba byo gutandukanya abarwayi bafite COVID-19 bizwi cyangwa bikekwa, harimo no gukora uburyo bwo gukora aerosol.
Gutanga umwuka mu buryo bwihariye butuma umuntu atagira umwuka mwiza bishobora kuba bikwiriye mu bigo bimwe na bimwe byita ku buzima n'iby'abarwayi.
Ibimenyetso bigomba gukoreshwa hakurikijwe ingamba zo kwirinda ku rwego rwa 3 rw'umutekano wa bioloji.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryasabye ko abarwayi baza mu bitaro batandukanywa mu duce dutandukanye, bitewe n'uko bakekwaho COVID-19. Uretse ibikoresho bya bwite, OSHA yasabye ko abantu bakora mu kirere cya metero 6 ku barwayi bazwi ko banduye SARS-CoV-2, cyangwa bakekwaho kwandura, ndetse n'abakora imikorere yo gukora aerosole, bakenera ibikoresho byo guhumeka.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, ibikoresho byo guhumeka by'ibanga byemewe na NIOSH N95 cyangwa ibindi byiza bigomba gukoreshwa mu rwego rw'umushinga w'uburinzi bwo guhumeka wanditswe mu buryo bwimbitse, urimo ibizamini byo kwambara, amahugurwa n'ibizamini by'ubuvuzi.
Izindi bwoko by'ibikoresho byo guhumeka bishobora kurinda cyane kandi bigatuma abakozi barushaho kumva bamerewe neza. OMS ntishishikariza abantu kwambara imyenda yo kwipfuka, kuko COVID-19 ari indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero aho gukwirakwizwa binyuze mu mazi yo mu mubiri.
OMS isaba ko abakozi bakora mu rwego rwo kugenzura abantu binjira mu gihugu bakoresha gusa agapfukamunwa.
Ku bantu bakusanya ibipimo by'ubuhumekero, bita ku barwayi ba COVID-19, cyangwa bakabatwara nta buryo bwo gukora aerosole, OMS irasaba kwambara agapfukamunwa, udushumi, cyangwa indobo, ikanzu n'intoki.
Iyo habanje gukorwa igikorwa cyo gukora aerosol, agapfukamunwa ka kirimbuzi gashyirwa mu gikoresho cyo guhumeka cya N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Kubera ko gutanga PPE ku isi yose bidahagije, OMS isaba kugabanya ibyo gukenera PPE binyuze mu buvuzi bwa kure, inzitizi z'umubiri nk'amadirishya asukuye, kwemerera gusa abafite uruhare mu kwita ku murwayi wa COVID-19 kwinjira mu cyumba, gukoresha PPE ikenewe gusa ku gikorwa cyihariye, gukomeza gukoresha imashini imwe yo guhumeka nta kuyivana mu gihe yita ku barwayi benshi bafite icyorezo kimwe, kugenzura no guhuza urubuga rw'itangwa rya PPE, no kudashishikariza gukoresha udupfukamunwa ku bantu badafite ibimenyetso.
