b'Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni enzyme ifatanye ku gice cyo hanze (membrane z'ingirabuzimafatizo) z'ingirabuzimafatizo zo mu bihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu bihimba no mu maraso.
ACE2 irwanya ibikorwa bya enzyme ihindura angiotensin (ACE) binyuze mu kugabanya ingano ya angiotensin-II no kongera Ang (((1-7) bituma iba umuti wizewe mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 kandi ikora nk'aho yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za coronavirusi zimwe.
Imiterere y'iyi enzyme mu bantu ikunze kwitwa hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 ni metaloenzyme irimo zinc iherereye ku butaka bw'ingirabuzimafatizo zo mu nda n'izindi.
Poroteyine ya ACE2 irimo umurongo wa N-terminal peptidase M2 n'umurongo wa C-terminal wa collectrin mu byuma bitwara amino acid.
ACE2 ni poroteyine yo mu bwoko bwa I ikora mu gice kimwe cy'uruhu, ifite urubuga rw'imikorere ya enzymatically ikora ku maso y'ingirabuzimafatizo mu bihaha no mu bindi binyabuzima.
Urubuga rwo hanze y'ingirabuzimafatizo ya ACE2 ruva mu gice cyo mu nda ya transmembrane na enzyme imwe izwi nka sheddase, maze poroteyine iboneka ikavanwa mu maraso, amaherezo ikajya mu cyondo.
ACE2 iri mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifatanye n'uruhu rw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ibice by'ubuhumekero by'ubwoko bwa II, intarocyte zo mu maraso magufi, intanga z'ubuhumekero bw'imitsi n'imitsi n'utundi turemangingo tw'imitsi n'utundi tw'imitsi mu bice byinshi by'umubiri.
ACE2 mRNA nayo iboneka mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubwonko.
Intego nyamukuru ya ACE2 ni ugukora nk'igihombo cyo kurwanya ACE.
ACE isatura angiotensin I mu buryo bw'imikorere ya angiotensin II.
ACE2 nayo ihindura karboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine mu angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) maze ikayihindura hydrolyses mu angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora kandi gufatanya ibindi bipindi byinshi birimo [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, na ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi igenzura uruhu rw'indangururamajwi ya amino acid SLC6A19 kandi rwagizwe uruhare mu ndwara ya Hartnup.
Nk'umushinga wa transmembrane, ACE2 ikora nk'aho inzobere zimwe na zimwe za coronavirusi zinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo, harimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi itera SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi itera COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, guhuza poroteyine ya spike S1 ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 ku gice cya enzymatic cya ACE2 ku butaka bw'ingirabuzimafatizo bigira ingaruka mu gutangiza no guhindura virusi na enzyme mu bice by'imbere biri mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Iyi nzira yo kwinjira kandi isaba gutangiza poroteyine ya S na serine protease TMPRSS2, ubufasha bwayo burimo gukorwaho ubushakashatsi nk'umuti ushobora kuvura. Ibi byatumye bamwe batekereza ko kugabanya urugero rwa ACE2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo, bishobora gufasha mu kurwanya ubwandu.
Icyakora, imiryango myinshi y'abahanga n'inzego zishinzwe kugenzura ibiyobyabwenge byasabye gukomeza gukoresha imiti isanzwe yo mu rwego rwa ACE n'iyo mu bwoko bwa ARB.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku buryo bufite gahunda no gusuzuma ibintu byakozwe, bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012, bwagaragaje ko "gukoresha imiti ituma umuntu atagira ubushobozi bwo kuvura indwara ziterwa n'ubushye bw'uruhu byagabanyije cyane ibyago byo kurwara indwara z'uruhu ku kigero cya 34 ku ijana ugereranyije n'abari mu itsinda ry'abapima indwara ziterwa n'ubushye bw'uruhu".
Byongeye kandi, "ibyago byo kurwara impyiko byagabanutse no ku barwayi bavurwa n'abagabanya ACE bari bafite ibyago byo kurwara impyiko, cyane cyane abafite ikibazo cyo gutera stroke n'umutima udakora neza.
Gukoresha imiti ihagarika ACE byajyanye no kugabanya impfu ziterwa n'indwara z'ibicurane, nubwo ibisubizo bitari bikomeye cyane ugereranyije n'ibyagereranywa n'ingaruka zose z'indwara z'ibicurane".
