b'Ibikoresho bya COVID-19 ni porogaramu za porogaramu zigendanwa zashyizweho mu rwego rwo gufasha mu gukurikirana abo umuntu yahuye na bo mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-20, ni ukuvuga igikorwa cyo kumenya abantu ("abahuye") bashobora kuba barahuye n'umuntu wanduye.
Hariho porogaramu nyinshi zateguwe cyangwa zashyizweho, zashyigikiwe na leta mu turere tumwe na tumwe.
Hakozwe imiterere itandukanye yo kubaka porogaramu zo gukurikirana abo bahuye.
Hari impungenge z'ibanga zatanzwe, cyane cyane ku bijyanye na sisitemu zishingiye ku gukurikirana aho abakoresha porogaramu bari.
Bimwe mu bintu bitagira icyo bitwara cyane ni ugukoresha Bluetooth kugira ngo umenye aho umuntu ari hafi ya telefoni.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byombi byatangaje ko bizashyira hamwe imikorere yo gushyigikira porogaramu nk'izi zishingiye kuri Bluetooth mu buryo butaziguye muri sisitemu z'imikorere za Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa, ifatanyije na Alipay, yashyizeho porogaramu ituma abaturage bashobora kureba niba bahuye n'abantu bafite COVID-19.
Iri gukoreshwa mu mijyi irenga 200 yo mu Bushinwa. Muri Singapore, hari porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether ikoreshwa.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe n'umuryango wa IT wo muri ako gace, isohoka nk'umushinga ufunguye kandi izahabwa leta. Macédoine y'Amajyaruguru yatangije "StopKorona!", porogaramu ishingiye kuri Bluetooth igamije gukurikirana abantu bashobora kwandura no gutanga igisubizo cyihuse ku nzego z'ubuzima.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe na Minisiteri y'Itangazamakuru n'Ikoranabuhanga na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Guhera tariki ya 14 Mata 2020, iyi porogaramu yari itegereje kwemerwa na Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, guverinoma yavuze ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abantu iri mu cyiciro cyateye imbere cyo guteza imbere, kandi ko izaba ishobora gukoreshwa mu byumweru bike. Porogaramu nk'iyi iteganyijwe muri Irilande no mu Bufaransa ("StopCovid").
Australia na Nouvelle Zelande byombi birimo gutekereza kuri porogaramu zishingiye kuri porogaramu ya TraceTogether ya Singapore na protokoli ya BlueTrace. Uburusiya bufite umugambi wo gushyiraho porogaramu yo gucunga ahantu ho mu rwego rw'isi ku barwayi basanganywe COVID-19 baba i Moscou, igamije kwemeza ko batagomba kuva mu rugo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu wigisha iby'ubwubatsi bw'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yavuze ibibazo byinshi bishobora kuvuka mu mikorere y'ibikoresho, harimo n'ibimenyetso by'uko abantu bakoresha ibyo bikoresho mu buryo butari bwo, n'uko bishobora kutagira icyo bigeraho mu gihe abantu bake ari bo bakoresha ibyo bikoresho.
Mu guhangana n'impungenge z'ikwirakwira ry' porogaramu za "coronavirus" zishobora kuyobya cyangwa kwangiza, Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku bwoko bw'imiryango ishobora kongeramo porogaramu zijyanye na coronavirus muri App Store yayo, ikazigabanya ku miryango "yemewe" gusa cyangwa ifite izina ryiza.
Google na Amazon na byo byashyizeho amategeko nk'ayo.
Abashyigikiye uburenganzira bw'ibanga bagaragaje impungenge ku ngaruka zo kugenzura abantu benshi hakoreshejwe porogaramu za coronavirus, by'umwihariko niba ibikorwa remezo by'ubugenzuzi byashyizweho mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus bizasenywa igihe ibyago bizaba byashize.
Umuryango mpuzamahanga uharanira uburenganzira bw'ikiremwamuntu (Amnesty International) n'indi miryango isaga 100 basohoye itangazo risaba ko habaho imipaka ku bihereranye n'ubwo buryo bwo kugenzura.
Amashyirahamwe yatangaje ibintu umunani ku mishinga ya leta:
kugenzura bigomba kuba "bikwiriye, bikenewe kandi bihuje n'amategeko";
kongererwa gahunda yo kugenzura no kugenzura bigomba kuba bifite ingingo z'uko byatinda;
gukoresha amakuru bigomba kugabanywa ku mpamvu za COVID-19;
umutekano w'amakuru n'ubwirengagizi bigomba kurindwa kandi bikagaragazwa ko birindwa bishingiye ku bimenyetso;
Igenzura ry'ikoranabuhanga rigomba kwirinda kongera ivangura no kwirengagiza;
gusangira amakuru n'abantu batatu bigomba gusobanurwa mu mategeko;
hagomba kubaho ubuziranenge bwo kwirinda ihohoterwa n'uburenganzira bw'abaturage bwo kugira icyo bakora ku ihohoterwa;
"Kwifatanya mu buryo bwumvikana" kw' "abashishikajwe n'ikibazo" bose, harimo n'abahanga mu by'ubuzima rusange n'amatsinda y'abantu bari ku ruhande. Ikigo cy'ubucukuzi cya Computer Club (CCC) n'ikigo cy'abanyamakuru batagira imipaka (RSF) na byo byatanze urutonde rw'ibanze.
Gahunda iteganyijwe ya Google/Apple igamije gukemura ikibazo cy'ubugenzuzi buhoraho binyuze mu gukura uburyo bwo gukurikirana mu bikoresho byabo bya sisitemu y'imikorere iyo butakiri ngombwa.
Ibihugu bimwe byakoresheje uburyo bwo gukurikirana aho umuntu ari hakoreshejwe ikoranabuhanga aho gukoresha porogaramu, bivanaho icyifuzo cyo gukuramo porogaramu no kwirinda gukurikirana.
Muri Isirayeli, hemejwe uburyo bwo gukurikirana abantu hakoreshejwe imbuga nkoranyambaga.
Ibisubizo bishingiye ku muyoboro bifite uburyo bwo kubona amakuru y'aho umuntu ari bifite ibibazo bikomeye by'ibanga.
Icyakora, ntabwo sisitemu zose zifite seriveri z'ibanze zikeneye kubona amakuru yerekeye aho umuntu ari; hari umubare w'imitegekere yo kubungabunga ubuzima bwite yashyizweho ikoresha seriveri z'ibanze gusa mu itumanaho (reba igice kiri hasi).
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, hakoreshejwe uburyo butari bushingiye kuri porogaramu kugira ngo hakorwe igikorwa cyo gushakisha abo bahuye.
Aho gukoresha porogaramu yihariye, sisitemu yakusanyije amakuru yo gukurikirana ava mu masoko atandukanye harimo amakuru yo gukurikirana ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki hamwe namakuru y'ubucuruzi bwikarita, maze ibi bihuza kugirango byemeze binyuze mu butumwa bwanditse kubantu bashobora kwandura.
Uretse kuba leta yakoreshaga ayo makuru kugira ngo imenyeshe abantu bashoboraga guhura na yo, nanone yashyize ku mugaragaro amakuru y'aho umuntu yaba ari, ibyo bikaba byaratumye amategeko agenga ubuzima bwite bw'abantu ahinduka cyane nyuma y'uko muri icyo gihugu habonetse icyorezo cya MERS.
Aya makuru aboneka ku mugaragaro binyuze kuri porogaramu nyinshi na site za interineti. Ibihugu birimo n'u Budage byafashe umwanzuro wo gukoresha uburyo bwagutse n'ubw'ibanga.
Kugeza ku ya 6 Mata 2020, amakuru arambuye yari ataragaragara.
Gukurikirana amakuru y'umuntu ku giti cye ni igitekerezo cyemewe, gifite ibitabo byinshi by'ubushakashatsi byatangiye mu mwaka wa 2013.Ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda y'impuguke asaga cumi n'abiri arimo gukora ku bisubizo by'ibanga, nko gukoresha Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) kugira ngo umuntu agere kuri telefoni zigendanwa.
Ariko, PEPP-PT ni igikorwa cyo guhuza inama kirimo uburyo bw'ibanze n'ubw'ibanze, kandi ntabwo ari porotokaramu imwe. Porotokaramu z'ibanze zirimo: uburyo bwo gukurikirana hafi butabogamye (DP-PPT/DP-3T), nomero z'abashyikirana by'agateganyo (TCN, fka Contact Event Numbers, CEN), porotokaramu z'ibanga n'uburyo bwo gukurikirana abakorana n'ibanga (PACT) n'izindi.
