Guhera muri Mata 2020, leta ya Amerika ntabwo ikurikirana amakuru ajyanye n'imibonano mpuzabitsina y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko indwara ziterwa na virusi nka Ebola, SIDA, ibicurane na SARS, zigira ingaruka zitandukanye ku bagabo n'abagore.
Umubare munini w'abakozi b'ubuzima, cyane cyane abaforomo, ni abagore, kandi bafite amahirwe menshi yo kwandura iyi virusi.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ku wa 11 Gashyantare 2020 ko izina ry'ubuvuzi ryagombaga kuba "COVID-19".
Umuyobozi wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus yasobanuye ko CO ari corona, VI ari virusi, D ari indwara, na 19 ari igihe icyorezo cyamenyekanye bwa mbere: 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Izina ryatowe kugira ngo hatagira havugwa ahantu runaka (urugero: Ubushinwa), ubwoko bw'inyamaswa cyangwa itsinda ry'abantu, hakurikijwe amabwiriza mpuzamahanga yo kwita amazina agamije gukumira amahano. Virusi itera COVID-19 yitwa severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
OMS ikoresha kandi "virusi ya COVID-19" na "virusi itera COVID-19" mu itumanaho rusange.
Iyi ndwara na virusi byombi bikunze kwitwa "coronavirus".
Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya mbere cyabereye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, virusi n'indwara byavuzwe cyane ko ari "coronavirus" na "Wuhan coronavirus".
Muri Mutarama 2020, OMS yasabye 2019-nCov na 2019-nCoV indwara y'ubuhumekero nk'amazina y'agateganyo ya virusi n'indwara hakurikijwe amabwiriza yo mu 2015 yo kwirinda gukoresha ahantu mu mazina y'indwara na virusi.
Amazina yemewe ya COVID-19 na SARS-CoV-2 yashyizwe ahagaragara ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020.
Kubera ubushobozi buke mu byuma bitanga ibyangombwa, abahanga mu gukora ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga barimo gucapa ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi nk'ibikoresho byo mu mazuru n'ibice by'ibikoresho byo guhumeka.
Urugero, igihe ibitaro byo mu Butaliyani byasabaga cyane valve y'ubwonko, kandi uwo mucuruzi akaba atashoboraga kuyitanga mu gihe cyagenwe, hari ikigo cyo muri ako gace cyatangiye gukora imirimo y'ubwubatsi bw'ubwonko cyakoze ubuhanga bwo guhindura ibintu maze gicapura valve 100 zari zikenewe mu ijoro rimwe.
Nyuma y'icyorezo cya COVID-19, ibitekerezo by'impirimbanyi, amakuru atari yo n'amakuru atari yo byatangiye kuvugwa ku nkomoko, ubukana, kwirinda, kuvura n'ibindi bice by'iyi ndwara, bikwirakwira ku rubuga rwa interineti mu buryo bwihuse.
Abantu basa n'aho bashobora gukwirakwiza virusi ku zindi nyamaswa.
Ubushakashatsi ntibwabonye ibimenyetso byerekana ko virusi ishobora kwiyongera mu ngurube, mu du na mu ngurube.
Nta miti cyangwa urukingo rwemewe kuvura iyi ndwara.
Ubushakashatsi mpuzamahanga ku nkingo n'imiti ya COVID-19 burakorwa n'inzego za leta, amatsinda y'abanyeshuri n'abashakashatsi mu by'inganda.
Muri Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangije "SOLIDARITY Trial" igamije gusuzuma ingaruka zo kuvura imiti ine irimo kurwanya virusi ifite icyizere cyo gukora neza.
Nta rukingo ruboneka, ariko inzego zitandukanye zirimo gukora mu buryo bwihuse inkingo zishobora gukoreshwa.
Ibikorwa bya mbere kuri SARS-CoV birakoreshwa kuko SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 byombi bikoresha ACE2 receptor kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'umuntu.
Hari uburyo butatu bwo gukingira burimo gukorwaho ubushakashatsi.
Mbere na mbere, abashakashatsi bifuza gukora urukingo rwa virusi yose uko yakabaye.
Gukoresha virusi nk'iyi, yaba idafite ingufu cyangwa yapfuye, bigamije gutuma umubiri w'umuntu ugira ubushobozi bwo kwirinda indwara vuba na bwangu ku ndwara nshya ya COVID-19.
Uburyo bwa kabiri, ni urukingo rw'icyiciro cya kabiri, rugamije gukora urukingo rutuma abadepite bagira ubushishozi ku byiciro bimwe na bimwe bya virusi.
Ku bijyanye na SARS-CoV-2, ubwo bushakashatsi bwibanda kuri poroteyine ya S-spike ifasha virusi kwinjira mu gikoresho cya ACE2.
Uburyo bwa gatatu ni ubwo gukingira umuti w'umushongi wa nucleic acid (urukingo rwa DNA cyangwa RNA, uburyo bushya bwo gukora urukingo).
Inkingo zigerageza zo muri izi nzira zose zigomba gupimwa ku birebana n'umutekano n'akamaro. Ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020, igerageza rya mbere ry'urukingo ryatangiye ku bantu bane bitangiye gukora mu mujyi wa Seattle.
Uru rukingo rurimo kode ya jenoside itagira ingaruka ikururwa kuri virusi iteza iyi ndwara. Kwongera ubushobozi bw'umubiri w'umuntu ku buryo bw'umubiri byashyizwe ahagaragara nk'imbogamizi ishobora kuvuka mu gukora urukingo rwa SARS-COV-2, ariko ibyo biravuguruzwa.
Kugeza muri Mata 2020, hari ibizamini by'ubushakashatsi birenga 300 birimo gukorwa.
Ibizamini birindwi byasuzumaga uburyo bwo kuvura malariya bwamaze kwemerwa, harimo n'ubushakashatsi bune bwagize ku cyitwa hydroxychloroquine cyangwa chloroquine.
Imiti ya virusi isubirwamo ni yo igize ubushakashatsi bwinshi mu Bushinwa, aho hakozwe ibizamini icyenda bya III bya remdesivir mu bihugu bitandukanye biteganyijwe ko bizatangazwa mu mpera za Mata.
Igenzura ry'imikorere y'ubushakashatsi ku miti yo gukingira COVID-19 n'indi yifuza gukoreshwa, ryatangiye muri Mata 2020. Imiti myinshi irimo gukingira virusi irimo gusuzumwa mu kuvura COVID-19, harimo remdesivir, chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir na lopinavir/ritonavir ifatanyije na interferon beta.
Hari ibimenyetso by'ibanze byerekana ko umuti wa remdesivir ufite akamaro, guhera muri Werurwe 2020.
Iterambere ry'amaraso ryagaragariye mu barwayi bavurwa na remdesivir ikoreshwa mu buryo buhuje n'ubushake.
Ibizamini by'icyiciro cya III birimo gukorwa muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani. Chloroquine, yakoreshwaga mbere mu kuvura malariya, yasuzumwe mu Bushinwa muri Gashyantare 2020, hagaragaye ibisubizo bya mbere.
Icyakora, hari abantu basaba ko ubushakashatsi bukorwa hakurikijwe uko abantu babibona.
Abayobozi b'ubuzima bo muri Koreya no mu Bushinwa batanga inama yo gukoresha chlorokine.
Icyakora, Ikigo cya Wuhan gishinzwe iby'imikorere y'agakoko gatera indwara, mu gihe gitanga inama yo gufata gramu imwe buri munsi, kivuga ko incuro ebyiri z'iyo dosiye ari akaga cyane kandi ko zishobora kwica.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze uruhushya rw'ubutabazi bwo gukoresha hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine ku bw'amahitamo y'abaganga bavura abantu barwaye COVID-19. Amabwiriza y'icyongereza yo mu cyongereza yo mu cyiciro cya 7 arimo na interferon, ribavirin cyangwa umifenovir yo gukoresha mu kurwanya COVID-19.
Amakuru y'ibanze agaragaza ko ingano nini ya ribavirin ari ngombwa mu kubuza SARS-CoV-2 in vitro.
Nitazoxanide yagiriwe inama yo gukorerwa ubundi bushakashatsi mu mubiri nyuma yo kugaragaza ko ifite ubushobozi buke bwo gukumira SARS-CoV-2. Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gutangira gutangiza poroteyine ya spike na transmembrane protease serine 2 (TMPRSS2) ari ngombwa kugira ngo SARS-CoV-2 yinjire mu mubiri binyuze mu guhuza na ACE2 receptor.
Ubushakashatsi ku miti ya chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine irimo cyangwa idafite azithromycin bufite aho bugarukira cyane ku buryo bwabujije abaganga gukoresha iyi miti nta kindi cyifuzo cyo kwiga. Oseltamivir ntabwo ihagarika SARS-CoV-2 in vitro kandi nta ruhare ifite mu kuvura COVID-19.
Umuyaga w'ibinyabutabire bishobora kuba imbogamizi mu byiciro by'inyuma bya COVID-19 ikomeye.
